(4734,'Sootfoot Service: Bellowing for Help','Tradeskill','Unknown',45,45,'Smakametta has asked me to help repair the bellows for his forge, which are not pumping air properly.',0,'I managed to repair the bellows for Smakametta.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(4735,'Sootfoot Service: Hot Rocks','Tradeskill','Unknown',45,45,'Smakametta has promised to give me a copy of his recipes and one of the secret Sootfoot armor molds if I bring him some magma to make it with.',0,'I brought Smakametta the magma and he gave me his recipes, and also one of the secret Sootfoot armor molds.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(4736,'Sootfoot Service: Ore Spillage','Tradeskill','Unknown',45,45,'Smakametta now requires assistance in tidying up his ore bin and refilling its contents.',0,'I brought Smakametta the ore that he needed.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(4737,'Sootfoot Service: Repairing the Repairs','Tradeskill','Unknown',45,45,'Smakametta says the chimney over his forge hasn\'t worked well since the Sootfoot carpenters offered to repair it. I will use the schematics he has and see if I can do a better job.',0,'I repaired the chimney for Smakametta and he was very grateful.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(4738,'Sootfoot Service: Special Delivery','Tradeskill','Unknown',45,45,'Smakametta has mistaken me for a delivery minion, and is expecting me to bring him some gems for his work. This may be my way into his trust.',0,'I brought Smakametta the gems that he needed.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(4739,'Come And Get It!','Tradeskill','Unknown',60,60,'Captain Velgre has asked that I cook up some bait that we can use to bait the drakes and keep them away from the wind komodos. I should make the bait, then place it in the traps in the Vicious Breeding Grounds.',0,'I returned the bait to the traps, which should hopefully keep the drakes from getting too close to the wind komodos, at least for the time being.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(4740,'Digging For Grubs','Tradeskill','Unknown',60,60,'I met with a kerran scout named Darga Fleetpaw. She mentioned that she was with a group of explorers who had gone to the Vicious Breeding Grounds to research the appearance of a creature they called the wind komodo. She asked that I meet with Captain Velgre, who has been working to protect them.',0,'I was able to collect some grubs for Captain Velgre, which should help him with the first part of his plan.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(4741,'Fruit of Your Labor','Tradeskill','Unknown',60,60,'Shio Laugerwithe believes that the wind komodos are docile enough to accept a bridle and saddle, but they must be specifically made for these creatures. She has drawn up plans for a saddle she believes will be suitable for the komodos.',0,'I made the komodo saddle, and much to my surprise, Shio asked that I try it out first on one of the more amicable ones. It turned out very well, and now I have a wind komodo of my own.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(4742,'Warm on the Inside','Tradeskill','Unknown',60,60,'Shio Laugerwithe has asked that I make some meals for the wind komodos themselves, as it has been difficult for them to get their own food. She has given me a recipe that she believes will provide nourishment and comfort to the troubled wind komodos.',0,'I was able to make the meals for the wind komodos.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(4743,'Warm on the Outside','Tradeskill','Unknown',60,60,'Captain Velgre suggested that I speak to Shio Laugerwithe, who is working directly with the wind komodos to help ensure their survival. She apparently has a task that could use my skills. I should be able to find her up on the Wind Komodo Overlook.',0,'I was able to make a few egg warmers for the wind komodo eggs that I gathered.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(4744,'New Lands, New Profits','Tradeskill','Unknown',70,70,'I met Taskmaster Greeblentus in Teren\'s Grasp and he informed me of job opportunities he can connect me with if I can complete a task for him. ',0,'I have assisted Taskmaster Greeblentus as he requested. He has now vouched for me to work for the Bathezid or Riliss camps.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(4745,'A Far Seas Favor','Tradeskill','Unknown',80,80,'I met a rather timid Far Seas Trading Company representative who\'s been sent to investigate the rediscovered continent of Odus. I offered to bring her back some information about the current state of things in what used to be the city of Paineel.',0,'I investigated the changes in the city of Paineel and brought the information back to the Far Seas Trading Company representative.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(4746,'By Land, Air, or Teleporter','Tradeskill','Unknown',80,80,'I met a rather timid Far Seas Trading Company representative who\'s been sent to investigate the rediscovered continent of Odus. She has asked me to discover what forms of transportation may be available around the continent.',0,'I investigated the transportation availability around the continent, and brought the information back to the Far Seas Trading Company representative.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(4747,'I, Spybot','Tradeskill','Unknown',80,80,'I met a rather timid Far Seas Trading Company representative who\'s been sent to investigate the rediscovered continent of Odus. She has asked me to place a number of tinkered spybots at key places around the region in order to scout for more information about the continent.',0,'I placed the tinkered spybots to gather information for the Far Seas Trading Company representative.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
