(4749,'Insider Trading','Tradeskill','Unknown',81,81,'I met a rather timid Far Seas Trading Company representative who\'s been sent to investigate the rediscovered continent of Odus. She has asked me to get acquainted with the Craftkeepers of Paineel and learn more about the interests of each faction.',0,'I investigated the Craftkeepers of Paineel, and returned to the Far Seas Trading Company representative with the information.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(4750,'Remote Markets','Tradeskill','Unknown',83,83,'I met a rather timid Far Seas Trading Company representative who\'s been sent to investigate the rediscovered continent of Odus. The tinkered spybot I placed for her indicated there may be trade markets worth investigating on Kerra Isle. I should return and investigate.',0,'I traveled to Kerra Isle, and brought back what I learned to the Far Seas representative.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
