(5141,'Termite Troubles, Part I','Tradeskill','Unknown',200,100,'Varick is concerned about the reports of termites in the trees around Tupta. Besides causing Tupta harm, he is worried they might infest any trade shipments that leave Tupta and cause problems in other parts of Norrath. He has asked me to consult some specialists around the Shattered Lands for ideas on how to prevent this.',0,'I visited a number of insect specialists and obtained advice for Varick on how to control the Tupta termites.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5142,'Termite Troubles, Part II','Tradeskill','Unknown',200,100,'Varick is concerned about the reports of termites in the trees around Tupta. He has asked me to gather some possible ingredients to create a termite sterilization potion. ',0,'I obtained the ingredients for a termite sterilization potion.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5143,'Termite Troubles, Part III','Tradeskill','Unknown',200,100,'Varick is concerned about the reports of termites in the trees around Tupta. He has asked me to craft a large batch of termite sterilization potion in order to prevent the termite population from increasing.',0,'I crafted a large supply of potion for Varick.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5144,'Termite Troubles, Part IV','Tradeskill','Unknown',200,100,'Varick is concerned about the reports of termites in the trees around Tupta. He has manufactured a spray bottle to apply the potion I concocted onto the termites, in hopes of stopping them from breeding in Tupta.',0,'I applied the sterilization potion to the Tupta termites. This should prevent them from breeding new termites, and eventually the population in Tupta should die out.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
