(5150,'Zubzub\'s Munchies, Part I','Tradeskill','Unknown',200,100,'Zubzub has a lot of reports to write this week, but is having trouble concentrating! She\'s asked me to go and trap the ingredients for her favorite snack, so she\'ll have something to nibble on as she works. I need to catch them alive so they\'ll be as fresh as possible!',0,'I have trapped enough swamp rats to last Zubzub for a good long time.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5151,'Zubzub\'s Munchies, Part II','Tradeskill','Unknown',200,100,'Zubzub has a lot of reports to write this week, but is having trouble concentrating! She\'s asked me to go and gather the ingredients for her favorite snack, so she\'ll have something to nibble on as she works. ',0,'I have harvested swamp spices to flavor Zubzub\'s favorite snack.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5152,'Zubzub\'s Munchies, Part III','Tradeskill','Unknown',200,100,'Zubzub has a lot of reports to write this week, but is having trouble concentrating! She\'s asked me to go and gather spores from the fens sifters for her favorite snack, so she\'ll have something to nibble on as she works. This can be found on the bottom half of the Moors of Ykesha. ',0,'I have collected spores to season Zubzub\'s favorite snack.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5153,'Zubzub\'s Munchies, Part IV','Tradeskill','Unknown',200,100,'Zubzub has a lot of reports to write this week, but is having trouble concentrating! She\'s asked me to cook up a good supply of her favorite snack, so she\'ll have something to nibble on as she works. ',0,'I have cooked up enough spiced swamp rat to last Zubzub for a good long time.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
