(5157,'Buckle Down','Tradeskill','Unknown',200,100,'Liaison Zubzub reports that the demand for Grobb\'s fine metalwork has been so high that the trolls of Grobb are running short of metalwork for their own use. Zubzub has asked me to help by crafting polished buckles for Grobb. She has given me chunks of crude lead to get me started.',0,'Liaison Zubzub reported that the demand for Grobb\'s fine metalwork was so high that the trolls of Grobb were running short of metalwork for their own use. I assisted Zubzub by crafting a number of fine buckles for the trolls to use.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
