(5163,'Fighting Swamp Foot','Tradeskill','Unknown',200,100,'Liaison Mug mentioned that the guards and travelers around Firmroot Moot are vulnerable to a nasty fungal infection known as &quot;swamp foot&quot; caused by the constant damp. He would like to demonstrate the good will and fine quality goods that the Far Seas Trading Company can provide to help, so he has asked that I craft Ykeshan leather boots to protect the feet of the guards of Firmroot Moot guards.',0,'I assisted Liaison Mug by crafting some sturdy boots to protect the guards of Firmroot Moot from the nasty &quot;swamp foot&quot; infection. This should both build good will towards the Far Seas Trading Company, and demonstrate the valuable goods that they can offer in trade.','Quests/MultipleZones/Empty.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
