(5380,'Homemade Beetle Juice ','The Crypt of Betrayal','The Crypt of Betrayal',24,1,'I found a bottle of beetle juice while in the Crypt of Betrayal and it wasn\'t too bad. I decided to make some more for later consumption.',0,'It took many beetles, but I\'ve got plenty of beetle juice to last me, for a while anyway.','Quests/TheCryptofBetrayal/homemade_beetle_juice.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5381,'Gross Report ','The Crypt of Betrayal','The Crypt of Betrayal',24,1,'It\'s amazing what you can find down here in these catacombs. This appears to have been some sort of official notice or report or something. I wonder what would happen if I carried out its plan?',0,'Interesting... I guess it was worth it for the experience. I suppose it couldn\'t hurt to take on adventures such as these.','Quests/TheCryptofBetrayal/gross_report.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5382,'First Strike','The Crypt of Betrayal','The Crypt of Betrayal',27,1,'It\'s amazing what you can find down here in these catacombs. This appears to have been some sort of official notice or report or something. I wonder what would happen if I carried out its plan?',0,'Interesting... I guess it was worth it for the experience. I suppose it couldn\'t hurt to take on adventures such as these.','Quests/TheCryptofBetrayal/first_strike.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5383,'Destroy the Undead','The Crypt of Betrayal','The Crypt of Betrayal',24,1,'After holding a very old and soiled doll the urge to destroy the undead here in the Crypt of Betrayal had overcome me.',0,'After eliminating many of the undead in the Crypt of Betrayal the urge to destroy them left me.','Quests/TheCryptofBetrayal/destroy_the_undead.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5384,'Deadly Report','The Crypt of Betrayal','The Crypt of Betrayal',24,1,'It\'s amazing what you can find down here in these catacombs. This appears to have been some sort of official notice or report or something. I wonder what would happen if I carried out its plan?',0,'Interesting... I guess it was worth it for the experience. I suppose it couldn\'t hurt to take on adventures such as these.','Quests/TheCryptofBetrayal/deadly_report.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5385,'Crypt Jerky  ','The Crypt of Betrayal','The Crypt of Betrayal',24,1,'After tasting some dried bat meat that I found in the Crypt of Betrayal I decided to make my own bat jerky.',0,'I\'ve got plenty of bats now. These should last me for quite a while.','Quests/TheCryptofBetrayal/crypt_jerky.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5386,'Blowing off Steam','The Crypt of Betrayal','The Crypt of Betrayal',24,1,'While putting away a fishing hook I stuck myself pretty badly. What am I doing down here anyway? It stinks! I\'m tired and all these things just get in my way! I feel like killing everything that crosses my path, this sewer is just driving me nuts. Everything must die... now!',0,'You feel much better after blowing off a little steam.','Quests/TheCryptofBetrayal/blowing_off_steam.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5387,'Little Lost Minotaur','The Crypt of Betrayal','The Crypt of Betrayal',20,2,'A gnome in the Crypt of Betrayal, Torg Bramblehair, lost his pet minotaur. He thinks Spike will come back if there were fewer crypt tempests in the catacombs. I\'ve offered to make the passage safe for Spike.',2010009,'I have killed ten crypt tempests and need to tell Torg Bramblehair in the Crypt of Betrayal. With any luck, his pet minotaur Spike should be home soon.','Quests/TheCryptofBetrayal/little_lost_minotaur.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5388,'An Axe For All Ages','The Crypt of Betrayal','The Crypt of Betrayal',20,1,'I\'ve found a chipped and broken axe that appears to have once been a fine weapon. The markings on its remaining pieces seem to hint at old magical construction. If I could remake the axe it may be a fine weapon.',0,'I have found all the pieces and reassembled Sharpscar.','Quests/TheCryptofBetrayal/an_axe_for_all_ages.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5389,'Cellana\'s Locket','The Crypt of Betrayal','The Crypt of Betrayal',28,1,'I found a locket in the Crypt of Betrayal with a note in it asking me to take vengeance for someone who died there. The agonized essences were apparently responsible, so I am going to hunt them down.',0,'I have destroyed the agonized essences. I hope Cellana\'s spirit is able to rest in peace now.','Quests/TheCryptofBetrayal/cellanas_locket.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5390,'Strength of the Ire Minions','The Crypt of Betrayal','The Crypt of Betrayal',25,1,'The voice in the statue told me to seek out ire minions to strengthen my knowledge of battle. I have to admit that I\'m curious about this; I think I shall hunt them.',0,'I have slain the ire minions and feel that I have learned quite a bit from fighting them.','Quests/TheCryptofBetrayal/strength_of_the_ire_minions.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5391,'Gift of the Restless Corpses','The Crypt of Betrayal','The Crypt of Betrayal',21,1,'I have found a coin that claims that I will be rewarded for hunting restless corpses in the Crypt of Betrayal. I am curious as to how this is possible, so I am going to check this out.',0,'I have slain quite a few of the contorted forms, and definitely feel like I\'ve learned from the experience.','Quests/TheCryptofBetrayal/gift_of_the_restless_corpses.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5392,'Stolen Bones','The Crypt of Betrayal','The Crypt of Betrayal',28,1,'The agonized essences in the Crypt of Betrayal are created from parts of skeletal corpses. Their souls will never be able to rest in this undead state. I will slay them and put them to rest myself.',0,'I have slain quite a few of the agonized essences. I hope the souls of those who were used to create them rest peacefully.','Quests/TheCryptofBetrayal/stolen_bones.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5393,'The Hidden Wanted Poster','The Crypt of Betrayal','The Crypt of Betrayal',26,1,'I found a wanted poster seeking the heads of the Bloodsaber sentinels in the Crypt of Betrayal. I think I shall bring them to justice if I am able.',0,'I have helped the city of Qeynos by bring the Bloodsaber sentinels to justice.','Quests/TheCryptofBetrayal/the_hidden_wanted_poster.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5394,'Lore and Legend: Goblin','Lore and Legend','Multiple Zones',25,1,'I am searching for goblin body parts in order to gain knowledge about their kind.',0,'I have learned the secrets of the goblin.','Quests/MultipleZones/lore_and_legend_goblin.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
