(5435,'A Crumpled Note','The Down Below','The Down Below',10,1,'I found a note while exploring the catacombs. At first, I wasn\'t particularly interested, but it seems that once I finally opened it, the note contained some information as to a plot. I have decided to take this note to the Temple of Life and speak with the priests about it.',2220164,'I gave the note to Ian Turner at the Temple of Life.    He was quite happy that I brought it to his attention.','Quests/TheDownBelow/a_crumpled_note_priest.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5437,'Nyla\'s Pie Thief','Baubbleshire','Baubbleshire',5,1,'I\'ve offered to find Nyla\'s pie thief. She says the mysterious disappearance of a pie or two happens quite often around here, but I think I\'ll track this one down!',2380023,'I guess the thief was Lozoria over in the Deepmug tavern. Couldn\'t resist he said! Oh well, it seems like everything\'s all right though.','Quests/Baubbleshire/nylas_pie_thief.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5438,'Oro Root for Lozoria','Baubbleshire','Baubbleshire',5,1,'Lozoria Shinkicker would like me to go fetch some of the root the halflings have been using as a replacement for the jum jum. It still seems odd that the halflings have moved in here. They\'ve made a nice home for themselves with the gnomes, but I\'m sure they miss the vale a lot.',2380030,'I managed to collect the ten roots that Lozoria wanted for their new brew. He seems to like the ale it makes just fine, that\'s for certain! He\'s rather charming in an odd sort of way!','Quests/Baubbleshire/oro_rootforlozoria.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5439,'Cleaning Supplies for Findlebop','Baubbleshire','Baubbleshire',6,1,'Though the gnome named Findlebop was a bit rude, I offered to go fetch him something to clean up the gear he was working on. He mentioned the best thing would be a Mystail rat tail, so I guess I\'ll bring him one of those.',2380011,'I finally got a suitable tail to bring back to Smithy Findlebop, and it seemed to work out well for his purposes. He apologized for being so curt with me earlier too.','Quests/OakmystForest/cleaning_supplies_for_findlebop.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5440,'In Search of the Shrine of Estle','Baubbleshire','Baubbleshire',9,1,'Mirf Guinders of Baubbleshire has hired me to locate the Shrine of Estle within the Down Below, a section of the catacombs. When I find it I am to relay the location to him in exchange for a reward.',2380029,'I discovered the location of the Shrine of Estle within the Down Below. Having relayed this information to Mirf Guinders he has paid me for my service.','Quests/Baubbleshire/in_search_of_the_shrine_of_estle.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5441,'In Search of The Tower of the Order of Three','Baubbleshire','Baubbleshire',12,8,'Algan Tinmizer of Baubbleshire has hired me to find the ruins of an ancient mage tower. The tower was supposedly the original home of the first Qeynos mage society called the Order of Three.',2380037,'I discovered the location of the ancient ruins of the Order of Three. This information was passed on to Algan Tinmizer of Baubbleshire who in turn paid me for my service.','Quests/Baubbleshire/in_search_of_the_tower_of_the_order_of_three.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5442,'Picnic Basket for Yola','Baubbleshire','Baubbleshire',5,1,'Tapster Bregun over in the Deepmug Tavern asked me to bring a picnic basket to Yola over near the pond. It shouldn\'t take too much time to help him out.',2380028,'I delivered the picnic basket to Yola over at the pond. She was quite happy with the delivery, and Bregun was pleased when I came back.','Quests/Baubbleshire/picnic_basket_for_yola.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5443,'A Tattered Journal for Valean','Baubbleshire','Baubbleshire',8,1,'Ganla Dindlenod has hired me to deliver a tattered journal to Innkeeper Valean in Castleview Hamlet. He is going to attempt to decipher the elven words within the book.',2380022,'I delivered the tattered journal to Innkeeper Valean. I then informed Ganla Dindlenod that it will take some time to decipher the words. She was thankful and paid me for the deed.','Quests/Baubbleshire/a_tattered_journal_for_valean.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5444,'\'Lendel\'s Grand Lager\' Delivery','Baubbleshire','Baubbleshire',8,1,'Barkeep Deeppockets has tasked me with the delivery of a jug of Lendel\'s Grand Lager to the Frozen Tundra Tavern in Graystone Yard. I am to deliver it to Bartender Coppershot.',2380031,'I delivered the jug of Lendel\'s Grand Lager to Bartender Coppershot in Graystone. He then had me deliver a Fool\'s Gold stein to Barkeep Deeppockets. He was very pleased with the stein and paid me for my service.','Quests/Baubbleshire/lendels_grand_lager_delivery.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5445,'Potions for Jodi','Graystone Yard','Graystone Yard',6,1,'I have agreed to fetch a few potions for Jodi while she waits in line at the Graystone bank. I must find a merchant named Fuzzlecutter in Baubbleshire village in Qeynos.',2350022,'I delivered Fuzzlecutter\'s potions to Jodi in Graystone. She was very thankful and allowed me to keep the change.','Quests/GraystoneYard/potions_for_jodi.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5446,'Checking Up on Lolla\'s Kegs  ','Nettleville','Nettleville',8,1,'Lolla Cotgrove appeared to be in the middle of setting up a new tavern. She seemed quite busy at the moment with the preparations. I was asked by her to check on the progress of her new kegs that are being tinkered by Zipiff Clamorclang in the Baubbleshire.',2330012,'I reported back to Lolla Cotgrove that her tinkered kegs are coming along well and should be ready soon. She was pleased with the news and paid me with with an interesting concoction of hers and a few coins.','Quests/Nettleville/checking_up_on_lollas_kegs_.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5447,'Spindlecog\'s New Job ','Baubbleshire','Baubbleshire',24,1,'A gnomish tinkerer in the Baubbleshire named Spindlecog needs his stamping machine repaired. He\'s sent me out to gather components to fix it so he can stamp any government paperwork that comes his way.\r\n',2380016,'Sadly, Spindlecog\'s stamping device broke down again shortly after he tested it. Well, at least it worked for a little while.','Quests/Baubbleshire/spindlecogs_new_job_.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5448,'Half Pint Help','Ruins of Varsoon','Ruins of Varsoon',32,6,'I found the most peculiar little halfling imprisoned within the Ruins of Varsoon. Even more odd was his concern for completing his task of gathering components for his master, he had no regard for his own well being just his task at hand. So I decided to help him.',2560013,'I was able to gather all of the components that the halfling had lost down in the Ruins of Varsoon, and deliver them to his master. What a peculiar little halfling. I wonder how he is doing, and if he\'s made his way out of that cell yet?','Quests/RuinsofVarsoon/half_pint_help.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5449,'Acidic Liquid','Ruins of Varsoon','Ruins of Varsoon',28,3,'I found a strange liquid in a glass beaker. When I poured a bit out on the ground it bubbled a bit and ate away at the area surrounding it. It seems to be highly acidic in nature. Perhaps I can find someone to buy the liquid, a rogue or a locksmith...',2560133,'It seems that I found someone interested in the liquid... Rebik Sprocketrock was working on what seemed to be an un-pickable lock... but it wasn\'t impervious to the liquid. He bought the remainder of the liquid on the spot for quite a hefty amount of coin.','Quests/RuinsofVarsoon/acidic_liquid.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5450,'Inner Strength ','Ruins of Varsoon','Ruins of Varsoon',31,5,'The enchanted clays in Varsoon have the souls of a great warriors imbued in them. I will seek out these souls and make my own knowledge of battle stronger.',2560132,'I have slain the enchanted clays and feel stronger in my knowledge of battle techniques.','Quests/RuinsofVarsoon/inner_strength_.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5451,'Beware of Biting Books   ','Ruins of Varsoon','Ruins of Varsoon',32,6,'There are some enchanted tomes in the Ruins of Varsoon that can and will attack anyone who tries to read their contents. I have decided to destroy the enchanted tomes and be rid of their threat!',2560148,'I have destroyed the books as I have encountered them, I hope I have spared at least one unwary traveler the pain of their bite.','Quests/RuinsofVarsoon/beware_of_biting_books_.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5452,'Reservations for a Visitor','Castleview Hamlet','Castleview Hamlet',6,1,'Listalania has made the humble request that I make arrangements at the inn here in Castleview for her friend Taneran.',2360011,'I made arrangements with Innkeeper Valean for Taneran as per Listalania\'s instructions. Valean mentioned they will likely be wed soon... if what he says is true they do make a lovely couple.','Quests/CastleviewHamlet/reservations_for_a_visitor.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5453,'Valean\'s Stolen Books','Castleview Hamlet','Castleview Hamlet',8,1,'I need to seek out the stolen books within the Down Below section of the catacombs.',2360024,'I have discovered Innkeepers Valean\'s stolen books in the catacombs. I relayed the information to the Valean and he has given me a reward.','Quests/CastleviewHamlet/valeans_stolen_books.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5454,'Bupipa\'s New Amplificator','Castleview Hamlet','Castleview Hamlet',8,1,'Bupipa of Guryup asked me to take her bill of sale and pick up her new order. The gnome who tinkered it is Bizrinn Clamorclang and his shop resides in the Baubbleshire.',2360008,'I delivered the new Sonance Volume Amplificator to Bupipa and she paid me for the delivery. I hope the village of Castleview can forgive me if she ever gets it set up...','Quests/CastleviewHamlet/bupipas_new_amplificator.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5455,'Sword for Aadalian','Castleview Hamlet','Castleview Hamlet',6,1,'I\'ve been sent by Aadalian Farenair to check on his sword\'s status in the Castleview smithy run by a froglok named Froptub. It seems odd that a Koada\'dal would be interested in having a family sword inscribed by a froglok though.',2360019,'I suppose Aadalian was pleased with the work Froptub did. The mark was not to my own liking, but under the circumstances, I believe it was decent work.','Quests/CastleviewHamlet/sword_for_aadalian.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5456,'A Jug of Water for the Hole in the Wall ','Castleview Hamlet','Castleview Hamlet',8,1,'I was instructed by Bartender Bulurg to carry her jug into Oakmyst Forest. There I must find a waterfall and hold the jug beneath its cascading fall water. After I fill the jug I must return it to Bulurg.',2360021,'I filled the jug with fall water from the Oakmyst waterfall. I then gave the filled jug to Bartender Bulurg for the creation of a new high elf drink called \'Tunare\'s Finest.\' In return I received a small reward.','Quests/CastleviewHamlet/a_jug_of_water_for_the_hole_in_the_wall_.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5457,'New Etching Tool for Froptub\'s Smithy','Castleview Hamlet','Castleview Hamlet',6,1,'I met Arms Dealer Froptub who is getting behind on his orders. He asked me to find his apprentice, Boggi, who hasn\'t returned with his new etching tool yet. Hopefully, I\'ll find Boggi soon so that Froptub can get caught up on his work.',2360018,'I was able to help Arms Dealer Froptub get back to work by finding his apprentice Boggi and returning the new etching tool. I really doubt Boggi\'s leg injury story...','Quests/CastleviewHamlet/new_etching_tool_for_froptubs_smithy.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5458,'Bog Exploring for Grommluk','Castleview Hamlet','Castleview Hamlet',7,1,'Grommluk Oognee, a froglok swimming in Castleview\'s fountain, wanted to find a genuine swamp to swim in. I agreed to gather a sample of bog water for Grommluk from the middle of Peat Bog.',2360030,'I returned Grommluk\'s jar to him with swamp water I collected from the middle of Peat Bog. He paid me for my exploration services.','Quests/CastleviewHamlet/bog_exploring_for_grommluk.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5459,'Jewelry Delivery to Taneran','Castleview Hamlet','Castleview Hamlet',10,1,'Taneranthalis believes he will soon ask Listalania for her hand in marriage. He asked me if I would deliver a note to Tara Ironforge at the Jewel Box in North Qeynos and I obliged.',2360012,'I\'m sure Taneranthalis and Listalania will make a good couple when and if he decides the time is right. Perhaps one day their children will be able to visit his home city of Felwithe... indeed, maybe I will be able to see its white towers as well.','Quests/CastleviewHamlet/jewelry_delivery_to_taneran.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5460,'Proving Myself to Captain Gerathalas','Castleview Hamlet','Castleview Hamlet',8,1,'Captain Gerathalas wants me to prove how well I can take care of myself. I accepted an offer to slay putrid vermin in the Catacombs and bring back 6 putrid vermin tails to him. The captain was good natured about the ribbing but I really want to prove myself to him.',2360031,'I completed the task of collecting 6 putrid vermin tails for Captain Gerathalas. He seemed quite pleased with how well I did. He rewarded me with a piece of armor.','Quests/CastleviewHamlet/proving_myself_to_captain_gerathalas.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5461,'Food for Kruuprum','Castleview Hamlet','Castleview Hamlet',8,1,'Poor Kruuprum works so hard... he doesn\'t even have a chance to catch a decent bite to eat! I empathize with his plight, and have offered to fetch him some food. Although it will already be dead when he gets it, I think the food will suffice.',2360040,'Kruuprum was very thankful for the food I provided for him.','Quests/CastleviewHamlet/food_for_kruuprum.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5462,'A Sack of Rusty Daggers for Kruuprum','Castleview Hamlet','Castleview Hamlet',8,1,'Merchant Kruuprum of Castleview Hamlet has asked me to retrieve a bag of daggers from Mender Ironmallet in Graystone Yard.',2360040,'I retrieved a sack of rusted daggers for Merchant Kruuprum of Castleview Hamlet. I think he sells these inferior daggers.','Quests/CastleviewHamlet/a_sack_of_rusty_daggers_for_kruuprum.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5463,'Bat Fur for Fevalin ','Castleview Hamlet','Castleview Hamlet',10,1,'Merchant Fevalin is apparently running short of white fur. I\'m not certain what he uses it for, but he seems to want some pretty badly. So, I\'m off to go gather up some rare albino fur from the bats in the Caves.',418780,'Despite asking me for a second set of rare albino fur, I gathered all the bat fur Fevalin needed. Perhaps I am the stronger for it.','Quests/CastleviewHamlet/bat_fur_for_fevalin_.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5464,'Mystail Tails for Fevalin','Castleview Hamlet','Castleview Hamlet',4,1,'I have been asked by Merchant Fevalin of Castleview Hamlet to venture into Oakmyst Forest and collect six mystail yearling tails. I am supposed to return the with the tails.',2360039,'I collected all six mystail yearling tails for Merchant Fevalin. He has rewarded for my service.','Quests/CastleviewHamlet/mystail_tails_for_fevalin.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5465,'Badger Claws For Yanari ','Castleview Hamlet','Castleview Hamlet',7,9,'Yanari Cyellann needs vicious badger claws to continue work on her research. She says the badgers can be found in Oakmyst Forest.\r\n',2360047,'I delivered four vicious badger claws to Yanari Cyellann and she imbued a wand for me as payment.','Quests/CastleviewHamlet/badger_claws_for_yanari_.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5466,'Substance Extract for Yanari','Castleview Hamlet','Castleview Hamlet',6,1,'Yanari Cyellann has directed me to collect six vials of crypt substance extract. I will find crypt substances in a section of the catacombs called the Down Below.',2360047,'I have collected six vials of crypt substance extract and returned them to Yanari. She has paid me for my service.','Quests/CastleviewHamlet/substance_extract_for_yanari.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5467,'Gathering Elddar Leaves','Castleview Hamlet','Castleview Hamlet',6,1,'Scribe Bleemeb asked me to gather some leaves from the base of the tallest Elddar tree in the grove on the north end of Qeynos.',2360055,'I\'ve gone ahead and returned all the leaves I found around the base of the great Elddar tree to Scribe Bleemeb. It seems that Yanari will have enough for her next research forray.','Quests/CastleviewHamlet/gathering_elddar_leaves.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5468,'The Lost Book of Arbos','Castleview Hamlet','Castleview Hamlet',8,1,'I have agreed to retrieve the Book of Arbos from Faeadaen of Castleview Hamlet. I will return it to Scribe Bleemeb.',2360055,'I retrieved the Book of Arbos and returned it to Bleemeb. The book was written in a rare lost elven language.','Quests/CastleviewHamlet/the_lost_book_of_arbos.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5469,'Oh Deer Me','Castleview Hamlet','Castleview Hamlet',14,1,'Eireneith Alannia is a rather imperious high elf female in Castleview. I offered to assit her in thinning the glade deer population in Antonica.',2360036,'I\'ve done as Eireneith Alannia requested and brought down the glade deer population. She was nice enough to reward me for taking care of the task.','Quests/CastleviewHamlet/oh_deer_me.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5470,'Regrowth','Oakmyst Forest','Oakmyst Forest',8,1,'Adalin Emerael has asked for my help in cleansing certain trees in Oakmyst Forest. He was cleansing them himself when he claims was attacked by a gnoll and was unable to fend off the attack. He says the guards didn\'t believe him, but he is sure of what attacked him. He has asked that I go and continue his work. He has also asked that I keep my eyes open for any gnolls. If one does appear he has asked that I take its paw as proof for the guards.',1950004,'In helping Adalin Emerael cleanse some of the trees in Oakmyst Forest I was attacked by a gnoll. With the gnoll\'s paw as proof Lieutenant Charlin has agreed that a possible gnoll threat needs to be looked in to.','Quests/OakmystForest/regrowth.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5471,'Kualdin\'s Duet Offer','Willow Wood','Willow Wood',8,1,'I met Kualdin Swoonsong in the Willow Wood. He spoke of wanting to hold a concert when a hall is available. He asked if I would take an offer to Bupipa Guryup to see if she was interested in joining him for the duets. He said I could find her In Castleview.',2370015,'I told Kualdin that Bupipa was interested in the offer but she required at least one solo. Kualdin said he could fit her solo in somewhere between his second and fifth solo. I hope the wood elf can put on a good show.','Quests/TheWillowWood/kualdins_duet_offer.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5472,'Two Wrongs Do Not Make a Right','The Crypt of Betrayal','The Crypt of Betrayal',26,6,'I have found a note on one of the undead within the Crypt of Betrayal. It appears that he once owned a pair of short blades he was obsessed with. Before he was to be hanged for his crimes it appears he took the blades apart and had the pieces hidden. I believe he was buried with at least one so it may still be found down here if I could find his original grave.',0,'I have done all I needed and have remade the twin blades of Scorn and Shame.','Quests/TheCryptofBetrayal/two_wrongs_do_not_make_a_right.lua',0,1,0,0,0);
INSERT INTO `quests` VALUES
(5473,'The Eldritch Staff','Ruins of Varsoon','Ruins of Varsoon',34,5,'I\'ve found a rather odd staff being held by one of the monstrosities within the halls of Varsoon. Made from a slate grey colored wood, its texture almost feels like flesh. The wood holds faint carvings that are imperceptible to the eye.',0,'I\'ve managed to bring this staff to \'life\'. Having destroyed a number of bound souls, the staff seemed to absorb all of these life forces. The staff now seems to be more powerful at this point.','Quests/RuinsofVarsoon/the_eldritch_staff.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5474,'Magnificent Machinery','The Forest Ruins','The Forest Ruins',7,1,'Poko Zing has asked for my help collecting up some of the abandoned machinery that litters the Forest Ruins. According to Poko, many of the parts are still functional and could be put to good use.',1960003,'One of the machine parts I found concerned Poko a great deal. He says it looks like Freeportian machinery. I took this news to Lieutenant Germain.','Quests/ForestRuins/magnificent_machinery.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5478,'Scavenger Rats','Willow Wood','Willow Wood',5,1,'I met Salinia Brooklily in the Willow Wood today. She is a druid who has an interest in the balance of nature. She told me that the presence of so many new people in Qeynos is causing a problem with the predators of the scavenger rats in the Peat Bog from hunting them to a healthy balance. She asked that I slay eight scavenger rats to help bring about a new balance.',2370043,'I\'ve slain eight scavenger rats in the Peat Bog. I hope that will help with the overpopulation of the rats there.','Quests/TheWillowWood/scavenger_rats.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5479,'Any Messages For Jendan? ','Willow Wood','Willow Wood',4,1,'I met Jendan Greenthorn in Willow Wood today. He said he is looking for his brother who should have arrived from the Queen\'s Colony. He asked that I would take a note to Innkeeper Yeoni asking if there were any messages left for him.',2370035,'I talked with Innkeeper Yeoni and told Jendan that she didn\'t have any messages for him.  She said that Jendan asks if he has any messages at least twice a day.  I hope Jendan hears from his brother soon.','Quests/TheWillowWood/any_messages_for_jendan_.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5480,'The Balance of Life','Willow Wood','Willow Wood',17,1,'I\'ve met a wood elf named Daryann Stormrider. She monitors the various wildlife in the area and reduces the numbers of predators or prey to keep them in balance. I\'ve offered to help her cull some of the creatures.',2370108,'I\'ve done what\'s necessary as a good steward of the lands. I\'ve learned that every animal must have its numbers managed or life\'s balance is upset. Daryann appreciated my help.','Quests/TheWillowWood/the_balance_of_life.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5481,'The Willow Wood Memorial','Willow Wood','Willow Wood',6,1,'I met a strong young woman today by the name of Rebeka Lori. She told me how she hopes that one day she will see her cousins come off the boat in Qeynos. She told me of a small memorial near the tunnel\'s end from the boat dock that the villagers of Willow Wood have started for relatives they have given up hope in seeing again. I would like to see this memorial.',2370022,'I found the memorial that Rebeka Lori spoke of. I would like to hold to the same hope that Rebeka has that I may see my friends again some day.','Quests/TheWillowWood/the_willow_wood_memorial.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5482,'Baynor\'s Bent Tongs','Willow Wood','Willow Wood',8,1,'Blacksmith Baynor in Willow Wood\'s smithy asked if I could take his bent tongs to Mender Ironmallet in Graystone Yard to get them repaired for him. He is a superstitious one, I would have just repaired them myself if smithing was my job.',2370021,'I took Baynor\'s tongs to Mender Ironmallet and he fixed them right up. I returned to Baynor and gave him the tongs back. He also gave me some coin for my trouble.','Quests/TheWillowWood/baynors_bent_tongs.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5483,'Vaughn\'s Stuff','The Forest Ruins','The Forest Ruins',10,1,'I offered to help Outlander Vaughn recover some of his stolen property. He says the Blackfurl deckhands stole his satchel that had contained many important items. I told him I would help him get his stuff back.',1960053,'I eventually found all of Outlander Vaughn\'s items. He was grateful and asked if I would help him with something else.','Quests/TheForestRuins/vaughns_stuff.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5484,'Letter for Hunter Forestdeep','The Forest Ruins','The Forest Ruins',8,1,'I\'ve already helped Vaughn get his gear back, I figure I might as well help out one more time. I\'m to take a letter to a hunter in the Willow Wood village, who goes by the name of Forestdeep.',190053,'I have delivered the letter to hunter Lathar.','Quests/TheForestRuins/letter_for_hunter_forestdeep.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5485,'Lost Spellbook Fragments','The Forest Ruins','The Forest Ruins',9,1,'I recovered one of the spellbook fragments that the Concordium is looking for. They seem to be all over the Forest Ruins.',2310071,'I returned the fragment of the spellbook for a reward to Amren Talbot at the Three Towers. It wasn\'t much, but at least it was something.','Quests/TheForestRuins/lost_spellbook_fragments.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5486,'Forest Ruins Volunteer','The Forest Ruins','The Forest Ruins',6,1,'Sergeant at Arms Uthros offered me a warning and some background on the forest ruins of Qeynos. As I am intent on staying in the area for a while, the good Sergeant asked for some assistance with the local vermin.',1960004,'I\'ve hunted a fair amount of local creatures; I\'m sure Sergeant Uthros is happy for the help.','Quests/TheForestRuins/forest_ruins_volunteer.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5487,'Snapper Shells','The Forest Ruins','The Forest Ruins',7,1,'Therven Senshun has asked me to collect some turtle shells from the Forest Ruins for him. He is working on refining a process he\'s created that smoothes out the turtle shells for ornamental use.',1960010,'I gave Therven the turtle shells he asked for. He was very thankful.\r\n','Quests/TheForestRuins/snapper_shells.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5488,'Far Seas Direct Requisition #FRN0378','The Forest Ruins','The Forest Ruins',6,1,'I have discovered a direct delivery Far Seas Requisition slip. The hunter charged with filling the order must have been slain. If I hunt down the creatures and fill the order I can deliver the order to the client, Merchant Grekin in Starcrest Commune.',0,'I filled the Far Seas Requisition and delivered the goods to the client in Starcrest Commune. I have been paid in full for this work, but the order was late.','Quests/TheForestRuins/far_seas_direct_requisition_frn0378.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5489,'Far Seas Direct Requisition #FRN0931','The Forest Ruins','The Forest Ruins',6,1,'I have discovered a direct delivery Far Seas Requisition slip. The hunter charged with filling the order must have been slain. If I hunt down the creatures and fill the order I can deliver the order to the client, Merchant Grekin in Starcrest Commune.',0,'I filled the Far Seas Requisition and delivered the goods to the client in Starcrest Commune. I have been paid in full for this work, but the order was late.','Quests/TheForestRuins/far_seas_direct_requisition_frn0931.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5490,'Deposit for Grekin','Starcrest Commune','Starcrest Commune',6,1,'I\'ve been hired by a merchant by the name of Grekin to deliver his daily deposit to the bank. It really is amazing how trusting everyone is here.',2340037,'I deposited Grekin\'s money in the local bank. His merchant tent was really very close to the bank after all; I hardly had any trouble finding it.','Quests/StarcrestCommune/deposit_for_grekin.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5491,'For Qeynos','The Forest Ruins','The Forest Ruins',7,1,'Elvic Garrett has asked that I help the Qeynos Guard. They have been trying to get more information about the Forest Ruins. Elvic says that a number of temporary campsites have been spotted around the area. He has asked that I inspect these camps and see if I can discover who has been setting them up.',1960007,'I found a gnollish book at one of the abandoned campsites. Lieutenant Germain was very concerned at the possibility of a gnollish presence in the Forest Ruins.','Quests/TheForestRuins/for_qeynos.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5492,'Uncover the Caches','The Forest Ruins','The Forest Ruins',10,1,'Lieutenant Germain has learned that caches with weapons, armor, and tools have been hidden around the Forest Ruins in the same manner as the camp that Del Varun found. He has asked that I find and destroy them.',1960005,'I have destroyed the gnoll caches within the Forest Ruins.','Quests/TheForestRuins/uncover_the_caches.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5493,'Lure','Forest Ruins','The Forest Ruins',11,1,'Lieutenant Germain\'s sources have discovered the leader of the gnoll presence in the Forest Ruins. The gnoll\'s name is Malox. Germain says he can be lured out by setting fire to the hidden gnoll encampment north of the pond on the west side of the ruins.',1960005,'I have slain Malox and taken his head. Lieutenant Germain says that we were lucky that we stopped them when we did, but that there may still be much work ahead of us.','Quests/TheForestRuins/lure.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5494,'Unnatural Causes','The Forest Ruins','The Forest Ruins',7,1,'Ilaen Lilac is concerned at the number of dead deer in the Forest Ruins. She has asked that I inspect some of the fallen bodies to see if I can determine what caused their deaths.',1960059,'I found gnoll teeth in the bodies of one of the dead animals. I gave this information to Lieutenant Germain at Ilaen\'s request.','Quests/TheForestRuins/unnatural_causes.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5495,'Ash Covered Necklace','Ruins of Varsoon','Ruins of Varsoon',27,1,'The necklace I found on the corpse of the dead adventurer had a maker\'s inscription on the clasp. It said it was made in the Willow Wood by Mossclean. If I\'m ever back that way, I\'ll take it to this Mossclean and see what they can make of this necklace.',2370019,'The travel was well worth the effort. The ash covered necklace was actually a black pearl necklace. Like I said, it was well worth the trouble.','Quests/RuinsofVarsoon/ash_covered_necklace.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5496,'Last Place They\'d Look','Ruins of Varsoon','Ruins of Varsoon',27,1,'Near the entrance of the Ruins of Varsoon I found a journal purposely abandoned by a very unfortunate adventurer. By the condition of the journal it appears to have been left here a while ago. I have little faith that the author of this journal is still alive, but while here with in the Ruins of Varsoon I will keep an eye out for this misfortunate adventurer.',0,'I may have found the author of the journal. There was an old necklace within the remains of the corpse.','Quests/RuinsofVarsoon/last_place_theyd_look.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5498,'Shrillers for Tillheel','Graystone Yard','Graystone Yard',6,1,'I have agreed to help Assistant Tillheel in the alchemy shop of Graystone Yard. He needs me to slay five juvenile shrillers in the Down Below and collect their wings.',2350056,'I collected and delivered five sets of shriller wings to Tillheel. He was very grateful.','Quests/GraystoneYard/shrillers_for_tillheel.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5499,'Elixir for Tillheel','Nettleville','Nettleville',8,1,'Alchemist Garion Dunam has hired me to deliver an elixir to Assistant Tillheel in Graystone Yard.',2330027,'I delivered the elixir of mistmire to Assistant Tillheel. I then returned his payment to Alchemist Garion Dunam. Garion allowed me to keep the change and even threw in a bag as payment for my service.','Quests/Nettleville/elixir_for_tillheel.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5500,'Return the Tome for Viceheart','Graystone Yard','Graystone Yard',6,1,'Barry Viceheart has asked me to take a tome back to a scribe\'s shop in Castleview Hamlet, a village in Qeynos.',2350024,'I returned the tome to Bleemeb in Castleview Hamlet.','Quests/GraystoneYard/return_the_tome_for_viceheart.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5501,'Armor for Watchman Fiercecry','Graystone Yard','Graystone Yard',6,1,'I met a member of the Graystone Watch, a barbarian by the name of Fiercecry. He bade me pick up a suit of armor he had been fitted for by a smith named Snowboot.',2350015,'I\'ve picked up the suit of armor from armorsmith Snowboot.','Quests/GraystoneYard/armor_for_watchman_fiercecry.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5502,'Snake Skin for Soulforge','Graystone Yard','Graystone Yard',10,1,'Weaponsmith Soulforge needs some snake skins for his swords, so after I opened my big mouth, he sent me out snake hunting. With my luck, they\'ll probably be venomous.',2350013,'I guess the hunting wasn\'t so bad. I\'m none the worse for wear; however, the snakes are. Soulforge stiffed me a bit on the price for them, just because they were damaged. I think it will make the weapons look more authentic!','Quests/GraystoneYard/snake_skin_for_soulforge.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5503,'Rat Man Bloodsaber Crusade','Graystone Yard','Graystone Yard',10,1,'Watcher Curmogliel in Graystone has instructed me to smite four Ratonga Bloodsabers in the catacombs. I shall prove my faith in the silent gods.',235001,'I have slain the Bloodsabers and shown my faith to Watcher Curmogliel.','Quests/GraystoneYard/rat_man_bloodsaber_crusade.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5504,'Inspect the Oakmyst Forest Gate','Graystone Yard','Graystone Yard',6,1,'Captain Salomar has asked me to check the Oakmyst Forest Gate in Graystone Yard. It may be toppled.',2350043,'I checked the Oakmyst Forest Gate and reported back to Captain Salomar. The gate was intact.','Quests/GraystoneYard/inspect_the_oakmyst_forest_gate.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5505,'New Fishing Pole for Brice','Graystone Yard','Graystone Yard',6,1,'Brice Strongmend has tasked me with retrieving a new fishing pole to replace his old one while he holds his spot on the docks. That old pole of his looks so beat up, it\'s a wonder he can catch any fish at all.',2350005,'I purchased a new fishing pole for Brice Strongmend with the money he gave me. He was so impressed with it that he let me keep what money was left over.','Quests/GraystoneYard/new_fishing_pole_for_brice.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5506,'Dane Steelfist, Bureaucrat','Graystone Yard','Graystone Yard',15,1,'I encountered a dwarf named Dane Steelfist, a new bureaucrat in Graystone Yard. He\'s pretty busy learning the ropes and I agreed to help him out with one or two of his tasks.',2350037,'Dane Steelfist still has a lot to learn about being a bureaucrat, but I feel good that I helped him out -- without having to make a campaign contribution, either!','Quests/GraystoneYard/dane_steelfist_bureaucrat.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5507,'New Fishing Spot for Ubani','Graystone Yard','Graystone Yard',10,1,'Ubani has been having some poor luck in Graystone Yard. He can\'t seem to catch any fish at all. I offered to help him out in whatever way I could, and he asked that I go check the waters at the harbor near the pier.',2350028,'I brought Ubani some great news, the harbor waters around the pier are loaded with fish! Schools and schools of them flourish in the waters there. I\'m sure Ubani will have better luck if he doesn\'t get escorted from the city before he catches some.','Quests/GraystoneYard/new_fishing_spot_for_ubani.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5508,'Graystone Bank Tally Delivery','Graystone Yard','Graystone Yard',6,1,'Banker Dori asked if I would be so kind as to run an errand for her. She needed a tally delivered to the main branch of the Qeynos Exchange in the harbor district.',2350026,'I\'ve returned to Dori with the letter from banker Newbury about the impending inventory of her bank. It seems to me that if she hired better help than Jalan, she\'d be doing herself a favor.','Quests/GraystoneYard/graystone_bank_tally_delivery.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5509,'The Dusty Blue Stone','Nettleville','Nettleville',25,6,'I examined the blue stone that Vida Sweeps gave me. It feels very strange, I haven\'t seen anything like it before. I should probably follow Vida\'s advice and ask a mineral expert about it.',6631,'After asking a few different people to look at the stone it turns out it is the adornment of an ancient undead slaying sword called Ghoulbane.','Quests/Nettleville/the_dusty_blue_stone.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5510,'Inform Tracker Kelnis','Graystone Yard','Graystone Yard',8,1,'I have agreed to help Pathfinder Silentstride. I must inform Tracker Kelnis of her knowledge of a gravesite belonging to a Holly Windstalker.',2350014,'I have informed Kelnis and reported back to Silentstride. She was grateful. They are seeking a gravesite of Holly Windstalker.','Quests/GraystoneYard/inform_tracker_kelnis.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5511,'The Stein of Moggok:  It Can Be Rebuilt...','Heritage','City of Freeport',40,3,'I learned of an old item that was last seen in the Age of Turmoil while talking to Rumdum Clurg in the Seafarer\'s Roost. I think I\'ll travel to the Feerrott and see what I can turn up concerning the Stein of Moggok.',1280030,'I was able to rebuild the Stein of Moggok! I\'ll be sure not to mention this to Rumdum...','Quests/CityofFreeport/the_stein_of_moggok_it_can_be_rebuilt.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5512,'Double Cross & Revenge','Wailing Caves','Wailing Caves',17,1,'Ariana had sacrificed her freedom in exchange for the orcs not attacking her people\'s camp. The orcs have lied to her and now I must warn her husband of the planned attack, but first I must buy her people some time. I will slay the advisor Kre\'lak; this should slow them down and give me enough time to warn Ariana\'s husband Orwen in the Commonlands.',2580021,'I was successful in each of my tasks. I took care of the orc advisor and warned her husband. Owren was in the midst of fashioning another blade and gave it to me for my continued service.','Quests/WailingCaves/double_cross__revenge.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5513,'In Search of Spiritkeepers','In Search of Spiritkeepers','City of Freeport',17,2,'Lieutenant Darrius of the Freeport Militia has hired me to venture into the depths of Wailing Caves where I am to hunt down no less than some form of caster called a spiritkeeper. Their existence could all just be a myth, but I may as well check it out.',5590120,'I was hired by the Freeport Milita officer, Lieutenant Darrius, to hunt down rumored spiritkeepers in the Wailing Caves. I slew no less than five Ree spiritkeeprs and returned with their scalps as proof. For this service, I was paid handsomely.','Quests/CityofFreeport/in_search_of_spiritkeepers.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5514,'Pelle\'s Manuscript','The Elddar Grove','The Elddar Grove',10,1,'I\'ve met a rather intriguing halfling. He is apparently the proprietor of the tavern in the Elddar forest, but with the halfling penchant for stretching the truth, he could just be a patron! At any rate, he bade me deliver a manuscript to a wizard friend of his in southern Qeynos.',2070067,'After I spoke with Rune Shimmerstar, he sent me off to go speak with yet another of their old company. I was relieved to find Aundor only wished me to return Pelle\'s copy of the book and not play messenger any longer. When I returned to Pelle, he did have a rather nice bracelet for me!','Quests/TheElddarGrove/pelles_manuscript.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5515,'Visiting the Windstalker Grave','The Elddar Grove','The Elddar Grove',15,1,'Venylle, a ranger lookout stationed in the Elddar Grove, told me of the grave of Holly Windstalker. She says the rumor is that Holly may have risen from it and now walks the hills again. Maybe there will be some clues at her grave site. Venylle told me that the gravesite can be found in Antonica, by following the aqueduct from Qeynos to Windstalker Village and that the gravestone is overlooking the village.',2070049,'I found Holly Windstalker\'s grave on the hill overlooking Windstalker Village. I didn\'t see any sign of the grave being disturbed though, I did remove a dirty mug near the site. The rangers may just be overly cautious as of late.','Quests/TheElddarGrove/visiting_the_windstalker_grave.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5516,'Unnatural Lesson','The Elddar Grove','The Elddar Grove',14,8,'Lookout Venylle\'s position puts her in many dangerous situations, some natural, some unnatural. She said to further understand I should experience the unnatural first hand, and that I should lay to rest the unnatural decaying skeletons and risen protectors near some mausoleum out in Antonica. Lookout Venylle said that I can find this mausoleum by heading to the northwest from the northern gates of Qeynos.',2070049,'I\'ve put to rest the decaying skeletons and risen protectors that Lookout Venylle had requested. Venylle told me that this was but one of many lessons to come, I have a feeling she\'s right.','Quests/TheElddarGrove/unnatural_lesson.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5517,'Hawk Hunt','The Elddar Grove','The Elddar Grove',10,1,'I\'ve offered to assist Gregor Earthstride, a ranger in the Elddar Grove, in retrieving a number of hawk feathers for his fletchings. I believe the hawks are to be found in the forest ruins just outside the Baubbleshire.',2070010,'Gregor Earthstride was grateful for the hawks I downed for him. I found it hard to bite my tongue when he mentioned that he could not find the birds he needed... after all, he is a ranger!','Quests/TheElddarGrove/hawk_hunt.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5518,'Does the Underforge Exist?','Antonica','Antonica',15,1,'Kinamer Galemaul, a dwarf smith in Antonica, spoke of a mythical smithy named Underforge that was said to reside within Stormhold, home of the legendary Knights of Thunder. He said that the Underforge was used to supply the Knights with all of their magical equipment. He doesn\'t put much faith in the stories from crypt raiders that Stormhold has been discovered, but did ask me to let him know if the Underforge does exist.',120278,'I found the Underforge within Stormhold and returned to Kinamer Galemaul. The forge wasn\'t as impressive as legend made it out to be. He was surprised and elated by the news.','Quests/Antonica/does_the_underforge_exist.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5519,'Unraveling the Bloodsaber Plots','Antonica','Antonica',20,8,'Continuing from what Wesaelen Brookshadow has found, my journey appears to be spiraling towards a confrontation with the Bloodsabers. Though the story I\'ve managed to piece together thus-far has been largely incomplete.',120069,'Now sure of the Bloodsaber\'s return, I am compelled to stop them from becoming a threat to our fair city of Qeynos once again. The War of Plagues will not return. There will be no future for this evil cult.','Quests/Antonica/unraveling_the_bloodsaber_plots.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5520,'The Half Eaten Order Slip ','Antonica','Antonica',12,1,'I found a slip with the name Walcott on it. I will find the owner and see if he needs any assistance with anything.',120078,'I aided Farmer Walcott in his fight against evil scarecrows in his fields. I slew two of the creatures for him.','Quests/Antonica/the_half_eaten_order_slip.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5521,'Arrows for Fanthis','The Elddar Grove','The Elddar Grove',10,1,'Fanthis tasked me with retrieving arrows from Master Archer Nightbow at the archery shop on the northeast side of the grove called In-Range.',2070080,'I restocked Patrolman Fanthis\' supply of arrows with the assistance of the local bowyer, Aysabelle Nightbow. To see such a display of courtesy between shop keeper and customer is wonderful in these times.','Quests/TheElddarGrove/arrows_for_fanthis.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5522,'Lord Grimrot\'s Scythe','Access Quest','Antonica',18,1,'I met a dwarf named Ignar Steadirt near the Qeynos\' Claymore monument. He thinks I\'m the answer to his prayers for help in the battle against the undead! I\'ve never been the answer to anyone\'s prayers before.',120414,'Ignar Steadirt is still frustrated that he has to remain at the Claymore monument, but he was very grateful for living the battles vicariously through my reports. It has been my pleasure.','Quests/Antonica/lord_grimrots_scythe.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5523,'Nightbow\'s Deposit','The Elddar Grove','The Elddar Grove',10,1,'I\'m making the daily deposit for Master Archer Nightbow with the Qeynos Exchange. She told me to go to Grisvane Stonearm to deliver the coin - he\'s the dwarf she usually deals with while banking at the Exchange.',2070011,'I\'ve deposited In-Range\'s daily earnings with the bank, where I met a dwarf named Grisvane. The proprietor of the shop, Aysabelle Nightbow, paid me for running the coins over to the bank.','Quests/TheElddarGrove/nightbows_deposit.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5524,'Recipe for Duvo','The Elddar Grove','The Elddar Grove',10,1,'Scribe Duvo was too busy to go retrieve a recipe from Penny Goodhearth, a cook for the Ironforge family in northern Qeynos, so I offered, or rather, I was recruited to fetch the recipe for him.',2070044,'I found Penny Goodhearth at Voleen\'s Bakery in North Qeynos, and have undoubtedly met the busiest two halflings ever. Duvo was so busy that he couldn\'t even pick up a recipe! He seemed ecstatic about the recipe, and thanked me whole-heartedly for its retrieval.','Quests/TheElddarGrove/recipe_for_duvo.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5525,'Message for Zwena','The Elddar Grove','The Elddar Grove',10,1,'I\'ve found myself a third party to a forbidden love between Lunaru, a monk of the Sanctum, and the troubador Zwena. I\'m to deliver a message about what I can only assume is a secret tryst.',2070069,'I\'ve delivered the message from Initiate Lunaru to Zwena. She seemed quite pleased with the message.','Quests/TheElddarGrove/message_for_zwena.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5526,'Helanni\'s Golden Engraved Arrow','The Elddar Grove','The Elddar Grove',10,1,'Helanni Firewyng has recently won an archery tournament, which was one of her goals in life. She would like to share her good fortune with an old friend of hers that she doesn\'t see too often. She has asked me to take her golden engraved arrow and give it to Leona Ward in South Qeynos.',0,'I gave Helanni\'s golden engraved arrow to her friend Leona Ward. It is a small way for Leona to know that Helanni accomplished one of her aspirations.','Quests/TheElddarGrove/helannis_golden_engraved_arrow.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5527,'Letter for Tabby','The Elddar Grove','The Elddar Grove',10,1,'Initiate Tara would like a letter delivered to Tabby Copperpot. She didn\'t say what the letter was for, but she sounded like it was urgent. She said that Tabby Copperpot can be found in South Qeynos.',2070085,'I have delivered a letter for Initiate Tara to Tabby, and Tabby was very excited to finally hear from Tara.','Quests/TheElddarGrove/letter_for_tabby.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5528,'A Frontierslady\'s Task','Antonica','Antonica',15,1,'I met a ranger or outlander named Dancer. She asked me to perform a few errands for her.',120410,'I performed some errands for the outlander named Dancer. She would not mention what it was all about, but it was very curious.','Quests/Antonica/a_frontiersladys_task.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5529,'Bryson\'s Bow','The Elddar Grove','The Elddar Grove',10,1,'Bryson would like me to retrieve a bow he has on order with Carpenter Paddock down at the harbor. With the time he\'s spent practicing he has neglected to retrieve it himself.',2070013,'Bryson was pleased to have his new bow and was kind enough to pay me for my time and effort.','Quests/TheElddarGrove/brysons_bow.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5530,'Battle with the Timberclaws','Antonica','Antonica',14,1,'Dancer has accepted my offer to save Archer Woods. She has instructed me to stop the gnolls in and around the woods.',120410,'I fought valiantly against the gnolls in Archer Woods. Dancer has given me her necklace. Upon examination I see that her name must truly be Verona. She must trust me to pass this along.','Quests/Antonica/battle_with_the_timberclaws.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5531,'Oakheart\'s Report','The Elddar Grove','The Elddar Grove',10,1,'Pathfinder Oakheart required the delivery of a patrol report to the ranger guildmaster, Rysian Gladewalker. He mentioned that I will find Rysian in Arbos, the great Elddar tree in the middle of the grove.',2070022,'I delivered the daily patrol report to Rysian Gladewalker, at Pathfinder Oakheart request. Oakheart was relieved he didn\'t have to diminish his resources to deliver the report.','Quests/TheElddarGrove/oakhearts_report.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5532,'Killing Fire Beetles','Qeynos Harbor','Qeynos Harbor',10,5,'Carpenter Paddock wants me to kill the fire beetles out in Antonica, because they eat the lumber they use to build ships with. Paddock wants twenty of their carcasses. Seems to me I\'ve also heard these things called \"klicnik mites\" around here.',2210153,'I\'ve killed many fire beetles and gathered twenty carcasses. Paddock was very pleased, and the reward was well worth my time and effort.','Quests/QeynosHarbor/killing_fire_beetles.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5533,'A Lonely Tree','The Elddar Grove','The Elddar Grove',38,6,'Something is wrong with the Heartwood Tree of the Elddar Grove, a young Elddar pine known as Arbos. I must investigate.',2070066,'I discovered a young Elddar tree in the Enchanted Lands named Arddin. I have reported its existence to Warble Wildmane. I am sure he and the Elddar Alliance shall see to the well being of the young tree.','Quests/TheElddarGrove/a_lonely_tree.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5534,'Papers from Fhara','North Qeynos','North Qeynos',10,1,'Fhara\'s business partner is waiting for some important papers. Fhara has charged me with getting them to him. Her business partner Trevor can be found in South Qeynos.',2220229,'I delivered some important business letters from Fhara to her partner Trevor.','Quests/NorthQeynos/papers_from_fhara.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5535,'Dwarven Fish Delivery','North Qeynos','North Qeynos',10,1,'Gretta Steinbeard needed someone to pick up a load of fresh fish from Umli Grayfist, a dwarf who can be found on the docks in the Qeynos Harbor. I\'m worried that the fish will already be ripe with age by the time I get there.',2220094,'Fortunately, the fish didn\'t smell too badly, and I was able to return them to Gretta Steinbeard at Irontoe\'s East before they turned my stomach.','Quests/NorthQeynos/dwarven_fish_delivery.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5536,'Blank Pages','North Qeynos','North Qeynos',10,1,'Andrea Dovesong would like some parchment so she may scribe her latest sonata. She asked me to go to the Elddar Grove and get some parchment from Scribe Duvo.',2220111,'Scribe Duvo was happy to oblige Andrea with as much parchment as she may need. Andrea was grateful for the errand and rewarded my efforts.','Quests/NorthQeynos/blank_pages.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5537,'Bear Fashion','North Qeynos','North Qeynos',10,8,'Rachael Clothspinner has been waiting on an order from the Far Seas Trading Company, but has not yet received it. She said if I fill the order of four fine pelts from Oakmyst great bears that she\'ll pay me for the order.',2220060,'I\'ve filled Rachael\'s order and she mentioned that I could make a decent living filling unfulfilled Far Seas Trading Company orders.','Quests/NorthQeynos/bear_fashion.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5538,'Dyes for Danielle','North Qeynos','North Qeynos',10,1,'Danielle Clothspinner requested that I seek out Khalil\'Mun, the proprietor of The Herb Jar in southern Qeynos to purchase two tubs of dye for her. She seemed so desperate, I couldn\'t resist helping her.',2220061,'After returning with the dyes from Khalil\'Mun\'s shop, Danielle was able to complete her work for the day. I found myself happy to do the task for her, and the pay for the pick-up wasn\'t too shabby either.','Quests/NorthQeynos/dyes_for_danielle.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5539,'Some Nice Bear Hides','North Qeynos','North Qeynos',10,1,'Danielle Clothspinner is pretty frustrated from having so much work. On top of that she doesn\'t usually get the best materials to work with all the time. I have offered to get some preserved bear hides for her to work with. I am sure I can find some bears in Antonica that will work for this.',2220061,'I have helped Danielle get four preserved bear hides. So when she is done with her normal sewing and dying she can make some really high quality products to sell.','Quests/NorthQeynos/some_nice_bear_hides.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5540,'Delivery for Fhara','North Qeynos','North Qeynos',7,1,'Baker Voleen asked if I could deliver a basket of goodies to her friend Fhara Hanford over at her furniture shop. The contents of the basket do smell really good though... I hope I can make it all the way there without sampling the contents!',2220025,'The baker who sent me out to Fhara Hanford\'s shop to deliver a basket of pastries gave me some loaves of bread and a few coins for managing to take her basket of goods to Fhara\'s Furniture without devouring its contents.','Quests/NorthQeynos/delivery_for_fhara.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5541,'Delivery for Thardrin','North Qeynos','North Qeynos',10,1,'I was accosted by a dwarf while I was peeking around the Qeynos Cache. After a slight misunderstanding, he sent me to deliver supplies to Sneed Galliway.',2220120,'After lugging that heavy crate of supplies from Thardrin to Sneed\'s Trading Post, my arms burned. It\'s just too bad the pay for it didn\'t load me down more than it did.','Quests/NorthQeynos/delivery_for_thardrin.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5542,'Delivery for the Temple of Life','North Qeynos','North Qeynos',10,1,'Gavin Ironforge tasked me with delivering a small box of silver etchings to the Temple of Life. I am to take the package to Rowena, a medic in North Qeynos and no one else.',2220127,'Medic Rowena showed great pleasure in the fact that the etchings from Gavin Ironforge were delivered a day early. Surely the blessings of Rodcet Nife shall follow me should the gods ever return to our world.','Quests/NorthQeynos/delivery_for_the_temple_of_life.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5543,'Gnoll Extermination','North Qeynos','North Qeynos',12,1,'I\'ve been tasked by Sir Laughlin to kill a number of the gnolls roaming Antonica. Apparently they\'ve gotten out of hand just outside the city, and need to have their numbers culled.',2220024,'Sir Laughlin commended me on my battle prowess! I\'ve taken my first steps into the greater world beyond the city. Today Qeynos, tomorrow the world!','Quests/NorthQeynos/gnoll_extermination.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5544,'Sword Delivery for Noelle','North Qeynos','North Qeynos',10,1,'Noelle Dering ordered a fine longsword from the Call to Arms, an establishment owned and operated by the Ironforge family. The proprietor, Walter Channing, asked if I would be kind enough to deliver the sword to her in the tavern, Irontoe\'s East.',2220053,'It appears that all is right. Noelle Dering was very pleased with both the quality of the sword and the timeliness of the delivery. Walter Channing seemed quite happy with my haste with delivering the sword as well.','Quests/NorthQeynos/sword_delivery_for_noelle.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5545,'Vermin\'s Plague','North Qeynos','North Qeynos',15,1,'I have volunteered to assist Elsabethia Hartsunder in the Temple of Life with her research. I must gather infected specimen from each of the three species of vermin from the Vermin\'s Snye catacomb that are known to carry the infection.',2220141,'I volunteered to assist Elsabethia Hartsunder in the Temple of Life with her research. I was able to gather the infected specimens and return them to her.','Quests/NorthQeynos/vermins_plague.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5546,'Performer Courier Service','North Qeynos','North Qeynos',10,1,'I happened across a performer named Dawson Magnificent in need of assistance. Unfortunately he\'s running late, and would like me to inform the proprietor of Fish\'s Alehouse in Qeynos Harbor that he\'ll be late.',2220113,'I spoke with Innkeeper Galsway regarding Dawson Magnificent\'s tardiness. He didn\'t seem displeased, though he was disappointed to hear that his favorite performers would be late.','Quests/NorthQeynos/performer_courier_service.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5547,'Visiting the Claymore Monument','North Qeynos','North Qeynos',11,1,'I spoke with a bard named Andrea Dovesong near the Qeynos Claymore Monument within North Qeynos. She told me she sang songs of the sword\'s storied history and told me of a second monument to the blade out in the Antonican hills. I think I\'d like to see this monument.',2220111,'I found the second Qeynos Claymore Monument not too far from the city of Qeynos itself. There were gnolls along the way, but not more than I could handle.','Quests/NorthQeynos/visiting_the_claymore_monument.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5548,'Sneed\'s Supplies','North Qeynos','North Qeynos',10,1,'Merchant Sneed Galliway has been pretty busy lately so I offered to pick up the supplies he has on order with Blacksmith Hegrenn in South Qeynos.',2220027,'I helped Sneed Galliway by getting his order from Blacksmith Hegrenn. I even earned some coin in the process.','Quests/NorthQeynos/sneeds_supplies.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5549,'Oakmyst Minerals','South Qeynos','South Qeynos',10,1,'Blacksmith Hegrenn would like me to verify some gossip she had overheard at some tavern. She would like me to find some of this mineral that is supposed to be inside the Oakmyst royal defenders out in the Oakmyst Forest. She would like three pieces.',2310038,'There was more to all of this than just gossip. Sure enough I found an unknown mineral. Hegrenn was quite pleased, but asked me to keep the news to myself.','Quests/SouthQeynos/oakmyst_minerals.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5550,'The Age of Rediscovery','North Qeynos','North Qeynos',15,1,'I\'ve agreed to help a historian by the name of Demini in Qeynos. He\'s looking for some pages to a book he bought from a passing traveler. If I find these pages for him, he claimed he\'d reward me for my work.',2220086,'I\'ve been able to collect the pages of the book that Scholar Demini was searching for.','Quests/NorthQeynos/the_age_of_rediscovery.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5551,'The Scholar\'s Search','North Qeynos','North Qeynos',17,5,'I\'ve agreed to help Scholar Demini once again, this time in search of the author of his newly acquired journal. I\'m hoping this won\'t take too long.',2220086,'I\'ve given Demini the bad news that the scholar he was searching for had met a bad fate at the hands of some bandits.','Quests/NorthQeynos/the_scholars_search.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5552,'Never Judge a Book By Its Cover','North Qeynos','North Qeynos',19,1,'Having helped Scholar Demini several times in the past already, I\'ve now agreed to help him find the Sage of Ages... or what\'s left of him.',2220086,'I didn\'t find the Sage of Ages, but was able to confirm that he wasn\'t killed by the bandits. His note made no mention of his scholar escort, however.','Quests/NorthQeynos/never_judge_a_book_by_its_cover.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5553,'Flight of the Sage ','North Qeynos','North Qeynos',21,5,'It might not be too late to find the Sage of Ages. If I can find him in time, not only can I meet him myself, I can even introduce him to Scholar Demini, too!',2220086,'The Sage of Ages has managed to book passage on a ship and set sail across the ocean. Though I\'m glad he made it safely away from the perils he faced, I\'m rather disappointed I never got a chance to meet him.','Quests/NorthQeynos/flight_of_the_sage_.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5554,'A Visit to the Tower of the Oracles','South Qeynos','South Qeynos',16,1,'I spoke with Eoradalanu Otuden, an Erudite on the grounds of the Three Towers. He told me about another similar tower out in the Antonican hills named the Tower of the Oracles. The Order of Coldwind resides within the tower and researches the nature of mana and the destruction of Luclin.',2310074,'I journeyed to the Tower of the Oracles and saw the structure first hand. It was an impressive tower but not as spectacular as the Three Towers in Qeynos, but can anything compare to that...?','Quests/SouthQeynos/a_visit_to_the_tower_of_the_oracles.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5555,'Gathering Components','South Qeynos','South Qeynos',8,1,'Khalil\'Mun of the Herb Jar in South Qeynos has charged me with the task of gathering components for one of his potions from the local Peat Bog. Though patronizing, it seems he means well.',2310048,'After a full warm bath and thorough scrubbing, I was able to clean the disgusting bog-filth away after collecting reagents for Khalil\'Mun\'s latest alchemical potion. Remind me never to work for a mage so cheaply again!','Quests/SouthQeynos/gathering_components.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5556,'Rabid Shriller Wings','South Qeynos','South Qeynos',9,1,'Khalil\'Mun -- of the Herb Jar in South Qeynos -- has told me that he is always working on improving his craft and to this end he has requested that I bring him eights pairs of rabid shriller wings. Rabid shrillers are known to be in the catacombs.',2310048,'I have given Khalil\'Mun of the Herb Jar in South Qeynos the eights pairs of rabid shriller wings that he requested. He was excited to finally have what he needs to continue with his experiments.','Quests/SouthQeynos/rabid_shriller_wings.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5557,'Corrupted Dryad Nuisance','South Qeynos','South Qeynos',9,1,'Fredrick Losce is one of the many people in the area that is fed up with the corrupted dryads that pester everyone in Oakmyst Forest. He has asked me to kill three of these dryads to see if it will help the situation.',2310108,'I went into Oakmyst Forest and killed three corrupted dryads at the request of Fredrick Losce. The little things have been a nuisance for far too long.','Quests/SouthQeynos/corrupted_dryad_nuisance.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5558,'Stop the Mischievous Tricksters','South Qeynos','South Qeynos',8,1,'Lieutenant Ilgar has convinced me to help him cull the faerie population in the Peat Bog. I\'ve heard faeries are difficult to find... I hope it doesn\'t take me too long to scare some of these up!',2310017,'Well, I\'ve managed to drive the faeries back, and keep them from playing pranks on the villagers of Nettleville and Starcrest Commune. I am happy I could be of assistance to these poor folk, even if it came at the cost of the lives of a few of the bog\'s more mischievous residents.','Quests/SouthQeynos/stop_the_mischievous_tricksters.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5559,'The Path of the Sun Wolf  ','The Peat Bog','The Peat Bog',10,1,'I have discovered an old withering journal that is barely readable. It details the path of a mythical creature called the Sun Wolf. I have decided to visit the locations that the Sun Wolf was last seen in hopes of encountering this beast and claiming its prize.',0,'I followed the path of the mythical Sun Wolf in the Peat Bog. At the end of my search the beast appeared, giving me an opportunity to face the creature in combat and emerge victorious.','Quests/ThePeatBog/the_path_of_the_sun_wolf_.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5560,'Qeynos Castaway\'s Isle ','Antonica','Antonica',14,1,'Tyllia has asked that I travel to the westernmost gnoll island, south of her location. Once there, she wants me to check the island for supplies and slay some gnolls. Without information on what the gnolls are bringing into Antonica, she isn\'t sure what the gnolls are up to.',121435,'I did as Tyllia asked. There were no supplies on the westernmost gnoll island.','Quests/Antonica/qeynos_castaways_isle.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5561,'Gnoll Shipping Lanes ','Antonica','Antonica',14,1,'Tyllia wants me to go to the dock on the eastern gnoll island and find a shipping manifest. When she finally has this information she can decide what to do about it.',121435,'I brought Tyllia the manifest she asked for.','Quests/Antonica/gnoll_shipping_lanes.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5562,'Elddar Rope','Qeynos Harbor','Qeynos Harbor',7,1,'Harron Griswald would like some help getting some rope he ordered from merchant Adrianna in Elddar Grove. Harron said something about using it for nets and harpoon line.',2210038,'I have been to Elddar Grove and picked up the rope that Harron ordered so he can make nets and harpoon line. He gave me some coin for my help.','Quests/QeynosHarbor/elddar_rope.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5563,'Sleek Wolf Hides','Qeynos Harbor','Qeynos Harbor',9,1,'Erwin Rohand needs all the money he can get so he can get back out to the sea and look for his lost love. I have offered to gather wolf hides for him so he may take them and turn them into valuable wearables.',2210124,'I went back to Erwin and gave him the sleek wolf hides that he requested. He was very happy to have stuff that would further his goal and I was happy to lend him a hand.','Quests/QeynosHarbor/sleek_wolf_hides.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5564,'Three Bushels Fresh','Qeynos Harbor','Qeynos Harbor',9,1,'The proprietor of the \"Fish\' Alehouse and Inn\" would like to get the best deal he can for three bushels of fresh fish, from the merchants at the \"Fisherman\'s Market.\" Galsway wrote the names of the four merchants in my journal.',2210022,'Galsway was pleased with the news of a five percent discount. He complimented me on my efforts, and made promises of future employment.','Quests/QeynosHarbor/three_bushels_fresh.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5565,'Visiting Crater Pond','Qeynos Harbor','Qeynos Harbor',11,1,'Ashilda MacHinry, a fisherwoman at the Qeynos Harbor, told me about a pool named Crater Pond where a meteor landed near the gates of the city. She warned that the water became poisoned by the rock. I think I\'d like to see this sight some day.',2210126,'I found the Crater Pond near the gates to Qeynos. I haven\'t tested the water myself, but it does look as though it is poisoned. Nothing was growing or living inside the pool, just as Ashilda MacHinry described. I found a small flask nearby, perhaps someone once wanted a sample.','Quests/QeynosHarbor/visiting_crater_pond.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5566,'The Patchwork Tapestry','Language','Multiple Zones',32,1,'I have discovered a patch of fay fabric with Norrathian letters printed on it. The letters are matched by a set of runes of equal size. This may form the foundation of a fairy language.',0,'I pieced together patches of fay fabric to discover the foundation of two languages, Norrathian and Fay. I have used the fabric patches to learn the language of the fairies, Fayfolk.','Quests/MultipleZones/the_patchwork_tapestry_classic.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5567,'Bark Like a Gnoll','Language','Multiple Zones',15,1,'I have discovered a gnoll rune with Norrathian and Gnoll languages on it. If I gather more of these Chirannite Threat Totems I might get an understanding of the gnoll language.',0,'I have studied a great amount of gnoll runes written in both Norrathian and Gnollish. I now understand the language of the gnolls.','Quests/MultipleZones/bark_like_a_gnoll_classic.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5568,'Claiming the Goblish Tongue','Language','Multiple Zones',34,1,'I have discovered a territory marker. The marker is written in both Norrathian and the goblin language. I can learn the goblin language if I had other territory markers to study.',0,'I have studied a great amount of territory markers written in both Norrathian and the goblin language. I now understand Goblish.','Quests/MultipleZones/claiming_the_goblish_tongue_classic.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5569,'An Order of Orc Tongue','Language','Multiple Zones',16,1,'I have discovered a requisition for seized goods between the orcs and smugglers. The order is written in both Norrathian and orc. I can learn the orc language if I had other orders to study.',0,'I have studied a great amount of orc smuggler requisitions written in both Norrathian and orc. I now understand the language, Orcish.','Quests/MultipleZones/an_order_of_orc_tongue_classic.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5570,'Wings of a Feather Hiss Together','South Qeynos','South Qeynos',10,1,'I\'ve come across an extravagant merchant by the name of Gauldry who has charged me with the task of recovering no less than six flying snake wings from the nearby caves.',2310037,'The winged snakes were no easy task, though I\'ve learned much dealing with their twisted tactics. Merchant Gauldry was pleased with my efforts and the quality of the wings recovered.','Quests/SouthQeynos/wings_of_a_feather_hiss_together.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5571,'Taking the Bait','Qeynos Harbor','Qeynos Harbor',5,1,'I met Sean Wellfayer at the dock in Qeynos Harbor and he\'d like me to fetch some bait for him. I\'m off to the Peat Bog to get some slug meat and bog faerie wings.',2210065,'I got everything Sean needed and he was quite pleased. The pay was decent and perhaps I\'ll help him get some more bait in the future.','Quests/QeynosHarbor/taking_the_bait.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5572,'Words of Pure Magic','Language','Multiple Zones',45,1,'I have read a tale of a magical language known to few, the language Druzaic. It is said that this is the language of pure magic, but to learn it I must find the four Druzaic Shrines scattered somewhere in the Shattered Lands.',0,'I finally discovered all four of the Druzaic Shrines in the Shattered Lands. I have studied them and learned the language of pure magic, Druzaic.','Quests/MultipleZones/words_of_pure_magic.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5573,'Fearful Words','Language','Multiple Zones',45,1,'I have discovered a Thulian puzzle box with phrases etched into it. The phrases appear in both Norrathian and Thulian, the language of Modinthule, the Plane of Fear. I can learn the language if I had other puzzle boxes to study.',0,'I have studied a great amount of Thulian puzzle boxes etched with phrases in both Norrathian and Thulian. I now understand the Thulian language of Modinthule, the Plane of Fear.','Quests/MultipleZones/fearful_words.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5574,'Words of a Giant','Language','Multiple Zones',29,1,'I have discovered a giant idol with runes on it. If I can collect more of these giant idols from the giants of Norrath I can probably begin to understand the foundation of all the giant languages.',0,'I studied a number of runes on giant idols and now understand the foundation of all the giant languages, Krombral.','Quests/MultipleZones/words_of_a_giant.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5575,'Tapping the Torrent','Language','Multiple Zones',40,1,'I have discovered an ebon storm gem. It fills my mind with bleak visions and a foreign tongue when I grasp it tightly. I can almost understand the voices before they abruptly stop. I need more of these gems to tap them of their power in order to understand this odd language.',0,'I tapped the power of a number of ebon storm gems. Their voices flooded my mind and then all of the sudden I could comprehend the language called Chaos Tongue, spoken by the fiends that have invaded parts of Norrath from worlds unknown.','Quests/MultipleZones/tapping_the_torrent.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5576,'Voices from Beyond','Language','Multiple Zones',41,1,'I have discovered a transference directive composed of mostly an odd alien script. A few lines appear in both Norrathian and some other language. This may be the language of the shadowed men. I can learn the language if I had other directives to study.',0,'I have studied a great number of transference directives scribed with phrases in both Norrathian and the shadowed man language. I now understand the language, Words of Shade.','Quests/MultipleZones/voices_from_beyond.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5577,'To Speak as a Dragon','Hallmark','Multiple Zones',50,8,'While traveling through Lavastorm we came upon an ancient High Elf that was being attacked by a pair of dragon-like Drakota. We were able to slay the creatures and rescue the High Elf from certain death. He introduced himself as the Sage of Ages, a chronicler of history. After some conversation we learned that the sage believes the Drakota were sent by the great red dragon Nagafen to kill him. He didn\'t know why the dragon would do such a thing and wanted to know what he had done to bring such an attack about but didn\'t want to venture any closer to the dragon\'s lair. We volunteered to go to the lair and get some answers.',3290001,'The red dragon Nagafen would not speak to us unless we were able to speak with him in his ancient language. This was told to us by his majordomo Inferinus. By following a theory the Sage of Ages had on the research of the Draconic language, I was able to find researched translations of all twenty six draconic runes which allowed the sage to teach me the ancient tongue.','Quests/MultipleZones/to_speak_as_a_dragon.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5578,'Fire and Ice','Hallmark','Multiple Zones',50,8,'I spoke with the red dragon, Lord Nagafen within his lair. He denied having sent the Drakota to attack the Sage of Ages and even denied knowing who he was. However, after hearing that I defeated two Drakota to save the sage, Nagafen made me a deal that if I could resurrect Lady Vox from death I would receive a large reward. Also, he would double the reward if I found and returned to him his lost Orb of Omnipotence.',0,'The dragon Darathar was the Sage of Ages all along! After temporarily resurrecting Lady Vox from the dead, she was able to sense that the Ice Giants held her long lost egg. We defeated the traitorous King Drayek to recover the egg for Nagafen but the Darathar double crossed us and took it!','Quests/MultipleZones/fire_and_ice.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5579,'Deception','Hallmark','Multiple Zones',50,8,'Nagafen was very angry that Darathar has gotten his claws on his egg. He was unable to tell us where Darathar is, and he said even Darathar\'s lieutenants can only reach him through the use of five Translocation Rings. Nagafen gave us one of the rings, we need to collect the other four.',2460002,'Darathar has been defeated but the egg was destroyed at the end of the battle. All that was left were prismatic egg shell shards. It seems Nagafen was only using us to find his missing egg. He didn\'t care it was destroyed, he was more concerned with someone other than himself possessing it.','Quests/MultipleZones/deception.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5580,'Running with Cake','South Qeynos','South Qeynos',5,1,'Tibby Copperpot is a baker of some renown. Harold Dunstan in North Qeynos is considering expanding his inventory. Tibby has asked me to deliver a bundle of fresh baked goods to Harold.',2310008,'I have delivered the baked goods from Tibby to Harold at Irontoe\'s East in North Qeynos. Harold is very excited to have such variety in his store and hopes to attract much more business. A few drinks and bread for my efforts were well worth it.','Quests/SouthQeynos/running_with_cake.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5581,'The Former Resting Place of Varsoon','South Qeynos','South Qeynos',15,4,'I spoke with Feodra Iceslayer about an old tomb that once held a mage by the name of Varsoon the Undying. She said the cataclysm may have weakened the spells put on the place to hold him there. I think I\'d like to check this place out for myself.',2310100,'I saw the Tomb of Varsoon. The crypt was broken open like Feodra speculated. Undead beings lurked in the area, probably former servants of the mage or results of his presence there. However I didn\'t see anything that would resemble a powerful undead mage.','Quests/SouthQeynos/the_former_resting_place_of_varsoon.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5582,'Deep Marshes','Feerrott','Unknown',38,1,'I have found a book by the name of \"Deep Marshes.\" Many of the pages are missing, but I think it may be possible to locate them.',0,'I have found all of the missing pages for the book titled \"Deep Marshes.\"','Quests/Unknown/deep_marshes.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5583,'The Lady of the Lake','Feerrott','The Feerrott',39,1,'I have found a book by the name of \"The Lady of the Lake.\" Many of the pages are missing, but I think it may be possible to locate them.',0,'I have found all of the missing pages for the book.','Quests/TheFeerrott/the_lady_of_the_lake.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5584,'The Commander\'s Wife','Ruins of Varsoon','Ruins of Varsoon',30,6,'I have found a book by the name of \"The Commander\'s Wife.\" Many of the pages are missing, but I think it may be possible to locate them.',0,'I have found all of the missing pages for the book titled \"The Commander\'s Wife.\"','Quests/RuinsofVarsoon/the_commanders_wife.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5585,'Sea Food Stew','Qeynos Harbor','Qeynos Harbor',14,1,'I met Cordun at the Fish\' Alehouse and Inn. He isn\'t the trusting type, for whatever reason. He said that if I head out to Antonica and catch him two barracuda, a manta ray and two sea turtles, I\'ve done him a favor and then he can trust me. Sounds like the makings of a tasty stew.',0,'I met Cordun at the Fish\' Alehouse and Inn. He isn\'t the trusting type, for whatever reason. He said that if I head out to Antonica and catch him two barracuda, a manta ray and two sea turtles, I\'ve done him a favor and then he can trust me. Sounds like the makings of a tasty stew.','Quests/QeynosHarbor/sea_food_stew.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5586,'Letter from the Boss','Qeynos Harbor','Qeynos Harbor',10,1,'Shanda Tierbold was given a letter from her boss to give to merchant Baily Dowden in Nettleville. I don\'t know who this boss is and I don\'t know what the letter is about, but I\'m going to make sure it gets there.',2210037,'I have done my job for Shanda and her boss by delivering a letter to Baily Dowden. After talking with Baily Dowden I\'m still not sure what it was about but I was given some coin and ale for my hard work.','Quests/QeynosHarbor/letter_from_the_boss.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5587,'Of Spars and Sails and ...','Qeynos Harbor','Qeynos Harbor',27,1,'Dajor Botswein is on shore leave investigating the theft of some rather mundane items from a variety of ships. Apparently, the Far Seas Trading Company is offering a reward for the person who solves the case, so with a few clues from Dajor, I\'m well on my way to collecting the coin!',2210115,'I located a few of the items but I don\'t seem any closer to finding out who the pirates are and why they are stealing such peculiar items. I need to talk to someone else in Qeynos Harbor and see if I can learn more about these mysterious happenings, starting with that barmaid that gave me my reward.','Quests/QeynosHarbor/of_spars_and_sails_and_.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5588,'Ian\'s Forgetful Family - Part I','Qeynos Harbor','Qeynos Harbor',20,1,'Ian Cathlan within Qeynos Harbor has asked me to help him look for his lost heirlooms. He\'s agreed to reward me for my help with some old armor he\'ll have refitted for me.',2210084,'Ian has rewarded me with armor for collecting a few of his lost family\'s possessions.','Quests/QeynosHarbor/ians_forgetful_family__part_i.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5589,'Ian\'s Forgetful Family - Part II','Qeynos Harbor','Qeynos Harbor',21,1,'Ian Cathlan within Qeynos Harbor has asked me to help him look for his lost heirlooms. He\'s agreed to reward me for my help with some old armor he\'ll have refitted for me.',2210084,'Ian has rewarded me with armor for collecting a few of his lost family\'s possessions.','Quests/QeynosHarbor/ians_forgetful_family__part_ii.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5590,'Ian\'s Forgetful Family - Part III','Qeynos Harbor','Qeynos Harbor',22,1,'Ian Cathlan within Qeynos Harbor has asked me to help him look for his lost heirlooms. He\'s agreed to reward me for my help with some old armor he\'ll have refitted for me.',2210084,'Ian has rewarded me with armor for collecting a few of his lost family\'s possessions.','Quests/QeynosHarbor/ians_forgetful_family__part_iii.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5591,'Ian\'s Forgetful Family - Part IV ','Qeynos Harbor','Qeynos Harbor',23,6,'Ian Cathlan within Qeynos Harbor has asked me to help him look for his lost heirlooms. He\'s agreed to reward me for my help with some old armor he\'ll have refitted for me.',2210084,'Ian has rewarded me with armor for collecting a few of his lost family\'s possessions.','Quests/QeynosHarbor/ians_forgetful_family__part_iv_.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5592,'Ian\'s Forgetful Family - Part V','Qeynos Harbor','Qeynos Harbor',24,6,'Ian Cathlan within Qeynos Harbor has asked me to help him look for his lost heirlooms. He\'s agreed to reward me for my help with some old armor he\'ll have refitted for me.',2210084,'Ian has rewarded me with armor for collecting a few of his lost family\'s possessions.','Quests/QeynosHarbor/ians_forgetful_family__part_v.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5593,'Ian\'s Forgetful Family - Part VI','Qeynos Harbor','Qeynos Harbor',25,6,'Ian Cathlan within Qeynos Harbor has asked me to help him look for his lost heirlooms. He\'s agreed to reward me for my help with some old armor he\'ll have refitted for me.',2210084,'Ian has rewarded me with armor for collecting a few of his lost family\'s possessions.','Quests/QeynosHarbor/ians_forgetful_family__part_vi.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5594,'The Forgotten Blackburrow Cask','Nettleville','Nettleville',8,1,'While walking the alleys of Nettleville I discovered a cask filled with Blackburrow Stout. The word Starcrest was also written on the cask. Perhaps I should find the owner.',0,'The cask of Blackburrow Stout was en route to Bartender Bermo in Starcrest Commune. I informed him of its location. Bermo paid me to keep quiet about this. The Ironforge Exchange has outlawed Blackburrow Stout.','Quests/Nettleville/the_forgotten_blackburrow_cask.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5595,'Verth\'s Delivery','Nettleville','Nettleville',8,1,'I met a human by the name of Verth while traveling behind the buildings in Nettleville. He said I looked trustworthy enough and offered me the job of meeting his brother down by the Nettleville Dock.',2330051,'I have gotten rid of the contraband given to me by Aves. I wonder if I did the right thing.','Quests/Nettleville/verths_delivery.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5596,'An Urgent Message from Nettleville','Nettleville','Nettleville',8,1,'I have accepted a mission from Captain Hastings of the Nettleville Garrison. I must deliver this urgent message to the captain of the Starcrest Garrison. Qeynos may depend upon it.',2330030,'I delivered the message. It was just a challenge sent by Captain Hastings to Captain Santis. Apparently the Qeynos Guards compete in Phalanx matches, a team sport. The few coins at least were worth my time.','Quests/Nettleville/an_urgent_message_from_nettleville.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5597,'Scalies for Shinies','Nettleville','Nettleville',10,1,'I met an... interesting... character by the name of Dirk Vagrin. Strangely enough he was willing to give me coin, which he called \"shinies,\" in exchange for Albino Snake Skin of all things. He said he wanted ten of them and they could be found in the Caves nearby.',2330020,'Sure enough, Dirk Vagrin gave me money and an albino snakeskin wristband for giving him the ten Albino Snake Skins. I felt kind of bad taking his money but we were both happy with the end results.','Quests/Nettleville/scalies_for_shinies.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5598,'Nia\'s Hissing Fit','Nettleville','Nettleville',8,1,'Nia Jaja was apparently insulted by Marjani Kenan while in the scribe shop in Nettleville. She asked that I go visit the shop and see if Marjani was still there. Nia doesn\'t want to go back to work until Marjani is gone.',2330023,'I checked out the scribe shop for Nia and reported back. Unfortunately, Marjani hadn\'t left yet so Nia won\'t be getting back to work any time soon.','Quests/Nettleville/nias_hissing_fit.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5599,'Sketch the Qeynos Claymore Monument','Nettleville','Nettleville',8,1,'Smith Cayless Chambers will pay me to sketch the Qeynos Claymore monument in the center of Qeynos. She needs a sketch to help her create a duplicate of the legendary sword.',2330041,'I discovered and sketched the Qeynos Claymore monument. I have given the sketchpad to Smith Cayless Chambers in Nettleville. She paid me for my service and threw in a easel for my future artistic endeavors.','Quests/Nettleville/sketch_the_qeynos_claymore_monument.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5600,'Essence Hunting for Obidudyn','Starcrest Commune','Starcrest Commune',10,8,'An Erudite scholar by the name of Obidudyn was quite irritated with the disruption to his studies on the summoning of elementals. He offered me the chance to hunt for six Essences of Elemental for him, probably to keep me busy. He said that Elementals can be found in the old Forest Ruins nearby.',2340034,'I was able to collect six Essence of Elemental that Scholar Obidudyn tasked me with finding and paid me for the job. He seemed a little surprised in how quickly I managed to fulfill his request.','Quests/StarcrestCommune/essence_hunting_for_obidudyn.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5601,'Quills for Ommanoden','Starcrest Commune','Starcrest Commune',13,1,'The uppity scribe in Starcrest Commune has sent me out to fetch him some new feathers for his quills. I suppose he\'s too busy to do it himself, probably has his nose buried ten cogs into that book. I\'ll need to gather the quills from hawks in Antonica.',2340052,'Despite gathering the most perfect feathers for his quills, the Erudite scribe remained aloof. Perhaps one day I will call on him to find information for me in all those books and scrolls he pens.','Quests/StarcrestCommune/quills_for_ommanoden.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5602,'Catacomb Rat Rummaging','Starcrest Commune','Starcrest Commune',8,1,'I somehow got myself involved with a man who wants to help his friend out by getting a King\'s Field game ended. I think he\'s going to drop giant rat corpses around the play area, and see if people run away in fear. I think he\'ll be sorely disappointed with the results.',2340008,'I fetched the rats for the spectator, though I don\'t believe they will do him much good. Judging by how intent Vandis and his opponent are on their King\'s Field game, I don\'t think even a dragon standing behind them would interrupt play.','Quests/StarcrestCommune/catacomb_rat_rummaging.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5603,'Elliasenka\'s Dagger is Ready','Starcrest Commune','Starcrest Commune',8,1,'Barrik, the arms dealer in Starcrest, asked me if I would deliver a note to Elliasenka Croosinaden letting her know her dagger is ready. He said that she could probably be found in the tavern.',2340010,'I gave Arms Dealer Barrik\'s note to Elliasenka and returned to him for my payment. I hope Elliasenka is only going to use it to cut fruit.','Quests/StarcrestCommune/elliasenkas_dagger_is_ready.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5604,'Searching for a Scroll','Starcrest Commune','Starcrest Commune',8,1,'I met two erudites pestering a man at the Inn. One of them, Zentomaron Croosinaden, bid me go to a scribe by the name of Varion Smitelin in Nettleville to retrieve a scroll to settle some debate. Hopefully when I return they\'ll cease questioning the man they have cornered!',2340020,'Scribe Varion would not divulge the scroll\'s location to Zentomaron. I fear whatever debate he\'s having will go on forever. I passed on the scribe\'s message to leave his nephew alone, but I don\'t know how seriously Zentomaron will take that request.','Quests/StarcrestCommune/searching_for_a_scroll.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5605,'Tanaira\'s Picnic Spot','Starcrest Commune','Starcrest Commune',8,1,'Tanaira the merchant wants to take Merchant Grekin on a picnic to let him know how she feels about him. She wants me to scout out a spot she heard about in Oakmyst Forest near the waterfall and to make a map to it.',2340040,'Tanaira seemed pleased with the map and my report that the location was a pretty good spot for a picnic. I hope she is able to get Grekin to take time off from being a merchant and to go on the picnic with her.','Quests/StarcrestCommune/tanairas_picnic_spot.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5606,'Selwyn\'s Errands - Part I','South Qeynos','South Qeynos',20,1,'Selwyn Oakheart within South Qeynos has asked me to help her with a few errands while she refits some old armor a friend of hers used to wear.',2310028,'Selwyn has paid me with some armor for my hands.','Quests/SouthQeynos/selwyns_errands__part_i.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5607,'Selwyn\'s Errands - Part II','South Qeynos','South Qeynos',21,6,'Selwyn Oakheart within South Qeynos has asked me to help her with a few errands while she refits some old armor a friend of hers used to wear.',2310028,'Selwyn has paid me with some armor for my forearms.','Quests/SouthQeynos/selwyns_errands__part_ii.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5608,'Selwyn\'s Errands - Part III','South Qeynos','South Qeynos',6,1,'Selwyn Oakheart within South Qeynos has asked me to help her with a few errands while she refits some old armor a friend of hers used to wear.',2310028,'Selwyn has paid me with some armor for my feet.','Quests/SouthQeynos/selwyns_errands__part_iii.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5609,'Selwyn\'s Errands - Part IV','South Qeynos','South Qeynos',6,1,'Selwyn Oakheart within South Qeynos has asked me to help her with a few errands while she refits some old armor a friend of hers used to wear.',2310028,'Selwyn has paid me with some armor for my shoulders.','Quests/SouthQeynos/selwyns_errands__part_iv.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5610,'Selwyn\'s Errands - Part V','South Qeynos','South Qeynos',6,1,'Selwyn Oakheart within South Qeynos has asked me to help her with a few errands while she refits some old armor a friend of hers used to wear.',2310028,'Selwyn has paid me with some armor for my legs.','Quests/SouthQeynos/selwyns_errands__part_v.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5611,'Selwyn\'s Errands - Part VI','South Qeynos','South Qeynos',6,1,'Selwyn Oakheart within South Qeynos has asked me to help her with a few errands while she refits some old armor a friend of hers used to wear.',2310028,'Selwyn has paid me with some armor for my chest.','Quests/SouthQeynos/selwyns_errands__part_vi.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5612,'Gildas\' Requests - Part I','The Elddar Grove','The Elddar Grove',20,1,'Gildas Cedartree within the Elddar Grove has asked me to help him with some of his duties while he is unable to leave the city. He has agreed to speak to a tailoring friend of his who might be able to make me some new clothes for my time and efforts.',2070033,'I have helped Gildas with what he has asked. I should return to him.','Quests/TheElddarGrove/gildas_requests__part_i.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5613,'Gildas\' Requests - Part II','The Elddar Grove','The Elddar Grove',21,1,'Gildas Cedartree within the Elddar Grove has asked me to help him with some of his duties while he is unable to leave the city. He has agreed to speak to a tailoring friend of his who might be able to make me some new clothes for my time and efforts.',2070033,'Gildas has rewarded me with a pair of silver touched armbands.','Quests/TheElddarGrove/gildas_requests__part_ii.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5614,'Gildas\' Requests - Part III','The Elddar Grove','The Elddar Grove',22,1,'Gildas Cedartree within the Elddar Grove has asked me to help him with some of his duties while he is unable to leave the city. He has agreed to speak to a tailoring friend of his who might be able to make me some new clothes for my time and efforts.',2070033,'Gildas has rewarded me with a pair of silver touched shoes.','Quests/TheElddarGrove/gildas_requests__part_iii.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5615,'Gildas\' Requests - Part IV','The Elddar Grove','The Elddar Grove',23,6,'Gildas Cedartree within the Elddar Grove has asked me to help him with some of his duties while he is unable to leave the city. He has agreed to speak to a tailoring friend of his who might be able to make me some new clothes for my time and efforts.',2070033,'Gildas has rewarded me with a silver touched shawl.','Quests/TheElddarGrove/gildas_requests__part_iv.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5616,'Gildas\' Requests - Part V','The Elddar Grove','The Elddar Grove',24,6,'Gildas Cedartree within the Elddar Grove has asked me to help him with some of his duties while he is unable to leave the city. He has agreed to speak to a tailoring friend of his who might be able to make me some new clothes for my time and efforts.',2070033,'Gildas has rewarded me with a pair of silver touched leggings.','Quests/TheElddarGrove/gildas_requests__part_v.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5617,'Gildas\' Requests - Part VI','The Elddar Grove','The Elddar Grove',25,6,'Gildas Cedartree within the Elddar Grove has asked me to help him with some of his duties while he is unable to leave the city. He has agreed to speak to a tailoring friend of his who might be able to make me some new clothes for my time and efforts.',2070033,'Gildas has rewarded me with a silver touched robe.','Quests/TheElddarGrove/gildas_requests__part_vi.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5618,'Trolls and Arms','Big Bend','Big Bend',7,0,'Armsdealer Bort would like to expand his business by selling to other dealers, but he isn\'t sure how to begin. I need to travel to Temple Street and speak with any Armsdealers I find there.',1340023,'I\'ve checked around Temple Street and found only one armsdealer. It seems she\'s been buying weapons from a human, just like Blort. Blort paid me with one of his painted weapons.','Quests/BigBend/trolls_and_arms.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5619,'Vermin Reduction','Big Bend','Big Bend',5,1,'Zarbt the Ratcatcher wants me to help him kill rats in Big Bend.',1340017,'Realizing the rodents are merely a byproduct of the city\'s inhabitants, I now know how futile my efforts were. Not to mention having to shake down that ratcatcher to get next-to-nothing for my efforts.','Quests/BigBend/vermin_reduction.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5620,'The Captive\'s Information','Big Bend','Big Bend',17,3,'Vakiza Skinner believes a thrall plans to use some monsters to attack Freeport. She wants you to attack these particular monsters.',1340031,'I\'ve taken care of the creatures for Vakiza Skinner.  She said the Overlord would be pleased with our work.','Quests/BigBend/the_captives_information.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5621,'Sorio\'s Giantslayer Problem','Big Bend','Big Bend',7,1,'I need to kill ten of the Giantslayer Thugs to send them a message that the Freeport Militia shouldn\'t be messed with.',1340032,'Guard Captain Sorio was surprised that I actually did what he asked. He offered me some coin and a militia wristband as payment for my help.','Quests/BigBend/sorios_giantslayer_problem.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5622,'Sorio\'s Dog Hunt','Big Bend','Big Bend',10,1,'You ask Captain Sorio if he needs more help, and he tells you he does not want the thugs breeding more dogs.',1340032,'Sorio paid me for killing the wild dogs. I\'m pretty sure he insulted me at the same time he thanked me. He\'ll pay one day.','Quests/BigBend/sorios_dog_hunt.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5623,'Skagga\'s Signs','Big Bend','Big Bend',8,0,'Merchant Skagga wants a sign for her shop to get more business for her \'precious wares\'.',1340008,'Skagga liked her signs, and offered me some coin for my time.','Quests/BigBend/skaggas_signs.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5624,'Skin for Skagga','Big Bend','Big Bend',9,1,'Merchant Skagga feels her signs are not working — a zombie skin would add a decorative touch and thus improve business.',1340008,'Skagga doesn\'t like her signs, but she thinks that zombie skin might help to make them prettier.','Quests/BigBend/skin_for_skaaga.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5625,'Paying the Tab','Big Bend','Big Bend',7,0,'Bartender Galenus wants to pay his debt at the bank, but he can\'t leave his bank in the hand of his barmaid. The bank is found in the district center, a short distance away from Galenus.',1340016,'I delivered the money that Galenus asked me to. He paid me for my time.','Quests/BigBend/paying_the_tab.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5626,'Hops for Galenus','Big Bend','Big Bend',9,0,'Galenus the bartender wants me to speak with a person by the name of Hurska and ask about \'hops and barley\'.',1340016,'I have given Galenus his package of \'hops and barley\'. I\'m pretty certain it wasn\'t what he said it was, but I\'d rather not ask any questions.','Quests/BigBend/hops_for_galenus.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5627,'Muzmog\'s Rat Smashing Fun','Big Bend','Big Bend',5,1,'Muzmog likes drinking ale, he likes smashng rats, and he especially likes smashing rats after drinking ale. I should kill rats to make Muzmog happy. There are rats everywhere throughout the city of Freeport. I can find rats in many places. Muzmog will not know the difference.',1340020,'I\'ve told Muzmog about what I did to the rats. He liked it so much that he told me I can drink with him any time.','Quests/BigBend/muzmogs_rat_smashing_fun.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5628,'Funny Rat Smashing','Big Bend','Big Bend',5,1,'Muzmog says smashing funny-looking rats is even more fun, and you get to participate again.',1340020,'I\'ve tried to make friends with Muzmog, but it seems he\'s had a bit too much to drink. I think I\'ll leave him alone from now on.','Quests/BigBend/funny_rat_smashing.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5629,'Dwarven Payback','Big Bend','Big Bend',9,1,'A Dwarven prisoner has been tortured by his captor and he wants revenge against the Ratonga who put him in this situation. I need to kill Ratongas in the Thieves Way.',1340028,'I\'ve killed a number of ratonga to avenge the dwarf.','Quests/BigBend/dwarven_payback.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5630,'Brona\'s Thralls','Big Bend','Big Bend',7,0,'I\'ve got to let Bartender Icebrew from the Scale Yard district know that Brona has new thralls for him to choose from.',1340030,'Running errands for Slaver Brona wasn\'t as bad as I had imagined... Perhaps I\'ll offer my services again.','Quests/BigBend/bronas_thralls.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5631,'Brona\'s Guard Check','Big Bend','Big Bend',8,0,'Slaver Brona wants to make sure the guards are at the city gate entrances for each of the districts, and she sends you to check on this.',1340030,'It was easy enough work, but that Brona is up to something and I\'ve unwittingly helped her. I wonder what she is trying to accomplish.','Quests/BigBend/bronas_guard_check.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5632,'Ay, There\'s the Rubb\'ish','Big Bend','Big Bend',3,0,'I am to remove the remnants of the fight from around the gates to the City of Freeport.',1340040,'I cleaned up the trash and other signs of the fight from around the gate to South Freeport.','Quests/BigBend/ay_theres_the_rubbish.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5633,'Rat Barsh!','Big Bend','Big Bend',4,1,'I need to go hunt for rats at the gate leading to the Sprawl.',1340040,'I barshed many rats at the gate to the Sprawl for Kroota.  Even though they were not what he had in mind, he still says they will come in useful.','Quests/BigBend/rat_barsh.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5634,'Much Ado\' About Rallos','Big Bend','Big Bend',4,0,'Rallos\' ceremony requires blood of his enemies, skins of the inferior, and incense.',1340040,'The ceremony to honor Rallos Zek will go well, now that the needed items were given to Kroota.','Quests/BigBend/much_ado_about_rallos.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5635,'The Fume and Fire Ceremony','Big Bend','Big Bend',5,0,'The ceremony for Rallos Zek is to continue without Kroota.',1340040,'The ceremony was completed without interruption.','Quests/BigBend/the_fume_and_fire_ceremony.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5636,'More Barshing!','Big Bend','Big Bend',5,0,'I need to find Enforcer Kurdek in The Sprawl and see what work he has for me.',1340040,'I have spoken to Enforcer Kurdek.','Quests/BigBend/more_barshing.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5637,'A Subtle Reminder ','Big Bend','Big Bend',3,0,'Speak to Thick-headed Ruzb about his culinary habits. He should be east of the Freeport gate, in the building with Brona the slaver.',1340039,'With Ruzb convinced to stop eating gnomes from the neighboring areas, Braz thanked me. Maybe I should come back later and ask him some more about the trolls.','Quests/BigBend/a_subtle_reminder_.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5638,'Gnoll Brew!?','Blackburrow','Blackburrow',15,1,'While venturing deep into Blackburrow I came across a geologist and his assistant. The assistant Wilabus told me that these gnolls have a brewery down here, and asked if I might fetch him a jug. He said that he would compensate me for me effort, though I\'m doing this more just to see if there is indeed a brewery.',170013,'Sure enough there was a brewery down here in Blackburrow. Kind of gives a new meaning to the phrase \"hair of the dog.\"','Quests/Blackburrow/gnoll_brew.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5639,'Trollish Delights','Big Bend','Big Bend',4,0,'Club down four Big Bend rats and take their carcasses. Braz said they should be by the gate to the Sprawl.',1340039,'How could anyone know that Braz wouldn\'t like his rats cooked? It seems like such a natural thing to do, really. Don\'t eat the food unless it\'s cooked. Isn\'t that taught to everyone?','Quests/BigBend/trollish_delights.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5640,'Rare Rock Lost','Blackburrow','Blackburrow',15,1,'While at the bottom of Blackburrow I came across a geologist and his assistant. It seems that Fribden had lost some rare rock samples in the upper mine of Blackburrow. At Fribden\'s request and with the promise of compensation, I said I would recover the rock samples.',170012,'I was able to recover all of the lost rock samples for geologist Fribden. He was very pleased with my efforts and I was well rewarded.','Quests/Blackburrow/rare_rock_lost.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5641,'Troll Patrol ','Big Bend','Big Bend',4,1,'Perform Braz Gutpounder\'s patrol around Big Bend.',1340039,'Aside from that filthy, foul and disruptive little halfling, the whole patrol was quiet. Only one dead. I suppose it\'s a good day.','Quests/BigBend/troll_patrol_.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5642,'Gnomore Gnomesteaks','Big Bend','Big Bend',5,1,'Check in with Ruzb and make sure he\'s not gone back to eating gnomes again.',1340039,'Unfortunately, Ruzb just couldn\'t keep from eating the gnomes. Much to his discomfort, he had to be put out of his own misery. Or rather, Freeport can\'t have its citizens eating each other. It\'s just bad for morale.','Quests/BigBend/gnomore_gnomesteaks.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5643,'Troll Adventures ','Big Bend','Big Bend',5,0,'Head out to the Sprawl and see if you can find Enforcer Kurdek.',1340039,'I\'ve spoken with Enforcer Kurdek in the sprawl.','Quests/BigBend/troll_adventures_.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5644,'A crude gnoll map','Antonica','Antonica',12,1,'A crude gnoll map leads me to believe that the gnolls are interested in a farmer named Walcott. I will go and find this Walcott in Antonica and speak to him of this.',120078,'I helped farmer Walcott gather the components necessary to construct a magical scarecrow that might help defend his crops from gnoll intrusions.','Quests/Antonica/a_crude_gnoll_map.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5645,'Search for the Shrubbery','Big Bend','Big Bend',3,0,'Graktak wants me to collect shrubs for his stew. They can be found in the center of Big Bend.',1340042,'I was able to find the shrubs of \'much goodness\' for Graktak. I have determined that most trolls in Freeport only care for two things, killing and eating. Fortunately, it seems if I continue to help Graktak he may decide not to eat me.','Quests/BigBend/search_for_the_shrubbery.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5646,'Swamp Water Stew','Big Bend','Big Bend',4,0,'I need to collect some stew from another troll\'s cooking pot in the center of Big Bend.',1340042,'I have collected the stew, if you could call it that, for Graktak. He was very pleased when I gave it to him, and suggested that maybe I am not food after all.','Quests/BigBend/swamp_water_stew.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5647,'That Slippery Toad','Big Bend','Big Bend',5,0,'I need to find the froglok in Big Bend, and retrieve Graktak\'s sword for him.',1340042,'I was able to find and squish the froglok just as Graktak asked. Graktak was very happy when I returned his sword, but seemed more excited that he may get to eat more frog meat.','Quests/BigBend/that_slippery_toad.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5648,'Secret of the Troll','Big Bend','Big Bend',5,0,'I need to answer Graktak\'s questions before he will help me get better equipment. Graktak wants to ask me some questions before introducing me to his friends.',1340042,'I passed Graktak\'s simple quest. Being a good troll sounds like it will be easy as long as I remember to eat often, and smash things more than I eat. In the end though, Graktak told me I should speak with Braz Gutpounder on the docks here in Big Bend, or Enforcer Kurdek in The Sprawl if I had already spoken to Braz.','Quests/BigBend/secret_of_the_troll.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5649,'99 Bottles Of Beer In My Hand','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',7,8,'I\'ve been hired by Festus Septimus to collect a special type of sand so that he can make some more glass bottles. It seems the sand can be found in the gizzards of the brine sifters that are in the Sunken City.',1370024,'I\'ve been paid by Festus Septimus for the sand I\'ve collected. It seems that he intended on using the sand to make weaker glass bottles. His market for glassware requires that his bottles break in a jagged fashion so that they can be used as weapons in a bar fight.','Quests/BeggarsCourt/99_bottles_of_beer_in_my_hand.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5650,'An Errand for the Queen','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',9,1,'Tullia Domna has lost it. She thinks she\'s\r\nQueen Antonia Bayle, and married to\r\nOverlord Luclan D\'Vere. She wants you to\r\nkill her \'entourage.\' I need to venture to the Sprawl and kill five Giantslayer Brutes.',1370000,'Tullia Domna, the mad woman in Beggar\'s Court, was going to knight me for killing the Giantslayer Brutes. Even though I was playing along with her insanity, I don\'t think I should go as far as giving her a sharp instrument to knight me with. This woman really needs help.','Quests/BeggarsCourt/an_errand_for_the_queen.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5651,'Antius\' Package','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',8,0,'Antius Vedrix has a package to send, and\r\nyou\'re just the one to deliver it, but as\r\nis often the way in Freeport, you saw\r\nand did nothing, hear?! I need to bring this package to an Iksar in Scale Yard, I think Antius said the Iksar was named Mirini, or Mirin, or something.',1370008,'Antius Vedrix has been given his message. I have absolutely no idea what\'s going on, or what I might have gotten myself into. I think I\'ll just avoid these people for the time being.','Quests/BeggarsCourt/antius_package.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5652,'Casing the Joint','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',5,0,'I\'ve been given a job by Lucius Vulso to see how secure the bank vault is in the Stonestair Byway district.',1370036,'I\'ve told Lucius about the rumored security leak in the vaults. It seems Lucius was having me ask around so that he wouldn\'t be the one identified for being suspicious.','Quests/BeggarsCourt/casing_the_joint.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5653,'Into The Sewers For Lucius','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',5,1,'Go into the Thieves’ Way and get trash hopper\r\nslime to disguise his scent when he\r\nbreaks into the bank vault. I need to go into the sewers and find six trash hoppers and kill them. Once they\'re dead, I\'ll scrape the slime off of their bodies. I sure hope they\'re not too big.',1370036,'I\'ve given Lucius Vulso enough slime from the frog\'s skin to mask his scent. If he manages to pull off this bank heist, I\'ll have to follow his lead and get out of the city. I\'m the only one who was seen asking about the place... what was I thinking?','Quests/BeggarsCourt/into_the_sewers_for_lucius.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5654,'Free Wares for Silentblade','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',7,1,'Silentblade the Arms Dealer has agreed to show me a few of his secrets in regards to the arms dealer trade. Before he shows me any of his tricks, I need to first kill undead battlepriests and gather up their maces',1370011,'Silentblade showed me that one of his secrets was to collect up old rusty weapons from the undead. Soaking the weapons in acid and giving them a new coat of paint make them look brand new. I\'m not sure I would ever buy anything from him if I wanted to live longer than my next battle.','Quests/BeggarsCourt/free_wares_for_silentblade.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5655,'Get Rich Quick!','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',10,0,'Silentblade has offered to teach me another one of his arms dealer secrets. I need to bring this supply of maces to Arms Dealer Blort that he\'s been waiting for. Supposedly this is part of the secret.',1370011,'I\'ve been shown by Arms Dealer Silentblade that one of the best ways to make money as an arms dealer is to let other people make it for you. It seems the trick is to get a bunch of people to buy from you, and when they have enough recruits, they can sell those weapons to other Arms Dealers. I may look into this someday. It seems I could get rich quick this way!','Quests/BeggarsCourt/get_rich_quick.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5656,'Joining the Gang','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',9,1,'Manius Gala runs a protection racket. When you ask to join the gang, he sends you on a little test... I need to kill some of the Freeport raiders in the Sunken City.  I can reach the Sunken City by using any of the bells in and around the City of Freeport.',1370127,'I\'ve killed the raider lackeys as Manius asked, completing my test. He said he\'ll think about letting me join, as he hasn\'t decided yet. I should check back with him later.','Quests/BeggarsCourt/joining_the_gang.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5657,'Donations from the Banker','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',9,0,'Manius Galla has one more task for you to see if you can be trusted in the gang: go collect a \'withdrawal\' from the banker. If he balks, ask if his family can afford to have any more accidents. If you don\'t bring back the money, you can expect to have your own accident. I need to speak with the banker in Beggar\'s Court and make sure he hands over his \'donation\'.',1370127,'I\'ve collected the \'donation\' from the banker and given it to Manius. I\'ve also told Manius what the banker said about him. Needless to say, he wasn\'t too happy. I just realized that I forgot to ask him about joining his gang. Maybe I\'ll ask him some other time.','Quests/BigBend/donations_from_the_banker.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5658,'A Journey Outside the City','The Ruins','The Ruins',10,0,'Captain Arellius in the Ruins has advised that I seek out adventures in the Commonlands. I should leave the gates of the City of Freeport and seek loyal subjects of the Overlord.',1270000,'I traveled outside the city gates and found Mooshga, an ogre who needs my help, as well as Gerun Pontian of the Freeport Militia. After completing some tasks for them, I should remember to journey back to the Ruins and finish my work there.','Quests/TheRuins/a_journey_outside_the_city.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5659,'Marcus Cantarius\'s Monumental Hatred','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',14,1,'I spoke with a human in Beggar\'s Court by the name of Marcus Cantarius, who has an unrivaled hatred for the dervish thugs in Commonlands. He wants me to seek out dervish thug scalps to decorate his home. I don\'t know why he has such a personal grievance, but if it means my getting some sort of reward to help him out, I\'m all for it.',1370042,'It was a long and arduous task killing so many dervish thugs, but the reward was well worth the effort!','Quests/BeggarsCourt/marcus_cantariuss_monumental_hatred.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5660,'Deliver Help to Janus Fieri','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',15,1,'Marcus Cantarius has a friend out at the\r\nCrossroads in the Commonlands, working\r\non an investigation. He has a lead for this\r\nfriend, and wants you to deliver it. I need to deliver this note to Janus Fieri at the Crossroads in the Commonlands.',1370042,'I\'ve delivered Marcus\' note to Janus and helped Janus with his murder investigation.  Turns out he was investigating his own brother\'s death.  It was a pleasure to help him take vengeance.','Quests/BeggarsCourt/deliver_help_to_janus_fieri.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5661,'Problem Solving','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',9,1,'I need to send a message to the vagrant squatters in the Ruins.  The message will involve a lot of them breathing dirt.',1260020,'I\'ve taken care of Crispin\'s problem. It shouldn\'t be long before his business partner decides to step in line.','Quests/BeggarsCourt/problem_solving.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5662,'Advanced Problem Solving','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',10,1,'I\'ve taken on another job from Crispin. I need to save his gang this time by taking care of a gang called the Giantslayers.',1260020,'I\'ve taken care of Crispin\'s problem. It seems that the guy isn\'t as tough as he acts.','Quests/BeggarsCourt/advanced_problem_solving.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5663,'Siricus and the Militia','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',8,0,'Hiding inside one of the homes in Beggar\'s Court is a guy by the name of Siricus. He believes that if he joins the Freeport Militia all of his troubles will go away. I\'ve offered to help him achieve this dream.',1370045,'Siricus Calventius is waiting to get into the Militia. I have a good feeling he\'ll be waiting a lot longer, considering how people treat the gimp.','Quests/BeggarsCourt/siricus_and_the_militia.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5664,'The Nyghtfallow Heirloom','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',8,1,'I\'ve been hired by Tsuul Nyghtfallow within Beggar\'s Court to retrieve his family heirloom. The heirloom, a pendant, will likely be found in the possession of one of the Guttersnipe hooligans who dwell in the Sprawl.',1370025,'I found and killed the dervish that held Tsuul Nyghtfallow\'s family pendant.  The item given in return is nice enough.','Quests/BeggarsCourt/the_nyghtfallow_heirloom.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5665,'To Spite a Darkleaf','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',10,1,'I have determined that Mariana Darkleaf has a bit of an attitude problem. While trying to have a friendly conversation with her, she treated me like I was a nobody. In the end, she insinuated that I get bit by a snake and die. I\'ve decided to do just that... except not die.',1370014,'Mariana Darkleaf wasn\'t too pleased to see me return - alive, that is. Even though it took some time out of my day to kill those snakes, it was still worth it just to see her face when I returned.','Quests/BeggarsCourt/to_spite_a_darkleaf.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5666,'Running For A Candidate','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',8,1,'I was hoping that Mariana Darkleaf would have had something more difficult to do. Instead, she has me delivering a message. I think my attempt at bothering her has backfired.',1370014,'I think I may have stumbled into some intrigue in the district. It seems that Lurina Galla and Mariana Darkleaf have something going on that involves Elowyn the Half-Elf. I wonder if one day I\'ll find out more about what\'s going on. No sense bothering Mariana again. For now.','Quests/BeggarsCourt/running_for_a_candidate.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5667,'Finding the Stash ','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',3,0,'I need to locate the hidden stash of items Alucius is looking for. He said it should be in one of the northwestern rooms.',1370005,'I was able to locate the hidden stash Alucius wanted. I have returned what I found to him.','Quests/BeggarsCourt/finding_the_stash_.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5668,'Saving History','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',4,1,'I need to locate a shady thug who has false historical records concerning the last war.',1370005,'I was able to remove the shady thug, put a halt to his horrible rumors about the Overlord, and return the false historical documents to Alucius.','Quests/BeggarsCourt/saving_history.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5669,'Big Trouble in Beggar\'s Court','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',4,0,'I need to locate Durio and sell this package to him.',1370005,'That snake Alucius was trying to sell off the fake documents I obtained for him earlier! I turned over the documents to a captain of the Freeport Militia as Durio suggested. Not only was I rewarded, but it felt good to be able to help Freeport and preserve the reputation of the Overlord.','Quests/BeggarsCourt/big_trouble_in_beggars_court.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5670,'Tricking the Traitor','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',5,0,'I need to go confront Alucius and convince him of his wrong doing.',1370027,'I have spoken with Alucius, and was able to convince him I am not to be messed with. I guess the thought of being marked as a traitor by the Overlord worked well.','Quests/BeggarsCourt/tricking_the_traitor.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5671,'Meet the Inquisitor','Beggars Court','Beggars Court',5,1,'I need to locate Inquisitor Thorson. I should use the bell to summon transport to the Sunken City.',1370027,'I\'ve spoken with Inquisitor Thorson in the Sunken City. I should be able to learn much more from him.','Quests/BeggarsCourt/meet_the_inquisitor.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5672,'A Special Perfume','Longshadow Alley','Longshadow Alley',5,1,'Zelina T\'Von needs assistance gathering\r\nscent glands from squalid vermin in the\r\nRuins so that she can make a perfume with\r\nwhich to entice her husband. I need to travel to the Ruins and gather a large scent gland from a small rodent.',1380033,'Zelina has given me some coin for gathering the scent gland. She should have enough to be able to make that perfume she was planning on making. If she wants to make a perfume that smell like wine, I don\'t see why she doesn\'t just use wine. Go figure.','Quests/LongshadowAlley/a_special_perfume.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5673,'For That Special Someone','Longshadow Alley','Longshadow Alley',7,0,'Zelina T\'Von is pleased with your contribution\r\nto her perfume and now seeks your\r\nassistance to take a bottle of wine to her\r\nhusband. I should bring this wine to the banker here in Longshadow Alley.',1380033,'It seems that Zelina isn\'t married to T\'val, and she tricked me into giving him some poisoned wine. I\'m not sure what\'s going on between the two, but it looks like I just got myself involved in something more than I had expected.','Quests/LongshadowAlley/for_that_special_someone.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5674,'Dead Man\'s Eyes','Longshadow Alley','Longshadow Alley',8,1,'Divek L\'Narr is bent on avenging his brother\'s murder from many centuries ago. To do this, he needs to perform a ritual that requires a pair of zombie eyes. I need to kill zombies, then choose the least rotted pair of eyes. I should be able to find some in the Graveyard.',1380029,'Divek has paid me for the eyes that he claims will be used to look for his brother\'s soul. I have been warned not to interrupt his ritual. At least I was paid for the job.','Quests/LongshadowAlley/dead_mans_eyes.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5675,'No Rivals For Yarana','Longshadow Alley','Longshadow Alley',20,2,'Yarana D\'Ven is an ambitious Dark Elf who seeks assistance in thwarting her rival\'s research and activities.',1380028,'Yarana will deal directly with her rival, but I\'ve done what she asked. She even gave me a reward, which seemed unusual, but I\'m not complaining.','Quests/LongshadowAlley/no_rivals_for_yarana_part_i.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5676,'Ogre Watch','Longshadow Alley','Longshadow Alley',6,0,'Orian D\'Rak in Longshadow Alley has asked me to deliver a message to Azreana, an Erudite in Stonestair Byway. The message appears to be written in some type of script I am unfamiliar with.',1380039,'Azreana was able to understand what the message said, and acted as if it was rather important. I might want to check back with Orian at a later time to see if he needs any more help.','Quests/LongshadowAlley/ogre_watch.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5677,'Information Gathering From a Fishmonger','Longshadow Alley','Longshadow Alley',6,0,'Orian D\'Rak needs information about a meeting location from Tilzak the fishmonger. I need to see if I can get him to tell me the information I need.',1380039,'Orian D\'Rak has decided to slow down his information gathering efforts. He will continue with his information gathering personally for now. He did reward me with some coin for my efforts, though.','Quests/LongshadowAlley/information_gathering_from_a_fishmonger.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5678,'Taking it Out on the Raiders','Longshadow Alley','Longshadow Alley',8,1,'Maliz T\'Rann, a rather angry dark elf in Longshadow Alley has suggested that I kill some  menacing Freeport raiders in the Sunken City. I\'ll kill ten of them before I consider my work complete.',1380030,'I have killed the raider kingpin like Maliz asked. I may catch my breath and kill some more of these raiders, or maybe see if Maliz had anything else he wanted me to do.','Quests/LongshadowAlley/taking_it_out_on_the_raiders.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5679,'A Dramatic Performance','Longshadow Alley','Longshadow Alley',8,0,'Malix T\'Raan feels more confident in your abilities after you killed the Freeport Raiders, and wants you to deliver a message to Pavo in Beggar\'s Court.',1380030,'Maliz seemed a lot different than I was expecting. He accepted the message, and suggested I talk to his friend, Inmat, for some more employment. I\'m curious as to what this is all about.','Quests/LongshadowAlley/a_dramatic_performance.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5680,'A Shady Clearing','Longshadow Alley','Longshadow Alley',8,1,'Imnat D\'Vren has hired me on to help his group complete their agenda. They are awaiting some type of treasure, and will be transporting it through the sewers. I need to make sure the way is cleared first.',1380031,'I\'ve cleared the way for Imnat\'s treasure to show up. I\'m not sure what this is all about, but it feels rather important. Imnat said that in time I may be told more about how this treasure will \'liberate\' the Teir\'Dal from Lucan\'s grasp.','Quests/LongshadowAlley/a_shady_clearing.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5681,'The Missing Book','Longshadow Alley','Longshadow Alley',9,0,'Lotni K\'ira is angry! She let her house for a few minutes and when she returned home, she saw a female Ratonga leaving her house with a book. She needs your help tracking down the dirty rat! I need to find and speak to the Ratonga who stole Lotni\'s book.',1380009,'Lotni claims she already spoke to the mastermind behind the theft. Unfortunately, she already killed him when his answers were not satisfactory. I doubt she will ever get her book back.','Quests/LongshadowAlley/the_missing_book.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5682,'Magical Retribution','Longshadow Alley','Longshadow Alley',10,1,'Lotni K’ira seeks the death of Black Magi, as they have stolen her precious spell book. Steal it back before they can use it! I should travel to the Sprawl and kill those Black Magi. I won\'t be done until I\'ve killed at least ten of them.',1380009,'I have killed a number of the Black Magi. They appear to have taught a number of their kin how to use magic, so they\'re not all dead. I\'ll decide whether to kill some more or just continue on. Either way, at least ten of them will no longer practice the forbidden magics.  Neither will the last one need the magical necklace it possessed.','Quests/LongshadowAlley/magical_retribution.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5683,'The Stolen Artifacts of Thex','Longshadow Alley','Longshadow Alley',10,0,'Kylanith D\'Lar needs information regarding five stolen Thex artifacts. I must go to Big Bend and find all five of the Thex artifacts relocated there.',1380032,'I discovered all five relocated Thex artifacts in Freeport. Kylanith D\'Lar in Longshadow Alley was pleased with my report.','Quests/LongshadowAlley/the_stolen_artifacts_of_thex.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5684,'The Truth is out There','Longshadow Alley','Longshadow Alley',6,0,'I\'ve been asked by Captain L\'Nek to investigate the matter of the Thexians. It seems there\'s a local group who\'s spreading dissension among the Teir\'Dal, and they\'ve been a lot more vocal as of late.',1380010,'I\'ve found the identity of the person who\'s been behind the propaganda due to the help of an informant by the name of Imnat D\'Vren. Captain L\'Nek says he\'ll be acting on the matter personally.','Quests/LongshadowAlley/the_truth_is_out_there.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5685,'Silenced Speech','Longshadow Alley','Longshadow Alley',8,1,'I\'ve offered to end the life of Kirs G\'Viz due to him spreading seditious propaganda. Captain L\'Nek claimed he\'ll be looking the other way while I take care of this business.',1380010,'The Captain didn\'t necessarily give me the reward I was expecting for helping him with Kirs. I guess I shouldn\'t have expected much.','Quests/LongshadowAlley/silenced_speech.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5688,'Door to Door Anger','Scale Yard','Scale Yard',5,0,'Evelyn Stoutfist in Scale Yard has asked me to find Plordo the gnome and ask him for her money back. I might want to check the Temple District, home to gnomes and ratonga.',1390023,'Evelyn Stoutfist was pretty upset when she heard the news about not getting a refund. I think she\'s planning to do something to the gnome.','Quests/ScaleYard/door_to_door_anger.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5689,'The Great Flood','Blackburrow','Blackburrow',15,1,'At first I thought this was a blank book, into which I could record my own thoughts. However, if you hold the pages toward the light, you can read the story of a natural disaster that happened in Blackburrow. According to the first page, several copies of this book were made, so I might be able to replace some of the smudged pages.',0,'Turns out that this is the story of someone who was trapped in a lower tunnel of Blackburrow during the Age of Cataclysms, when many of the lower tunnels were flooded. Although it doesn\'t come out and say so, I believe the person perished.','Quests/Blackburrow/the_great_flood.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5690,'Ending the Fury','Scale Yard','Scale Yard',8,1,'Dunn Coldbrow has told me that Lucan will allow the Barbarians to be the first to wipe out the Orcs. According to his advisor, Verin Ithelz, this will only happen if the Barbarians manage to kill a number of Darkblade furies in the sewers.',1390036,'I\'ve helped kill the Darkblade furies in the sewers. I have no idea what this has to do with the Barbarians killing the Orcs, though. I have a feeling Dunn\'s Iksar advisor, Verin Ithelz, is pursuing his own agenda rather than helping the Barbarians.','Quests/ScaleYard/ending_the_fury.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5691,'Avoiding the Sea Beasties','Scale Yard','Scale Yard',11,1,'I\'ve taken on a task from Warchief Coldbrow that involves me testing the patience of Lucan\'s will.',1390036,'Dunn Coldbrow has chosen to ask Verin why I wasn\'t killed by Lucan when I killed the orcs. I think I can see how his \'advisor\' may be the real Warchief. Dunn doesn\'t seem to have much common sense, only a very strong presence.','Quests/ScaleYard/avoiding_the_sea_beasties.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5692,'Icebrew\'s Secret Recipe','Scale Yard','Scale Yard',5,1,'Icebrew, the Bartender in Scale Yard, has asked me to gather together ten jars of rust monster blood. He says that the blood is actually liquid rust. I\'ll take his word for it.',1390051,'Icebrew has given me my money and my free beer. I think I\'ll hold onto the beer for now... it seems more like a weapon than a drink.','Quests/ScaleYard/icebrews_secret_recipe.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5693,'Blind Taste Test','Scale Yard','Scale Yard',6,0,'Icebrew the bartender wants me to have a Dark Elf in Longshadow Alley test his brew. I need to travel there, look for a tavern, and find someone to drink it.',1390051,'Icebrew the Bartender was pretty happy about this batch of Wheat Rust Stout. Even though it rendered someone blind and nearly killed them. I, for one, have no plans on drinking anything of his.','Quests/ScaleYard/blind_taste_test.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5694,'Sword-Chucks of Doom','Scale Yard','Scale Yard',6,0,'Once I find Briac Tundrafire, I need to tell him his \'sword-chucks\' are in.',1390046,'Shilza has paid me for giving Briac the message his \'sword-chucks\' are in. I\'m not too sure which person Shilza was referring to when she said that weapon would sever someone\'s head from their shoulders.','Quests/ScaleYard/swordchucks_of_doom.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5695,'Tasty Tears of the Thralls','Scale Yard','Scale Yard',8,1,'Dyerth said I should be able to find some Brokentusk shamans in the Ruins, so that\'s where I should start.',1390054,'Dyerth appreciated my helping her with making her drink. Perhaps someday in the future I may call on her to pay back the favor.','Quests/ScaleYard/tasty_tears_of_the_thralls.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5696,'The Chomper','Blackburrow','Blackburrow',16,2,'I\'ve found an odd object - a broken morningstar. I think there is more to this object than meets the eye.',0,'Applying a little bit of effort, I\'ve been able to change the broken morningstar into the Chomper.','Quests/Blackburrow/the_chomper.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5697,'Mancatcher ','Blackburrow','Blackburrow',16,1,'I\'ve found an odd staff with ropes wrapping its entire length. I don\'t believe it is intended to be used as just a staff alone. Perhaps the gnolls of Blackburrow may have a piece of what was intended to be attached to this odd staff.',0,'I\'ve managed to collect all the pieces that were once attached to this staff. It\'s now an intricate device, possibly of gnomish make. It looks as if it\'s intended to be used to catch opponents in addition to damaging them - like a mancatcher of sorts.','Quests/Blackburrow/mancatcher.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5698,'Orcish Manacles','Blackburrow','Blackburrow',16,1,'I\'ve found an odd object - a pair of handcuffs. I think there is more to this object than meets the eye.',0,'Applying a little bit of effort, I\'ve been able to change the handcuffs into a Orcish Manacles.\r\n','Quests/Blackburrow/orcish_manacles.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5699,'Spiked Bracelet ','Blackburrow','Blackburrow',16,1,'I\'ve found an odd object - a spiked strip of leather. I think there is more to this object than meets the eye.',0,'Applying a little bit of effort, I\'ve been able to change the spiked strip of leather into a Spiked Bracelet.','Quests/Blackburrow/spiked_bracelet.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5700,'Unfinished Breastplate','Blackburrow','Blackburrow',16,1,'I\'ve found an odd object - an unfinished breastplate. I think there is more to this object than meets the eye.',0,'Applying a little bit of effort, I\'ve been able to change the unfinished breastplate into some Gnawed Mail.','Quests/Blackburrow/unfinished_breastplate.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5701,'Verin\'s New Thralls','Scale Yard','Scale Yard',6,1,'Verin Ithelz, an Iksar in Scale Yard, has asked me to go to the Sprawl and kill ten guttersnipe crooks. I am to see how long it takes before they die, then report back to him.',1390020,'Verin paid me for testing the dervish crooks\' mettle and let me keep one of their manacles. He told me that he may have further use of me in the future, so I should check back with him later.','Quests/ScaleYard/verins_new_thralls.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5702,'Preventative Maintenance','Scale Yard','Scale Yard',6,1,'Verin has asked me to kill ten exiled orcs in the Ruins to prevent his rival from using them as thralls. Once I have killed them, I will need to return to him for my payment.',1390020,'Verin seems like he\'s a rather powerful person in Scale Yard. I don\'t think I\'ll want to cross him. He paid me for killing his rival\'s stock of potential thralls and even threw in a shield for my trouble.','Quests/ScaleYard/preventative_maintenance.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5703,'Will Work for War','Scale Yard','Scale Yard',5,0,'Colin Stoutfist wants you to find and ask Warchief Coldbrow when the attack on the orcs will be. I need to find and speak with this so-called Warchief.',1390052,'Colin Stoutfist is quite upset with the state of things in Scale Yard. It seems he has nothing to do, and began to make an unpleasant comment about his Warchief. He had the wisdom to stop mid-sentence.','Quests/ScaleYard/will_work_for_war.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5704,'Slaying the Giants','Scale Yard','Scale Yard',7,1,'Colin Stoutfist wants you to put a bit of pressure on the giantslayer thugs in the Sprawl so they will accept Warchief Coldbrow as their leader.',1390052,'I returned to Colin to tell him of my victory!','Quests/ScaleYard/will_fight_for_fun.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5705,'The Sabertooth Miner\'s Guide, Part One','Blackburrow','Blackburrow',12,1,'Apparently, this is a basic mining history of the Sabertooth gnolls of Blackburrow. Some pages are torn and others are duplicated several times over. If I want to read the whole thing, I\'ll have to get the correct pages in Blackburrow myself.',0,'There is a Part Two that continues the history of the Blackburrow gnolls. It might be interesting to see how they handled the influx of the \"furless.\"','Quests/Blackburrow/the_sabertooth_miners_guide_part_one.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5706,'The Sabertooth Miner\'s Guide, Part Two','Blackburrow','Blackburrow',15,1,'This is the second part of the mining guide written by the Sabertooth gnolls themselves. I had no idea they could write, let alone fill two volumes. As one would expect, they botched the book binding so that there are several duplicates and many missing pages. Looks like I\'ll have to comb Blackburrow myself to find the rest of the pages. Stupid gnolls.',0,'Until I read this book, I had no notion of the Sabertooth gnolls\' history in Blackburrow. I\'m still not entirely sure, but it was a interesting to see how the changing of our world changed the gnolls. Evidently, not much.','Quests/Blackburrow/the_sabertooth_miners_guide_part_two.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5707,'A filthy bronze key','Blackburrow','Blackburrow',16,1,'I found a key on a gnoll. This one appears to be filthy and made of bronze. Perhaps it was used by the gnoll to store its valuables.',0,'Inside the chest, I found the remains of the gnoll\'s personal property.','Quests/Blackburrow/a_filthy_bronze_key.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5708,'Polished steel key','Blackburrow','Blackburrow',16,1,'I found a key on a gnoll. This one appears to be tarnished with age and made of silver. Perhaps it was used by the gnoll to store its valuables.',0,'Inside the chest, I found the remains of the gnoll\'s personal property.','Quests/Blackburrow/polished_steel_key.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5709,'A tarnished silver key','Blackburrow','Blackburrow',17,1,'I found a key on a gnoll. This one appears to be tarnished with age and made of silver. Perhaps it was used by the gnoll to store its valuables.',0,'Inside the chest, I found the remains of the gnoll\'s personal property.','Quests/Blackburrow/a_tarnished_silver_key.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5710,'A grubby bone key','Blackburrow','Blackburrow',20,1,'I found a key on a gnoll. This one appears to be grubby and made of bone. Perhaps it was used by the gnoll to store its valuables.',0,'Inside the chest, I found the remains of the gnoll\'s personal property.','Quests/Blackburrow/a_grubby_bone_key.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5711,'Poisonous Zever','Scale Yard','Scale Yard',15,7,'Zever Tzizzink, an iksar in the Scale Yard, was apparently poisoned by someone named V\'shra. Zever\'s asked me to gather the ingredients for the antidote since he\'s too weak to get them himself. He\'s offered to pay me for my time.',1390024,'That double-crossing sneak! Instead of getting ingredients for an antidote, Zever had me gathering ingredients for a deadly poison! He thought he gave me a piece of junk for a reward, but he was mistaken!','Quests/ScaleYard/poisonous_zever_CLASSIC.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5712,'Relics for Elurad','Stormhold','Stormhold',20,2,'Archaeologist Elurad has requested that I find three lost relics that will help him piece together some of the history of what has happened in Stormhold.',150001,'I managed to retrieve the mace, tome and chalice from the depths of Befallen. Elurad seemed very pleased with the results.','Quests/Stormhold/relics_for_elurad.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5713,'Test Quest with ONLY Exp','Test','Unknown',1,1,'Testing quest with only exp reward.',0,'Testing quest with only exp reward.','Quests/Unknown/test_quest_with_only_exp.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5714,'The Cavemaw\'s Sinister Map','Antonica','Antonica',17,1,'Reading the map has made it obvious that the gnolls are planning something bigger than just mining the hills of Antonica. The Cavemaw tunnelers seem to be the key to the whole thing, I should stop them!',0,'I have slain a large amount of the seemingly limitless supply of Cavemaw tunnelers. I hope my efforts slowed them down a bit.','Quests/Antonica/the_cavemaws_sinister_map.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5715,'Peckett\'s Patrol','Antonica','Antonica',11,1,'I have learned that Corporal Peckett of the Coldwind Point Garrison is in need of aid in patrolling the lighthouse sector of Antonica.',0,'I patrolled the lighthouse sector of Antonica for Corporal Peckett. I found Captain Antillin and learned that he has discovered a gnoll den. He returned to plot its location.','Quests/Antonica/pecketts_patrol.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5716,'The Whereabouts of Clan McMarrin','Antonica','Antonica',23,1,'I met a barbarian named Tanen Danos who spoke of an old clan of Halas called Clan McMarrin. He mentioned that the clan set out on an expedition to find a land of their own following the Shattering. No word has been heard of them since their departure.',120289,'I found a journal of Clan McMarrian at a destroyed site in the Thundering Steppes. I sold the journal to Tanen Danos as he was eager to learn the fate of the clan. I don\'t think there is much hope for the clan considering the mess I found.','Quests/Antonica/the_whereabouts_of_clan_mcmarrin.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5717,'Qeynos Alignment','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'I have spoken with Ambassador Saera about the great city of Qeynos. Her words lead me to believe that I will be most at home within Antonia Bayle\'s lands.',0,'I have successfully arrived in Qeynos and gotten situated here.  I would prefer better quarters, and to live in the city, but I suppose I\'ll have to work towards that on my own.','Quests/MultipleZones/qeynos_alignment.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5718,'Baubbleshire Citizenship Task','Hallmark','Hallmark',6,1,'The task list requires that all citizens of Baubbleshire gather tokens from the Caves in order to show their worth to the citizenship officials.',0,'The task list is completed and you may now apply to become a citizen of the city of Qeynos.','Quests/Hallmark/baubbleshire_citizenship_task.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5719,'Castleview Citizenship Task','Hallmark','Hallmark',6,1,'The task list requires that all citizens of Castleview Hamlet gather tokens from the Down Below in order to show their worth to the citizenship officials.',0,'The task list is completed and you may now apply to become a citizen of the city of Qeynos.','Quests/Hallmark/castleview_citizenship_task.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5720,'Graystone Citizenship Task','Hallmark','Hallmark',6,1,'The task list requres that all citizens of Graystone Yard gather tokens from the Oakmyst Forest in order to show their worth to the citizenship officials.',0,'The task list is completed and you may now apply to become a citizen of the city of Qeynos.','Quests/Hallmark/graystone_citizenship_task.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5721,'Nettleville Citizenship Task','Hallmark','Hallmark',6,1,'The task list requires that all citizens of Nettleville gather tokens from the Peat Bog in order to show their worth to the citizenship officials.',0,'The task list is completed and you may now apply to become a citizen of the city of Qeynos.','Quests/Hallmark/nettleville_citizenship_task.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5722,'Starcrest Citizenship Task','Hallmark','Hallmark',6,1,'The task list requires that all citizens of Starcrest Commune gather tokens from the Down Below in order to show their worth to the citizenship officials.',0,'The task list is completed and you may now apply to become a citizen of the city of Qeynos.','Quests/Hallmark/starcrest_citizenship_task.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5723,'Willow Wood Citizenship Task','Hallmark','Hallmark',6,1,'The task list requires that all citizens of Willow Wood gather tokens from the Forest Ruins in order to show their worth to the citizenship officials.',0,'The task list is completed and you may now apply to become a citizen of the city of Qeynos.','Quests/Hallmark/willow_wood_citizenship_task.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5724,'Cutlass Cleaning','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',5,1,'I found an old blade that was on a ghost pirate captain. It is covered in rust and sea salt but it may still have some use left in it. I should find someone in the outpost who could clean it up for me.',0,'Mender Mannus was able to repair the blade as good as new.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/cutlass_cleaning.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5725,'Archetype Selection','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'I must report my profession to Garven Tralk.',0,'I have reported my profession to Garven Tralk.','Quests/Hallmark/archetype_selection.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5726,'Gruttooth Invasion','Hallmark','Hallmark',3,1,'I\'ve arrived on the Isle of Refuge and am apparently in the middle of a war between the port town here and the local goblins living on the island. Garven Tralk has already pressed me into the service of defending the town, a duty I must accept if I ever hope to leave this island.',3250020,'I successfully helped fend off one of the nearly constant goblin raids on this island, even managing to kill one of the invaders myself.  Garven has instructed me to seek out the trainer of my profession on the Isle for further tasks.  With any luck I\'ll be headed for one of the larger cities sometime soon.','Quests/Hallmark/gruttooth_invasion_fighter.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5727,'Gruttooth Invasion','Hallmark','Hallmark',3,1,'I\'ve arrived on the Isle of Refuge and am apparently in the middle of a war between the port town here and the local goblins living on the island. Garven Tralk has already pressed me into the service of defending the town, a duty I must accept if I ever hope to leave this island.',3250020,'I successfully helped fend off one of the nearly constant goblin raids on this island, even managing to kill one of the invaders myself.  Garven has instructed me to seek out the trainer of my profession on the Isle for further tasks.  With any luck I\'ll be headed for one of the larger cities sometime soon.','Quests/Hallmark/gruttooth_invasion_priest.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5728,'Gruttooth Invasion','Hallmark','Hallmark',3,1,'I\'ve arrived on the Isle of Refuge and am apparently in the middle of a war between the port town here and the local goblins living on the island. Garven Tralk has already pressed me into the service of defending the town, a duty I must accept if I ever hope to leave this island.',3250020,'I successfully helped fend off one of the nearly constant goblin raids on this island, even managing to kill one of the invaders myself.  Garven has instructed me to seek out the trainer of my profession on the Isle for further tasks.  With any luck I\'ll be headed for one of the larger cities sometime soon.','Quests/Hallmark/gruttooth_invasion_mage.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5729,'Gruttooth Invasion','Hallmark','Hallmark',3,1,'I\'ve arrived on the Isle of Refuge and am apparently in the middle of a war between the port town here and the local goblins living on the island. Garven Tralk has already pressed me into the service of defending the town, a duty I must accept if I ever hope to leave this island.',3250020,'I successfully helped fend off one of the nearly constant goblin raids on this island, even managing to kill one of the invaders myself.  Garven has instructed me to seek out the trainer of my profession on the Isle for further tasks.  With any luck I\'ll be headed for one of the larger cities sometime soon.','Quests/Hallmark/gruttooth_invasion_scout.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5730,'Speaking with Vladiminn ','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'Garven Tralk mentioned that I should speak with Vladiminn further about being a scout.',3250020,'I\'ve spoken with Vladiminn about being a scout as Garven Tralk.','Quests/Hallmark/speaking_with_vladiminn_.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5731,'Speaking with Braksan','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'Garven Tralk has bid me speak with Braksan Steelforge in the village about further information regarding being a fighter.',3250020,'I\'ve spoken with Braksan Steelforge as per Garven Tralk\'s instructions.','Quests/Hallmark/speaking_with_braksan.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5732,'Speaking with Nathinia','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'Garven Tralk has bid me go to speak with Nathinia Sparklebright in the village.',3250020,'I\'ve spoken with Nathinia Sparklebright in the village as Garven asked.','Quests/Hallmark/speaking_with_nathinia.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5733,'Speaking with Mizan','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'Garven Tralk has bid me speak with Mizan Vaeoulin about further mage information.',3250020,'I have spoken with Mizan Vaeoulin as Garven Tralk bid me.','Quests/Hallmark/speaking_with_mizan.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5734,'War Statues','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',3,1,'Nathinia Sparklebright has asked me to further aid the outpost by destroying some sacred goblin statues. Apparently there are Gruttooth mystics who draw their powers from these statues and only the divine might of a priest can destroy them. My task is to destroy three of these statues.',3250014,'With the power of my smite spell I was able to destroy three of the war statues.  With their mystics weakened the goblins should have a much harder time with their assaults on the outpost.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/war_statues.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5735,'Goblin Supply Raid','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',3,1,'Braksan Steelforge has recruited me to help in raiding the goblin supply camp to the west. I am to look for the supply runners and take them out so that mages in the camp can destroy their supplies.',3250017,'With the supply runners I killed, the mages shouldn\'t have much of a problem destroying the supply crates.  Hopefully this combined effort will set the goblin advance back a few steps.  ','Quests/IsleofRefuge/goblin_supply_raid.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5736,'Destroying the Goblin\'s Supplies','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',3,1,'Mizan Vaeoulin has recruited me to help with the effort to turn back the goblin aggressors. He heard about my work against the attackers at the barricade and wanted to know if I could help him. He wants me to destroy five goblin supply crates at a forward supply camp the goblins are using to stage the attacks.',3250057,'Mizan was grateful for my help and rewarded me with a pair of boots he placed in my bank.  Hopefully my work contributed to slow down the goblins attacks.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/destroying_the_goblins_supplies.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5737,'Deer Hunting','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',3,1,'Vladiminn has sent me out to help gather food for the other refugees on the island. I\'m sure everyone else will be doing their part as well. I know for certain that the priests will be doing so. Vladiminn explained that they\'ll be helping to cure the diseased deer so that I can hunt and gather meat from the healthy ones.',3250016,'I\'ve gathered enough meat for quite a few new refugees with the help of the priests curing the strange disease the deer have come down with.  Vladiminn rewarded me with some supple boots to help while stalking my prey.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/deer_hunting.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5738,'Venom Sac Collection','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',3,1,'It appears the goblins are using spider venom on their spears to poison the outpost\'s defenders. Nathinia Sparklebright asked if I would assist in the effort by collecting giant spider venom sacs so that she can create an antidote to combat the poison.',3250014,'I was able to collect five giant spider venom sacs and give them to Nathinia.  She is going to get to work immediately on creating an antidote.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/venom_sac_collection.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5739,'Refugee Rescue','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',3,1,'Braksan Steelforge informed me that a few refugees have gotten into trouble out in the wilderness. The outpost wasn\'t able to organize a rescue party yet and wanted to know if I could help free the people from their goblin captors. He advised me for the safety of the prisoners to taunt the creatures away from the refugees before engaging them in battle.',3250017,'I dispatched five of those Gruttooth aggressors that were holding the refugees captive and told Braksan that the refugees should be able to return to the outpost now.  He rewarded me with a new pair of protective leggings.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/refugee_rescue.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5740,'Gathering Sealant Components','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',3,1,'Mizan Vaeoulin has asked me to help in gathering components to use in making a sealant to protect the barriers against the impending goblin fire attacks. He told me to gather the remains of five mire bogs from the forest of the island.',3250057,'I was able to collect the remains of mire bogs for Mizan.  He is going to use them to create a sealant that will be spread on the wooden barricades to protect them against the impending goblin fire attacks.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/gathering_sealant_components.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5741,'Scouting the Goblin Camp','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',3,1,'Vladiminn has managed to find something else for me to do. Apparently the island officials would like him to scout out the goblin camp and report back to them with the numbers and strength of the goblins. Seeing as how he\'s quite busy with the other refugees and assisting with the gathering of food, I\'ve offered to lend my talents for this task.',3250016,'It seems that the goblin numbers are more than they\'d first expected.  I think Vladiminn will try to recruit me later to help out with the effort to drive back the goblins, but in the meantime, he\'s given me a pair of leggings to match the boots I received earlier.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/scouting_the_goblin_camp.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5742,'Striking Back at the Goblins','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',3,1,'Nathinia informed me that the scouts have discovered the location of the goblin village and that other adventures were taking the offensive to attack it. She wanted me to go along and help them but to also look for goblin totems to collect and bring back to her. She said collecting four of the totems would be enough for her study.',3250014,'I was able to collect four goblin totems for Nathinia and gave them to her for her study.  She may be able to determine the power of the totems and if they are the reason the goblins have become so aggressive.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/striking_back_at_the_goblins.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5743,'Striking Back at the Goblins','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',3,1,'Braksan Steelforge told me that the scouts for the outpost found the location of the goblins\' village to the northwest. He encouraged me to tag along with others who were heading out there to help them in the attack. He also wanted me to collect four flint head spears for him so that he could add them to his arsenal.',3250017,'I joined with others who were attacking the goblin village.  I was able to collect up four flint head spears for Braksan like he asked and deliver them to him.  He was very appreciative of my work and gave me a tunic in payment.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/striking_back_at_the_goblins_fighter.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5744,'Striking Back at the Goblins','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',3,1,'It appears scouts have found the location of the goblin village to the north west of the island. Mizan asked me to help in these attacks and to gather four samples of goblin blood. He mentioned the other adventurers may already have the blood and may be willing to trade for the samples.',3250057,'I was able to collect four goblin blood samples for Mizan and helped with the attacks on the village.  Mizan\'s teacher Malvonicus should be able to put the samples to good use.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/striking_back_at_the_goblins_mage.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5745,'Striking Back at the Goblins','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',3,1,'Vladiminn has finally done it. He\'s sent me off to die. Well, perhaps not, I suppose I could be successful, but he wants me to attack the goblin encampment directly and retrieve the harnesses off of the necks of their wolves.',3250016,'It appears that Vladiminn recognized something about either the workmanship or style of the harnesses I brought him.  He didn\'t explain directly what he meant, only that my part in all this was at an end, though I think if I prod him a bit, he may divulge what he\'s afraid of, or at least what it was he noticed about the collars.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/striking_back_at_the_goblins_scout.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5746,'A Sandy Bone Shard','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',5,1,'I have found a sandy bone shard in the claws of a crab here on the Island of Refuge. After looking closely at it I could see some designs etched on the surface. If I could find the other pieces and fix them I might have something to take from the island when I leave.',0,'I have found all the pieces I needed and put the Scrimshaw Token back together.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/a_sandy_bone_shard.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5747,'X Marks the Spot','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',5,8,'I found what looks to be an old map of the island among the remains of a skeleton. The map had an X marked just east of a waterfall. The map also said that this is \"Rockbelly\'s resting place\". Maybe I should check it out.',0,'The map seemed to have led to the grave of an old sailor.  He wasn\'t resting peacefully though and I had to defend myself against an attack from the grave\'s ghost!  I did manage to get some coin and an old cutlass.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/x_marks_the_spot.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5748,'Stop the Saboteurs','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',5,8,'I found what looks like a plan of attack after killing a goblin leader. It said \"Bossy say to break floaties. Go hide down at beach. Smash and bash next floaty that come. Use hot stickies to burn down floaty. No let more big peoples come here.\" I should take a few allies and investigate this information.',0,'It looks like the goblins were planning to burn down the next ship to pull into port.  We were able to stop them before this happened and slay the little monsters on the beach.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/stop_the_saboteurs.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5749,'Cellar Cleanup','Hallmark','Hallmark',3,1,'Assistant Dreak seems to have made a mess out of Master Mizan\'s cellar! He\'s offered me his personal assurance that I can use the cellar if I clean it up for him.',3250167,'Assistant Dreak was quite pleased with the work I did both in cleaning the cellar and making a bar to keep people out of it. He\'s now granted me full access to the cellar to work on any items I wish to.','Quests/Hallmark/cellar_cleanup.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5750,'Removing the Orc Menace ','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',4,8,'It has been discovered what is causing the goblins to make organized attacks against the outpost. It seems an orc pirate ended up on this island some time ago and has claimed leadership over the goblins, forming his own personal army. I am to go with others to remove this orc from power.',3250014,'I was able to assist in helping remove the orc from power.  In time, the goblins should now stop attacking the outpost and return to a less aggressive nature.  I was awarded a scepter for my part in putting an end to this menace.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/removing_the_orc_menace_.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5751,'Removing the Orc Menace ','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',4,8,'Braksan Steelforge told me that an orc has been seen on the island and that it is likely the cause of the goblins being stirred up to attack. He encouraged me to find others who were willing to hunt down this orc and slay the menace. He told me the orc is most likely holed up in a cave on the northeastern part of the island past the main goblin encampments.',3250017,'I found Grimgash the Black and helped slay him.  That orc will not be organizing raids any time soon... For all my hard work Braksan gave me a buckler as a reward for my service to the outpost.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/removing_the_orc_menace_Fighter.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5752,'Attack on the Orc Leader','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',4,8,'The cause for the goblin attacks has been found. An orc that somehow turned up on the island has organized the attacks in some sort of revenge against the Far Seas Trading Company. I am going to go along with others who are striking out against this menace.',3250057,'The orc leader is now dead.  Hopefully with his death the goblin attacks will stop and the goblins will retreat back from the outposts walls.  Mizan presented me with a staff for all the work I have done for him and the Far Seas settlement.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/attack_on_the_orc_leader.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5753,'Hunting the Orcish Leader','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',4,8,'I\'d thought I was off on a foolish errand before, attacking goblins and their pet wolves in their own domain. Now I know I\'m nuts! Vladiminn has sent me off to go find and kill the leader of the goblins on the island. I bet he\'s some ten-foot tall monstrosity too. Great.',3250016,'As unbelievable as it sounds, I gathered a group of others up and we managed to defeat Grimgash the Black, the leader of the goblins here on the island.  I\'m amazed we did so well, really.  Vladiminn has given me a final parting gift, and bids me off to see the rest of the world now.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/hunting_the_orcish_leader.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5754,'Xaliea\'s Request','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',5,1,'Priestess Xaliea, a dark elf near Ebb Tide\'s Alehouse, is unhappy that she is stuck mending wounds while she would rather be out adventuring. In order to live vicariously through my adventures, she has asked me to bring her three bone chips from some of the local skeletons.',3250009,'I defeated some of the local skeletons and gave Priestess Xaliea the three bone chips. This seemed to satisfy her lust for adventure.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/xalieas_request.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5755,'Ebik\'s Missing Parts','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',3,1,'Ebik Wobblecog is waiting for a ship to Qeynos. He just realized that he\'s missing some parts that his father asked him to collect. Ebik needs a size 7 clunker, a copper-coated springer, and a triangle spinner. I should look around the island for these devices. They could be anywhere!',3250008,'I gave Ebik Wobblecog all the parts he needed. Hopefully now he can meet up with his father and evade their family\'s famous curse.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/ebiks_missing_parts.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5756,'Lasydia\'s Call','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',4,1,'I found a statue under the waters that appears to be of a lesser deity named Lasydia. After reading the inscription chiseled on it I feel a great need to make the waters around me safer. My immediate thought is to remove the threat to others that the razortooth sharks pose.',3250011,'A mysterious sash floated to me out of the water after my desire to slay the vicious sharks left me. I can only guess if it was by accident or by design that the sash found me.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/lasydias_call.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5757,'Aquatic Research','Isle of Refuge','Isle of Refuge',5,1,'I found a research notebook that was apparently left behind by a research assistant tasked to collect specimens for Master Malvonicus. I decided I could finish the work. It sounds like these are all animals that would live in the water. Looks like it is time for a swim!',3250031,'I talked to Master Malvonicus at the top of his tower at outpost. Apparently his apprentice was an irresistible treat for the dreaded Bladefin. He gave me the reward that he had originally planned for his apprentice.','Quests/IsleofRefuge/aquatic_research.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5758,'Freeport Alignment','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'I\'ve spoken with Ambassador T\'kirr, and I\'m sure that Freeport is the place for me to go. The might of the Overlord cannot be denied, and any conflict between Freeport and Qeynos can only have one solution.',3250005,'I\'ve managed to make my way to the city of Freeport.  Although things aren\'t exactly as I was promised by Ambassador T\'Kirr, I will make do until I am able to forge my own destiny.','Quests/Hallmark/freeport_alignment.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5759,'Vaughn\'s Stuff','The Forest Ruins','The Forest Ruins',10,1,'I offered to help Outlander Vaughn recover some of his stolen property. He says the ruins skulkers stole his satchel that had contained many important items. I told him I would help him get his stuff back.',8270029,'I eventually found all of Outlander Vaughn\'s items. He was grateful and asked if I would help him with something else.','Quests/TheForestRuins/vaughns_stuff_CLASSIC.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5760,'Welcome to Qeynos','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'I have arrived in Qeynos and spoke with the Steward of the village. Not only did I receive a warm welcome, I\'ve also been given an inn room to call home.',0,'Thanks to the help of the inn\'s caretaker, I\'ve been able to familiarize myself with the Baubbleshire.  Not only did she show me the way around, she also let me know who to speak to in order to become a citizen.','Quests/Hallmark/welcome_to_qeynos_Baubbleshire.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5761,'Welcome to Qeynos','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'I have arrived in Qeynos and spoke with the Steward of the village. Not only did I receive a warm welcome, I\'ve also been given an inn room to call home.',0,'Thanks to the help of the inn\'s caretaker, I\'ve been able to familiarize myself with the Willow Wood.  Not only did she show me the way around, she also let me know who to speak to in order to become a citizen.','Quests/Hallmark/welcome_to_qeynos_WillowWood.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5762,'Welcome to Qeynos','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'I have arrived in Qeynos and spoke with the Steward of the village. Not only did I receive a warm welcome, I\'ve also been given an inn room to call home.',0,'Thanks to the help of the inn\'s caretaker, I\'ve been able to familiarize myself with Starcrest.  Not only did she show me the way around, she also let me know who to speak to in order to become a citizen.','Quests/Hallmark/welcome_to_qeynos_Starcrest.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5763,'Welcome to Qeynos','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'I have arrived in Qeynos and spoke with the Steward of the village. Not only did I receive a warm welcome, I\'ve also been given an inn room to call home.',0,'Thanks to the help of the inn\'s caretaker, I\'ve been able to familiarize myself with Nettleville.  Not only did she show me the way around, she also let me know who to speak to in order to become a citizen.','Quests/Hallmark/welcome_to_qeynos_Nettleville.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5764,'Welcome to Qeynos','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'I have arrived in Qeynos and spoke with the Steward of the village. Not only did I receive a warm welcome, I\'ve also been given an inn room to call home.',2350184,'Thanks to the help of the inn\'s caretaker, I\'ve been able to familiarize myself with Graystone.  Not only did she show me the way around, she also let me know who to speak to in order to become a citizen.','Quests/Hallmark/welcome_to_qeynos_Graystone.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5765,'Welcome to Qeynos','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'I have arrived in Qeynos and spoke with the Steward of the village. Not only did I receive a warm welcome, I\'ve also been given an inn room to call home.',0,'Thanks to the help of the inn\'s caretaker, I\'ve been able to familiarize myself with Castleview.  Not only did she show me the way around, she also let me know who to speak to in order to become a citizen.','Quests/Hallmark/welcome_to_qeynos_Castleivew.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5766,'Welcome to Qeynos, Citizen!','Hallmark','Hallmark',7,1,'Queen Antonia Bayle provides all new citizens of Qeynos with a copy of this booklet, which explains different experiences I might have while traveling Norrath and how to make the most of them.',0,'While I might have learned these things on my own, it\'s thoughtful of the Queen to provide this information to the citizens of Qeynos. Long live Antonia Bayle!','Quests/Hallmark/welcome_to_qeynos_citizen.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5767,'Mage Training, pt I','Hallmark','Hallmark',8,1,'Magister Niksel has offered to give me some lessons on magic. From what it sounds like, there are different types of magic that one can focus on, and he will be showing them to me.',2310376,'I\'ve learned what a summoner and a sorcerer studies from Niksel\'s lessons.  He has ended my first lesson so that he can write down the magical theory he came up with.  He has offered to teach me more again in the future.','Quests/Hallmark/mage_training_part_1.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5768,'Mage Training, pt II','Hallmark','Hallmark',8,1,'The Magister has offered to continue my lessons in magic. He is giving me a lesson in enchantment this time through. I wonder where my training will take me',2310376,'I\'ve only one task left to do now that I\'ve completed all of Niksel\'s other lessons!','Quests/Hallmark/mage_training_part_2.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5769,'Path of the Sorcerer','Hallmark','Hallmark',10,1,'I have chosen to become a sorcerer. After this final test, I shall have proved myself worthy. I must enter the trial in the room that Niksel set up inside the mage towers.',2310376,'I passed the trial and will continue on my path as a sorcerer.  I know that I cannot be reckless with my power, or these forces may overwhelm me.','Quests/Hallmark/path_of_the_sorcerer(Q).lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5770,'Path of the Summoner','Hallmark','Hallmark',10,1,'I have accepted the challenge of becoming a summoner from Magister Niksel. I believe that the role of Summoner suits my personality above all others, and have chosen my path accordingly. I must enter the trial in the room that Niksel set up inside the mage towers.',2310376,'Having completed my trial as a summoner, I will be focusing my studies in magic down the path I\'ve chosen.  I am well on my way in Norrath - and have learned valuable lessons in responsible summoning.','Quests/Hallmark/path_of_the_summoner.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5771,'Path of the Enchanter','Hallmark','Hallmark',10,1,'I accepted Magister Niksel\'s final test, or so he says. I am to subdue an angry crowd, but Niksel did mention something about being careful, and using everything at my disposal... I suppose I\'ll see what he means when I size up the situation.',2310376,'After thinking about it rationally, I realized that there was no way for those tavern patrons to have been so upset.  So naturally, I went to find the root of their animosity.  Having done so, I find myself in a new role as an enchanter.  I suppose I\'ll have much to learn.','Quests/Hallmark/path_of_the_enchanter(Q).lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5772,'Priest Training, pt I','Hallmark','Hallmark',8,1,'Hierophant Aldalad has offered to guide me on my path to spirituality. From what he has hinted at, there is far more to being one of the faithful than I previously believed.',2220484,'Hierophant Aldalad has shown me the difference between a cleric and a shaman.  I have learned that faith comes from many different avenues.  He has hinted at the fact there are even more paths to learn of, but wishes for me to learn from my experiences before I continue seeing more.','Quests/Hallmark/priest_training_pt_i.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5773,'Priest Training, pt II ','Hallmark','Hallmark',8,1,'Hierophant Aldalad has offered to show me another path to spirituality. I believe when he has shown me all he can, it will be time for me to choose which path I will journey down.',2220484,'I have listened to all that the Hierophant has to offer.  Looking in my heart, I know that there is only one way for me to proceed.  From hereon, I will follow my chosen path to spirituality and never waver from where it leads me.','Quests/Hallmark/priest_training_pt_ii_.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5774,'Path of the Cleric','Hallmark','Hallmark',10,1,'Aldalad will be putting me into a trance-state where I will be sorting out my beliefs, and cementing my faith. After the ordeal, I will surely emerge strong enough to be a cleric.',2220484,'After a somewhat surreal dream, I have cemented my beliefs and become a true cleric.  I stride forth with a renewed faith and will prove my worth to those around me in my adventures to come.','Quests/Hallmark/path_of_the_cleric.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5775,'Path of the Druid','Hallmark','Hallmark',10,1,'I go forth now to become a druid, one dedicated to the cause of nature and our environs. To begin my journey along this path, I must complete a trial which Aldalad has prepared for me. He offered only the advice that I should be prepared to use all the skills I have learned up to this point.',0,'I have completed the trial Aldalad set before me, and am finally ready to journey forth as a druid - a defender of the forests and animals, of those who cannot adequately do so for themselves.','Quests/Hallmark/path_of_the_druid.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5776,'Path of the Shaman','Hallmark','Hallmark',10,1,'Aldalad has tasked me with the removal or pacification of spirits haunting one of the houses here in Qeynos. Though he claims he cannot do it himself, I believe this is more akin to a test of my abilities as I complete my journey to become a shaman. I must venture into the house in South Qeynos, located among the middle row of buildings, and subdue the spirits within.',0,'The spirits I encountered proved quite spiteful, obviously intent on destroying all life around them.  Perhaps their souls were unable to find peace','Quests/Hallmark/path_of_the_shaman.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5777,'Start of Something Big','Enchanted Lands','Enchanted Lands',30,0,'To be collected.',390085,'To be collected.','Quests/EnchantedLands/start_of_something_big.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5778,'Surveyor Says','Enchanted Lands','Enchanted Lands',31,0,'',390085,'','Quests/EnchantedLands/surveyor_says.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5779,'What\'s This Thing Do?','Enchanted Lands','Enchanted Lands',32,0,'',390085,'','Quests/EnchantedLands/whats_this_thing_do.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5780,'Sanity Check','Enchanted Lands','Enchanted Lands',32,0,'To be collected.',390085,'To be collected.','Quests/EnchantedLands/sanity_check.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5781,'Halt, Who Goes There?','Enchanted Lands','Enchanted Lands',32,0,'To be collected.',390183,'To be collected.','Quests/EnchantedLands/halt_who_goes_there.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5782,'Scout Training, pt I','Hallmark','Hallmark',8,1,'Vemerik the Counselor has offered me advice on how to be a better scout. I should do what he suggests.',2220485,'I\'ve learned what it is to be a rogue and a bard, but there will be more to learn in the future. ','Quests/Hallmark/scout_training_pt_i.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5783,'Scout Training, pt II','Hallmark','Hallmark',8,1,'Vemerik has offered to train me further. He is now showing me another way of using my scouting skills.',2220485,'I\'ve learned how uses my skills in better ways.  I\'ve decided to focus on one type of skill in order to excel in my chosen field.  I have only Vemerik to thank for this. ','Quests/Hallmark/scout_training_pt_ii.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5784,'Path of the Bard','Hallmark','Hallmark',10,1,'I\'ve told Vemerik that I can take care of a rather angry crowd that was riled up by a bad performance. If I can handle this, I don\'t see any reason why I can\'t handle any other part of being a bard.',2220485,'I managed to lay out the entire mob single-handedly.  I\'ve proven that even in the off-chance I give a bad performance, I can handle anything the crowd might throw at me.','Quests/Hallmark/path_of_the_bard.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5785,'Path of the Predator','Hallmark','Hallmark',10,1,'After deciding that becoming a predator is best suited to my desires and talents, Vemerik has decided to test my skills by sending me after an assassin group operating inside Qeynos herself.',2220485,'My skills were up to the task and I have succeeded in killing the leader of the ring without alerting the others.  They will undoubtedly break apart now that their leader has perished... and now I have earned the title of predator.','Quests/Hallmark/path_of_the_predator.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5786,'Path of the Rogue','Hallmark','Hallmark',10,1,'In order to prove myself worthy of becoming a rogue, Vemerik has sent me in to try to snatch the orders from one of the Qeynos guard squads. It certainly won\'t be easy, but I believe I will be up to the challenge.',2220485,'I managed to grab the lieutenant\'s orders out from under the watchful eye of the Qeynos guard.  I\'m sure they\'ll be put through some rigorous training after this to help them keep a sharper eye out in the future, but that\'s not my concern now!','Quests/Hallmark/path_of_the_rogue.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5787,'Fighter Training, pt I','Hallmark','Hallmark',8,1,'Master-at-Arms Dagorel has offered to train me in the ways of fighting. He says he\'ll show me the different styles that are commonly pursued.',2310377,'Dagorel, Master-at-Arms of the Council, has shown me two different ways to focus on fighting.  So far I\'ve learned how a warrior and a brawler handle things.  Because my brawler tips got out of hand, Dagorel agreed to show me the last way when I\'ve taken time to recover.','Quests/Hallmark/fighter_training_pt_i.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5788,'Fighter Training, pt II','Hallmark','Hallmark',8,1,'Master-at-Arms Dagorel has continued my training where he had last left off. I think I\'ll make a choice to what type of style I\'ll pursue after he shows me the last way of fighting.',2310377,'Dagorel, the Master-at-Arms of Qeynos, has shown me different fighting styles.  Thanks to his training, I\'ve decided which way to direct my future training.  From hereon, I\'m no longer just a fighter.  In time, people will associate my name with my style of fighting.','Quests/Hallmark/fighter_training_pt_ii.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5789,'Path of the Crusader','Hallmark','Hallmark',10,1,'I\'ve gone over the teachings in my head, and I seem to be leaning towards becoming a crusader. I firmly believe in the defense of others before myself and in fighting for a cause. I will prove myself worthy of the title \"Crusader\"!',2310377,'I have rescued the frightened villager from the hands of a dangerous band of brigands, in the process proving to both myself and others that I fight for others and for what I believe in.  I am now worthy of becoming a crusader.','Quests/Hallmark/path_of_the_crusader.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5790,'Path of the Brawler','Hallmark','Hallmark',10,1,'I\'ve gone over the teachings in my head, and I seem to be leaning towards becoming a brawler. Dagorel has informed me that to become a brawler, I need to prove myself against a series of challenges in a dojo. I must prove my control over my actions by sparring, not killing, challengers within.',2310377,'One by one, I\'ve faced the opponents brought before me.  One by one, they have fallen before me.  I have proved myself worthy of becoming a brawler.','Quests/Hallmark/path_of_the_brawler.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5791,'Path of the Warrior','Hallmark','Hallmark',10,1,'I\'ve gone over the teachings in my head, and I seem to be leaning towards becoming a true warrior. Dagorel has instructed me to test my skills in an arena, where I will stretch them to their limits.',2310377,'I managed to defeat the creatures brought before me in the arena that was set up, and have proved myself worthy of being a warrior. Forever shall I wear this as a badge of courage and honor.','Quests/Hallmark/path_of_the_warrior.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5792,'The Call of Qeynos','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'I heard Antonia Bayle speak to me... \r\n\r\n\"Your loyalty will be tested, for you must earn the right to be called citizen.\"  \r\n\r\nI must speak with a Steward to begin my path towards citizenship to Qeynos. ',0,'I have taken the first steps declaring myself a true Qeynosian.','Quests/Hallmark/the_call_of_qeynos.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5793,'Maid for the Mist - Part I ','Access Quests','Nektulos Forest',25,1,'Daisy Winterhope is a Halfling in Nektulos who needs help building a ship to navigate the perilous waters of the Sea of Mist. In order to gain passage on her vessel, she requires payment in the form of materials.',1790042,'I have obtained 25 Nerius crab carapaces and 13 ash owlbear sinews and need to tell Daisy Winterhope in Nektulos. I hope this is enough for passage on her ship.','Quests/NektulosForest/maid_for_the_mist__part_I.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5794,'Corroborating the Existence of the Stormhold Library','Antonica','Antonica',20,1,'I found a strange mage in the Antonican hills named Timothus Yelrow. He said he was waiting for information to back up the previous story he heard about the uncovering of Stormhold and the library within. I told him I\'d find the library in exchange for some money and he agreed. I hope this doesn\'t get me killed...',120299,'I was able to find the library in Stormhold and provided Timothus Yelrow with information to verify what he previous heard. It looks like Timothus has plans concerning the uncovered library.','Quests/Antonica/corroborating_the_existence_of_the_stormhold_library.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5795,'Poaching the Poachers','Timorous Deep','Timorous Deep',1,1,'Tykor Gi\'Lok wants me to take out the Haoaeran poachers before they affect the food supplies of the Sarnak on Chrykori Island.',2630021,'I have slain the Haoaeran poachers for Tykor Gi\'Lok.','Quests/TimorousDeep/poaching_the_poachers.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5796,'Curious Ore','Timorous Deep','Timorous Deep',2,1,'Tykor Gi\'Lok is curious about the ore the Haoaerans have been mining along the beach wall inland to the west. He would like me to collect some samples of the ore for study.',2630021,'I have brought the ore samples to Tykor Gi\'Lok.','Quests/TimorousDeep/curious_ore.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5797,'Report to the Primary','Timorous Deep','Timorous Deep',3,1,'Tykor Gi\'Lok wants me to take this ore sample to Primary Conzuk Zum\'Ha. If I head north, I can take the ramp up into Chrykori Village where Primary Conzuk Zum\'Ha can be found.',2630021,'I have shown Primary Conzuk Zum\'Ha the ore sample.','Quests/TimorousDeep/report_to_the_primary.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5798,'Disrupting Haoaeran Studies','Timorous Deep','Timorous Deep',4,1,'Primary Conzuk Zum\'Ha would like me to travel northwest from Chrykori Village and take out the Haoaerans in the cave north of the Timeworn Pools. He would also like me to get a sample of whatever they\'re digging up.',2630460,'I have brought the inscribed pottery back to Primary Conzuk Zum\'Ha.','Quests/TimorousDeep/disrupting_haoaeran_studies.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5799,'Hunter\'s Manifest','Antonica','Antonica',12,1,'Upon reading the manifest, the idea of glorious hunts and the prestige of being a mighty hunter have inspired me to seek my fortune in the plains of Antonica. I shall not stop until I have proven my skills as a mighty hunter!',0,'I have hunted several different types of Antonican creatures, proving my skill in hunting to all those who cross my path.','Quests/Antonica/hunters_manifest.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5800,'A Festering Problem','World Event','World Event',25,1,'Intelligence Officer Gezlowe has informed me of something slightly disturbing. Apparently, a band of do-gooding Qeynosians has managed to find a way to heal the frog I ambushed out in the Commonlands. They\'re going to need to be taught a lesson.',5590146,'I\'ve managed to wipe out the scum of Qeynos and cleanse the stench of that foul frog from the lands outside the city gates. However, it looks like there may be more to be done.','Quests/Freeport/AFesteringProblem.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5801,'Hunter\'s Manifest','Antonica','Antonica',12,1,'Upon reading the manifest, the idea of glorious hunts and the prestige of being a mighty hunter have inspired me to seek my fortune in the plains of Antonica. I shall not stop until I have proven my skills as a mighty hunter!',0,'I have hunted several different types of Antonican creatures, proving my skill in hunting to all those who cross my path.','Quests/Antonica/hunters_manifest2.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5802,'Hunter\'s Manifest','Antonica','Antonica',12,1,'Upon reading the manifest, the idea of glorious hunts and the prestige of being a mighty hunter have inspired me to seek my fortune in the plains of Antonica. I shall not stop until I have proven my skills as a mighty hunter!',0,'I have hunted several different types of Antonican creatures, proving my skill in hunting to all those who cross my path.','Quests/Antonica/hunters_manifest3.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5803,'The Legend of Motte','Antonica','Antonica',19,1,'I have read about the Legend of Motte. Perhaps I can follow the rhyme and its instructions on how to help the spirit of Motte pass to peace beyond.',0,'I helped Sir Edwin Motte\'s spirit part from this world and its unrest. I earned a key that opened a secret compartment in Motte\'s tombstone filled with treasure.','Quests/Antonica/the_legend_of_motte.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5804,'The Hunt for the Windstalker Rumbler','Antonica','Antonica',21,8,'I read about the Windstalker Rumbler in a book found in the village of Windstalker Pond. Could this creature be real or is it just a myth to sway children from wandering off? I will keep this knowledge while I am in Antonica, although I very highly doubt that I will ever encounter such a creature.',0,'I killed the Windstalker Rumbler! I wonder if anyone would be interested, perhaps a family waiting to avenge one of theirs taken from them by this tunneling beast of Antonica.','Quests/Antonica/the_hunt_for_the_windstalker_rumbler.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5805,'These Boots Were Made For...','Heritage','Antonica',25,2,'I\'ve agreed to help Hwal Rucksif gather raw materials for his smithing. It seems that the sentries in Antonica have enlisted his assistance in re-outfitting themselves, but he just doesn\'t have the materials available to him to get the job done.',120197,'After a grueling series of tasks, Hwal Rucksif had the audacity to reward me with his... old work boots. Imagine that! All that work, and all he leaves me with is a pair of smelly old Dwarven Work Boots. At least they look broken in.','Quests/Antonica/these_boots_were_made_for.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5806,'A Tour of Antonica','Antonica','Antonica',15,1,'I have acquired a book titled \'Bootstrutter\'s Field Guide to Antonica.\' It appears to detail numerous points of interest within the region of Antonica. I have decided visit each location beginning with the first page.',0,'I visited all the locations listed in \'Bootstrutter\'s Field Guide to Antonica.\' Having done so, I decided to return the book to my cities\' local mage guild, keepers of all knowledge. They were delighted and rewarded me with a valuable piece of Bootstrutter gear.','Quests/Antonica/a_tour_of_antonica.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5807,'Quelling the Rebellion','World Event','World Event',30,1,'The frogloks seem to have found a savior in the dogs from Qeynos. They have organized a conspiracy to free this one from his cell inside the militia house. It would be a great honor to be the one to rid Freeport of these traitors.',0,'I have unraveled the traitorous plans of these frogs. It may be better that I simply destroy the one in the jail before he can cause more trouble or try and escape.','Quests/Freeport/QuellingTheRebellion.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5808,'Cold-blooded Relations...','World Event','The Lost Village of Kugup',35,1,'Teiluj has done something awfully foolish and he needs to get Oemor to forgive him, so I have to go pick some flowers and give them to her as a peace offering.',1230002,'I picked the flowers and delivered them to Oemor. She promptly forgot why she was mad and forgave Teiluj.','Quests/TheLostVillageofKugup/coldblooded_relations.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5809,'Whispers of Fortune','Antonica','Antonica',35,1,'Rikantus has told me to venture to Nektulos. There I shall cross a bridge and hope to find a clue as to where I may begin to follow the path of a former fortune hunter like myself.',120403,'I do not understand who or what Rikantus truly is, but I have survived the journey into Nektropos Castle and upon visiting Rikantus for a final time he has finally rewarded me.','Quests/Antonica/whispers_of_fortune.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5810,'Taking Out the Trash','World Event','The Lost Village of Kugup',35,1,'I\'ve been asked to help collect some trash bags from the Froglok trash cans and take them to the mage\'s platform to be used as target practice.',1230044,'I\'ve gathered trash for Pohpiks to use as target practice.','Quests/TheLostVillageofKugup/taking_out_the_trash.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5811,'The Fallen Bell','Antonica','Antonica',12,1,'When I touched the fallen bell in Vhalen\'s tower I saw visions of the sky lighting up like fire and the tower being hit by pieces of the shattering moon. Soon after the destruction, gnolls could be seen capitalizing on the chaos and suffering, advancing themselves further in the lands and attacking those trying to escape. The gnolls have yet to be driven back into their hole, Blackburrow, even to this day! I shall do my part in helping keep the gnolls away from Qeynos!',0,'I have slain quite a few gnolls, I hope my efforts do not go unnoticed. There are so many of them!','Quests/Antonica/the_fallen_bell.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5812,'Delivery From Sayer\'s Outfitters','Antonica','Antonica',15,4,'I have decided to help Mr. Sighard Sayer, owner of Sayer\'s Outfitters in Antonica. I will deliver some goods to clients for him.',120283,'After a long journey through the countryside of Antonica I finally delivered both shipments to their clients. Sayer paid me well for this deed.','Quests/Antonica/delivery_from_sayers_outfitters.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5813,'A Brass Key','Antonica','Antonica',12,6,'I found a key that has the head of a skull and crossed swords. This brass key is covered in rust, green tarnish and salt can be seen in the pits on the key.',0,'I used the key to open the cellar behind the lighthouse in Antonica and enter it.','Quests/Antonica/a_brass_key.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5814,'A Foul Wind','Access Quest','Antonica',19,1,'I found a request from Lord Nalin Glordar. He is in trouble at Firemyst Gully in the center of Antonica. He says that a cult of necromancers has shown their face there and are getting close to his encampment. He has asked for the assistance of the Qeynosian Guard. Hopefully it is not too late.',0,'Unfortunately it was too late when I arrived at Firemyst Gully. Lord Nalin and his encampment had succumbed to the touch of the Blightwind witches. The whole area will need to be cleansed now.','Quests/Antonica/a_foul_wind.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5815,'Fur Lined Gloves','Antonica','Antonica',15,1,'The small patch of dog fur has given me an idea. If I can gather enough of the pieces together, I might actually be able to make a nice set of gloves that wrap around my fingers perfectly.',0,'I\'ve been able to make a nice set of gloves for my hands. And they\'re fur lined, too!','Quests/Antonica/fur_lined_gloves.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5816,'Jolina Fairfeather\'s Gravestone','Antonica','Antonica',16,1,'Upon reading the gravestone, you find it hard to believe that the highwaymen in Antonica still roam as freely as they please. You decide it is time to seek justice in Jolina\'s name and kill these bandits.',0,'I have sought out the highwaymen in Antonica and made them pay for what they did to poor Jolina Fairfeather.','Quests/Antonica/jolina_fairfeathers_gravestone.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5817,'A Strange Gem','Antonica','Antonica',18,1,'I found a gem that looks like it was set in something. I should hang on to it.',0,'I found a statue and placed the gem in its eye revealing a small crawl space under the statue.','Quests/Antonica/a_strange_gem.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5818,'Far Seas Requisition. ANT0221','Antonica','Antonica',16,1,'Far Seas Trading Company: Far Seas Requisition OrderLocation: AntonicaFar Seas Huntsman to fill order of: Six Young Kodiak fur, Six Thicket Lizard tails, Two Sonic Shrieker wings.Resources are to be delivered to any local Far Seas Taskmaster of the Kingdom of Qeynos.',0,'I filled the Far Seas Requisition and delivered the goods to the Taskmaster out in Antonica. I have been paid in full for this work.','Quests/Antonica/far_seas_requisition_ant0221.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5819,'Far Seas Requisition. ANT0229','Antonica','Antonica',18,1,'Far Seas Trading Company: Far Seas Requisition OrderLocation: AntonicaFar Seas Huntsman to fill order of: Four handfuls of Rotstuffed Scarecrow hay, Two Earth Burrower eggs.Resources are to be delivered to any local Far Seas Taskmaster of the Kingdom of Qeynos.',0,'I filled the Far Seas Requisition and delivered the goods to the Taskmaster out in Antonica. I have been paid in full for this work.','Quests/Antonica/far_seas_requisition_ant0229.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5820,'Far Seas Requisition. ANT0235','Antonica','Antonica',12,1,'Far Seas Trading Company: Far Seas Requisition OrderLocation: AntonicaFar Seas Huntsman to fill order of: Six Klicnik Mite carapaces, Six Moat Rat tails, Six Lowland Viper fangs.Resources are to be delivered to any local Far Seas Taskmaster of the Kingdom of Qeynos.',0,'I filled the Far Seas Requisition and delivered the goods to the Taskmaster out in Antonica. I have been paid in full for this work.','Quests/Antonica/far_seas_requisition_ant0235.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5821,'Far Seas Requisition. ANT0243','Antonica','Antonica',13,1,'Far Seas Trading Company: Far Seas Requisition OrderLocation: AntonicaFar Seas Huntsman to fill order of: Ten lowland badger pelts. Resources are to be delivered to any local Far Seas Taskmaster of the Kingdom of Qeynos.',0,'I filled the Far Seas Requisition and delivered the goods to the Taskmaster out in Antonica. I have been paid in full for this work.','Quests/Antonica/far_seas_requisition_ant0243.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5822,'Far Seas Requisition. ANT0244','Antonica','Antonica',15,1,'Far Seas Trading Company: Far Seas Requisition OrderLocation: AntonicaFar Seas Huntsman to fill order of: Ten Timber Wolf pelts.Resources are to be delivered to any local Far Seas Taskmaster of the Kingdom of Qeynos.',0,'I filled the Far Seas Requisition and delivered the goods to the Taskmaster out in Antonica. I have been paid in full for this work.','Quests/Antonica/far_seas_requisition_ant0244.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5823,'Far Seas Requisition. ANT0351','Antonica','Antonica',13,1,'Far Seas Trading Company: Far Seas Requisition OrderLocation: AntonicaFar Seas Huntsman to fill order of: Five Bear cub furs, Five Pond Beaver pelts.Resources are to be delivered to any local Far Seas Taskmaster of the Kingdom of Qeynos.',0,'I filled the Far Seas Requisition and delivered the goods to the Taskmaster out in Antonica. I have been paid in full for this work.','Quests/Antonica/far_seas_requisition_ant0351.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5824,'Far Seas Requisition. ANT037','Antonica','Antonica',18,1,'Far Seas Trading Company: Far Seas Requisition OrderLocation: AntonicaFar Seas Huntsman to fill order of: Six Thorn Briar branches, Two Stonejaw Lizard skulls.Resources are to be delivered to any local Far Seas Taskmaster of the Kingdom of Qeynos.',0,'I filled the Far Seas Requisition and delivered the goods to the Taskmaster out in Antonica. I have been paid in full for this work.','Quests/Antonica/far_seas_requisition_ant037.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5825,'Far Seas Requisition. ANT0424','Antonica','Antonica',14,1,'Far Seas Trading Company: Far Seas Requisition OrderLocation: AntonicaFar Seas Huntsman to fill order of: Four Lowland Gecko tails, Six Coldwind Manta Ray stingers.Resources are to be delivered to any local Far Seas Taskmaster of the Kingdom of Qeynos.',0,'I filled the Far Seas Requisition and delivered the goods to the Taskmaster out in Antonica. I have been paid in full for this work.','Quests/Antonica/far_seas_requisition_ant0424.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5826,'Far Seas Requisition. ANT0437','Antonica','Antonica',18,1,'Far Seas Trading Company: Far Seas Requisition OrderLocation: AntonicaFar Seas Huntsman to fill order of: Five Haze Kodiak furs, Two Stonejaw Lizard skulls.Resources are to be delivered to any local Far Seas Taskmaster of the Kingdom of Qeynos.',0,'I filled the Far Seas Requisition and delivered the goods to the Taskmaster out in Antonica. I have been paid in full for this work.','Quests/Antonica/far_seas_requisition_ant0437.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5827,'Far Seas Requisition. ANT0724','Antonica','Antonica',18,1,'Far Seas Trading Company: Far Seas Requisition Order Location: Antonica Far Seas Huntsman to fill order of: an ancient octopus ink sac. Resources are to be delivered to any local Far Seas Taskmaster of the Kingdom of Qeynos.',0,'I filled the Far Seas Requisition and delivered the goods to the Taskmaster out in Antonica. I have been paid in full for this work.','Quests/Antonica/far_seas_requisition_ant0724.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5828,'The Cavemaw\'s Sinister Map','Antonica','Antonica',17,1,'Reading the map has made it obvious that the gnolls are planning something bigger than just mining the hills of Antonica. The Cavemaw tunnelers seem to be the key to the whole thing, I should stop them!',0,'I have slain a large amount of the seemingly limitless supply of Cavemaw tunnelers. I hope my efforts slowed them down a bit.','Quests/Antonica/the_cavemaws_sinister_map.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5829,'The Restless Runestone','Antonica','Antonica',18,1,'Underneath the boat I found what appears to be a restless runestone. The runestone is a marker used to attract undead to attack or occupy a particular place. Perhaps an army of undead are coming to the area. I should put a stop to this.',0,'I found some restless Caltorsites nearby, so I dispatched them with hopes of staving off any attempt to attack the watermill.','Quests/Antonica/the_restless_runestone.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5830,'The Starwisp Sword','Antonica','Antonica',16,1,'I\'ve found a rusty blade that looks like it was once a very powerful sword. It may be possible to restore this sword back to its original condition.',0,'I\'ve been able to not only clean the sword but restore it back to its original condition. For some reason I believe the name of the sword is Starwisp.','Quests/Antonica/the_starwisp_sword.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5831,'Ancient Kite Shield','Antonica','Antonica',13,1,'I\'ve found an old shield that\'s covered with muck and grime. The dirt seems to go deep into the metal, but it may be able to be cleaned.',0,'I\'ve cleaned the dirt off of the shield and now have an Ancient Kite Shield with the image of the Qeynos Gates on the front of the shield face.','Quests/Antonica/ancient_kite_shield.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5832,'Meteoric Hoop','Antonica','Antonica',16,1,'I\'ve found a meteor chunk that is large enough to be worked into something else. With a little hard work, I might be able to turn it into a nice piece of jewelry.',0,'I\'ve been able to take the meteor chunk I found and turn it into a nice Meteoric Hoop.','Quests/Antonica/meteoric_hoop.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5833,'Revenge on the Kodiaks','Antonica','Antonica',16,1,'I found a small banner in the reeds that pays tribute to a froglok who was attacked by a young kodiak while fishing. I have decided to act against these bears to prevent this from happening to someone else.',0,'I have slain some of the young kodiaks in the area, I hope that culls the population enough to make the area safer.','Quests/Antonica/revenge_on_the_kodiaks.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5834,'Strange Mutations','Antonica','Antonica',15,1,'I have found a drawing of a strangely mutated rat made by a local child.',0,'I wonder what could have caused these strange mutations...','Quests/Antonica/strange_mutations.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5835,'Wanted Gnoll Bandit!','Antonica','Antonica',15,1,'You have found what appears to be a wanted poster. On it you see a sketch of a Darkpaw gnoll\'s face.',0,'You have slain the Gnoll bandits.','Quests/Antonica/wanted_gnoll_bandit.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5836,'Wanted by Order of the City of Qeynos','Antonica','Antonica',18,1,'I have found a wanted poster ordering the destruction of beasts wanted by the City of Qeynos. It is my duty to help my city in any way that I can.',0,'I have carried out the orders on the wanted poster.','Quests/Antonica/wanted_by_order_of_the_city_of_qeynos.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5837,'Freedom','Antonica','Antonica',16,1,'I\'ve found a very odd bundle of chains and leather straps. I\'m certain there\'s something in the center of this bundle, but I can\'t make out what it is.',0,'I\'ve destroyed all of the chains that were hiding away Freedom, the legendary maul.','Quests/Antonica/freedom.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5838,'A Gnoll\'s Doll','Antonica','Antonica',15,1,'I found what looks like a gnoll\'s doll. This doll looks like it has claw and teeth marks in it. Judging from the marks, it was used by a Gnoll Mystic in a ritual of some sort.',0,'You feel much better now that there are fewer Darkpaw Mystics in the world.','Quests/Antonica/a_gnolls_doll.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5839,'Deadly Undead','Antonica','Antonica',18,1,'I have the journal entry of a Paladin named Grentithius. It reads: \"I\'m concerned about the undead population in this area. Left unchecked, they may prove to be the end of our great city. I should destroy the more powerful undead to cull their numbers.\"',0,'The undead Caltorsis in this area seem to be unaffected by my efforts. However, I have learned a great deal about the undead of Antonica. In the future, perhaps this experience will be of some use to me.','Quests/Antonica/deadly_undead.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5840,'The Missing','World Event','World Event',25,1,'A new froglok has washed up on the shores of Qeynos. Frup Groaak bids me seek out a lost compatriot of his, Giidib. Very curiously, no one seems to have heard anything about frogloks outside of Qeynos since the Age of Cataclysms.',0,'Though I tried to get Giidib to safety, the assassin\'s poison had already done its work. Upon arriving at the tower, he collapsed and died. If I read Frup correctly, it seems he may think there is something larger behind this attack.','Quests/WorldEvent/the_missing.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5841,'A Pain in the Backside','Antonica','Antonica',16,1,'I have discovered what appears to be the remains of a Bloodsaber Soldier\'s chest armor. The armor has no trace of tarnish, but there is a gaping hole in the small of the back. It must have taken a great force to break through this armor. I should find something I can use to patch the hole in the backside of this armor.',0,'I have managed to restore to the Bloodsaber chestpiece to a usable condition.','Quests/Antonica/a_pain_in_the_backside.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5842,'Bug Squashing','Antonica','Antonica',15,1,'The klicnik carapace really brought to light the outrageous amount of klicnik warriors in the area close to Qeynos. I should make an effort to squash a bunch of these fiery bugs, for the safety of anyone who might come through this area.\r\nStage 1',0,'I have destroyed quite a few klicnik warriors, I hope this helps keep them away from Qeynos.','Quests/Antonica/bug_squashing.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5843,'Isabella Cellus\' History of Antonica','Antonica','Antonica',13,1,'This is more of a portfolio than book as so many pages are missing. Reading through the pages that exist, I get the impression that the remaining pages are likely to be found in and around Antonica.',0,'I\'ve gathered many scattered pages of Isabella Cellus\' book. I wonder whether any of her descendants also wrote any histories? I shall keep my eyes open. Perhaps, someday, I\'ll find other tomes such as this throughout Norrath.','Quests/Antonica/isabella_cellus_history_of_antonica.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5844,'Ignatia Cellus\' History of Antonica','Antonica','Antonica',19,1,'This is more of a portfolio than book as so many pages are missing. Reading through the pages that exist, I get the impression that the remaining pages are likely to be found in and around Antonica.',0,'I\'ve gathered many scattered pages of Ignatia Cellus\' book. I wonder whether any of her descendants also wrote any histories? I shall keep my eyes open. Perhaps, someday, I\'ll find other tomes such as this throughout Norrath.','Quests/Antonica/ignatia_cellus_history_of_antonica.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
