(5858,'Stowaway: Antonica','Antonica','Alpha Test',1,1,'[ EMU Testing Passage ]\r\nThe Shady Swashbuckler provided me passage to Antonica. I need to find him once I arrive to arrange all the required paperwork.',0,'I have all the necessary parts for the Fast-Track passage to Qeynos. The ride was a bit cramped...','Quests/AlphaTest/stowaway_antonica.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5859,'Welcome to Freeport','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'I have finally arrived in Freeport and spoke with the Overseer of the district. Were it not for the fact that I\'ve been given a house, I think I would\'ve taught that Overseer a thing or two. Now it\'s time for me to gain my bearings.',0,'I\'ve managed to keep from killing Vathun long enough for me to familiarize myself with Stonestair Byway.  That disgusting man has shown me what I need to know about my new home, along with pointing me at who I need to talk to in order to become a citizen.  The next time we meet, things will be much different.','Quests/Hallmark/welcome_to_freeport__stonestair.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5860,'Welcome to Freeport','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'I have finally arrived in Freeport and spoke with the Overseer of the district. Were it not for the fact that I\'ve been given a house, I think I would\'ve taught that Overseer a thing or two. Now it\'s time for me to gain my bearings.',0,'I\'ve managed to keep from killing Vathun long enough for me to familiarize myself with Big Bend.  That disgusting man has shown me what I need to know about my new home, along with pointing me at who I need to talk to in order to become a citizen.  The next time we meet, things will be much different.','Quests/Hallmark/welcome_to_freeport__big_bend.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5861,'Welcome to Freeport','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'I have finally arrived in Freeport and spoke with the Overseer of the district. Were it not for the fact that I\'ve been given a house, I think I would\'ve taught that Overseer a thing or two. Now it\'s time for me to gain my bearings.',0,'I\'ve managed to keep from killing Vathun long enough for me to familiarize myself with Beggar\'s Court.  That disgusting man has shown me what I need to know about my new home, along with pointing me at who I need to talk to in order to become a citizen.  The next time we meet, things will be much different.','Quests/Hallmark/welcome_to_freeport__beggars_court.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5862,'Welcome to Freeport','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'I have finally arrived in Freeport and spoke with the Overseer of the district. Were it not for the fact that I\'ve been given a house, I think I would\'ve taught that Overseer a thing or two. Now it\'s time for me to gain my bearings.',0,'I\'ve managed to keep from killing Vathun long enough for me to familiarize myself with Longshadow Alley.  That disgusting man has shown me what I need to know about my new home, along with pointing me at who I need to talk to in order to become a citizen.  The next time we meet, things will be much different.','Quests/Hallmark/welcome_to_freeport__longshadow_alley.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5863,'Welcome to Freeport','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'I have finally arrived in Freeport and spoke with the Overseer of the district. Were it not for the fact that I\'ve been given a house, I think I would\'ve taught that Overseer a thing or two. Now it\'s time for me to gain my bearings.',0,'I\'ve managed to keep from killing Vathun long enough for me to familiarize myself with Scale Yard.  That disgusting man has shown me what I need to know about my new home, along with pointing me at who I need to talk to in order to become a citizen.  The next time we meet, things will be much different.','Quests/Hallmark/welcome_to_freeport__scale_yard.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5864,'Welcome to Freeport','Hallmark','Hallmark',1,1,'I have finally arrived in Freeport and spoke with the Overseer of the district. Were it not for the fact that I\'ve been given a house, I think I would\'ve taught that Overseer a thing or two. Now it\'s time for me to gain my bearings.',0,'I\'ve managed to keep from killing Vathun long enough for me to familiarize myself with Temple Street.  That disgusting man has shown me what I need to know about my new home, along with pointing me at who I need to talk to in order to become a citizen.  The next time we meet, things will be much different.','Quests/Hallmark/welcome_to_freeport__temple_street.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5865,'Freeport Citizen\'s Guide to Opportunity','Hallmark','Hallmark',7,1,'To reward those who become Freeport citizens, the Overlord has commissioned this book as his gift to those with the foresight to recognize his superiority. It contains several sections that recommend activities for citizens to undertake while in his service.',0,'This book is one more example of the Overlord\'s concern with the welfare of all Freeport citizens. All praise the Overlord!','Quests/Hallmark/freeport_citizens_guide_to_opportunity.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5866,'Big Bend Citizenship Task','Hallmark','Hallmark',5,1,'The task list requires that all citizens of Big Bend gather tokens from the Sprawl in order to show their worth to the citizenship officials.',0,'The task list is completed and you may now apply to become a citizen of the city of Freeport.','Quests/Hallmark/big_bend_citizenship_task.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5867,'Beggar\'s Court Citizenship Task','Hallmark','Hallmark',5,1,'The Sunken City has been seeded with tokens for the residents of Beggar\'s Court to gather. These tokens may be found on any creatures in the Sunken City. I can reach the Sunken City by using any of the bells in and around the City of Freeport.',0,'The task list is completed and you may now apply to become a citizen of the city of Freeport.','Quests/Hallmark/beggars_court_citizenship_task.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5868,'Longshadow Alley Citizenship Task','Hallmark','Hallmark',5,1,'The Ruins have been seeded with tokens for the citizens of Longshadow Alley to gather. These tokens may be found on any creatures in the Ruins. I can reach the Ruins by using any of the bells in and around the City of Freeport.',0,'The task list is completed and you may now apply to become a citizen of the city of Freeport.','Quests/Hallmark/longshadow_alley_citizenship_task.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5869,'Scale Yard Citizenship Task','Hallmark','Hallmark',5,1,'The task list requires that all residents of the Scale Yard gather tokens from the Thieves\' Way in order to show their worth to the citizenship officials.',0,'The task list is completed and you may now apply to become a citizen of the city of Freeport.','Quests/Hallmark/scale_yard_citizenship_task.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5870,'Stonestair Byway Citizenship Task','Hallmark','Hallmark',5,1,'The task list requires that all citizens of Stonestair Byway gather tokens from the Graveyard in order to show their worth to the citizenship officials.',0,'The task list is completed and you may now apply to become a citizen of the city of Freeport.','Quests/Hallmark/stonestair_byway_citizenship_task.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5871,'Temple Street Citizenship Task','Hallmark','Hallmark',5,1,'The task list requires that all residents of Temple Street gather tokens from the Thieves\' Way in order to show their worth to the citizenship officials.',0,'The task list is completed and you may now apply to become a citizen of the city of Freeport.','Quests/Hallmark/temple_street_citizenship_task.lua',0,0,0,0,0),
(5872,'Death Certificate','North Freeport','North Freeport',7,1,'Missionary G\'Zule has given me the death certificate of guard Barel to give to his widow, merchant Talia. Talia can be found in the Ruins. I don\'t think she is going to be too happy about this.\r\n',1440056,'I have given the death certificate of guard Barel to merchant Talia at the request of missionary G\'Zule.','Quests/NorthFreeport/death_certificate.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5873,'Vleko\'s Plan','Temple Street','Temple Street',6,1,'Vleko, the Ratonga merchant, wants me to bring him a sword from an orc. It seems he plans on killing his rivals and letting the orcs take the blame.',1360019,'Vleko paid me for the sword, and let me know that our deal is complete.','Quests/TempleStreet/vlekos_plan.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5874,'Muckwort\'s Quest','Temple Street','Temple Street',9,1,'Old Man Muckwort wants me to get a vial of \'something\' from Crantik the Crazed. I\'m not too sure what that foolish old man has in mind.',1360023,'Muckwort gave me an old mug in exchange for my service. I think he plans on poisoning the area so that the gnomes and ratonga don\'t step on his lawn anymore.','Quests/TempleStreet/Muckworts_Quest.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5876,'Teeth for Sparzit','Temple Street','Temple Street',6,1,'I\'ve met a gnome by the name of Sparzit within Temple Street. He has been looking for teeth from some snakes. I think I\'ve heard of some being found in the Sprawl.',1360041,'Sparzit was rather happy with the fangs I brought him. He gave me some coin for gathering the teeth for him.','Quests/TempleStreet/teeth_for_sparzit.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5877,'Obtain Adventurer Class','Hallmark','Hallmark',9,1,'I need to speak with Magister Niksel in South Qeynos about advancing as a mage.',0,'I spoke with Magister Niksel about advancing.','Quests/Hallmark/obtain_adventurer_class__qmage.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5878,'Obtain Adventurer Class','Hallmark','Hallmark',9,1,'I need to speak with Master at Arms Dagorel in South Qeynos about advancing as a fighter.',0,'I have contacted Master at Arms Dagorel about advancing.','Quests/Hallmark/obtain_adventurer_class__qfighter.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5879,'Obtain Adventurer Class','Hallmark','Hallmark',9,1,'I need to speak with Hierophant Aldalad in North Qeynos about advancing as a priest.',0,'I have contacted Hierophant Aldalad about advancing.','Quests/Hallmark/obtain_adventurer_class__qpriest.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(5880,'Obtain Adventurer Class','Hallmark','Hallmark',9,1,'I need to speak with Counselor Vemerik in North Qeynos about advancing as a scout.',0,'I have contacted Counselor Vemerik about advancing.','Quests/Hallmark/obtain_adventurer_class__qscout.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
