(6087,'Extinguisher','City Tasks','South Qeynos',17,1,'Students of the Three Towers are finding their magic ineffective against the scorched undead of Stormhold. Pupil Adept Wazzlefop of the Concordium has petitioned me to clear out this obstruction by destroying the skeletons.',2310070,'The acolytes should find their adventures through Stormhold easier now that I have destroyed a number of the undead.','Quests/SouthQeynos/extinguisher.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
