(6090,'Escorting the Royal Planners','City Tasks','South Qeynos',21,1,'Researchers attempting to survey Thundering Steppes have been impeded by aggressions from gnoll scouts. Chronicler Steelwill of the Concordium has petitioned me to remove this obstacle to the Three Towers by slaughtering Sabertooths.',2310059,'The assaults against the surveyors have slowed now that I have slaughtered a number of gnolls.','Quests/SouthQeynos/escorting_the_royal_planners.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(6091,'Mudslides and Sludge Water','City Tasks','South Qeynos',22,1,'The weeds and bracken within Thundering Steppes are being devoured by beetles, causing erosion and flooding of the lands. Chronicler Steelwill of the Concordium has petitioned me to restore order to the area by destroying the giant insects.',2310059,'The grass and scrub have returned to Thundering Steppes now that I have destroyed a number of the giant beetles.','Quests/SouthQeynos/mudslides_and_sludge_water.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(6092,'The Echoes of Silence','City Tasks','South Qeynos',26,1,'Screeching, swooping bats have been interrupting the research and meditations of scholars who adventure within the Ruins of Varsoon. Chronicler Steelwill of the Concordium has petitioned me to bring quietude to the caverns by slaying the shrieking bats.',2310059,'The sages should find more serene their meditations and studies now that I slain a number of the screeching bats.','Quests/SouthQeynos/the_echoes_of_silence.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(6093,'Boil with Oil','City Tasks','South Qeynos',27,1,'Blistering goos have been seeping up from the caverns below to contaminate with ooze the soil of Thundering Steppes. Chronicler Steelwill of the Concordium has petitioned me to impede the advancement by killing the goos within the Ruins of Varsoon.',2310059,'The contamination of the land should be slowed now that I have killed a number of the giant goos.','Quests/SouthQeynos/boil_with_oil.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(6094,'Secrets of the Shade','City Tasks','South Qeynos',27,1,'Students of the Three Towers sent to research the secrets of the Ruins of Varsoon describe as impregnable the lower chambers of this ancient tomb. Chronicler Steelwill of the Concordium has petitioned me to clear a path for the researchers by slaughtering the undead guards.',2310059,'The Concordium sages have found easier their incursions into the lower chambers now that I have slaughtered a number of the blighted protectors.','Quests/SouthQeynos/secrets_of_the_shade.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(6095,'He Was Number One!','City Tasks','South Qeynos',28,1,'Seers have determined the intent of the blighted sages within the Ruins of Varsoon to be the resurrection of the shade Valdoartus Varsoon. Chronicler Steelwill of the Concordium has petitioned me to destroy the undead apprentices before their labor unleashes an ancient fury upon the Shattered Lands.',2310059,'The ability of the blighted researchers to restore the remains of Valdoartus Varsoon has been diminished now that I have destroyed a number of the undead sages.','Quests/SouthQeynos/he_was_number_one.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(6096,'Bitter Utilitarianism','City Tasks','South Qeynos',33,1,'Deer within the Orcish Wastes have been devouring briarwood, an ingredient necessary for the production of parchment paper. Aesthetic Winchester of the Concordium has petitioned me to protect this resource by killing the dikdiks.',2310088,'The supply to Qeynos of briarwood has stabilized now that I have killed a number of glade deer.','Quests/SouthQeynos/bitter_utilitarianism.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(6097,'Millennium of the Scholar','City Tasks','South Qeynos',33,1,'Corrupted treants within the Orcish Wastes have been plunging their roots deep into crypts and subterranean ruins, collapsing the catacombs and burying with them tomes, artifacts, and scrolls. Aesthetic Winchester of the Concordium has petitioned me to preserve the dungeons for future research and discovery by slaying withered odeums.',2310088,'The destruction of the catacombs has slowed now that I have slain a number of the treant vandals.','Quests/SouthQeynos/millennium_of_the_scholar.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(6098,'Did It All for the Sake of Art','City Tasks','South Qeynos',34,1,'Raja Zutazakhan was a prominent scholar within the Three Towers before betraying Qeynos to sell his arcane talents to the Deathfist Empire. Now he seeks to mutate and corrupt the beasts of the Orcish Wastes. Aesthetic Winchester of the Concordium has petitioned me to destroy the abyss panthers before they are transformed into terrifying monstrosities that threaten the outpost.',2310088,'The danger from tainted panthers has been reduced now that I have destroyed a number of the great cats.','Quests/SouthQeynos/did_it_all_for_the_sake_of_art.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(6099,'Repulse the Bruisers','City Tasks','South Qeynos',33,1,'Orc savages have been ambushing scholars attempting to uncover the forgotten secrets of Jaggedpine Forest. Aesthetic Winchester of the Concordium has petitioned me to enable this research by slaughtering the Zek brutes within the Orcish Wastes.',2310088,'The sages have resumed their studies of the ancients now that I have slaughtered a number of orc mercenaries.','Quests/SouthQeynos/repulse_the_bruisers.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(6100,'Fulfill Your Oath','City Tasks','South Qeynos',37,1,'Reports indicate that lizardmen mystics are summoning an army of undead pirates and thugs to command in an assault against Qeynos Harbor. Aesthetic Winchester of the Concordium has petitioned me to prevent an attack by slaughtering Evol Ew priests within the Feerrott.',2310088,'The Alliz Evol Ew invasion has been disrupted now that I have slaughtered a number of the lizardmen defilers.','Quests/SouthQeynos/fulfill_your_oath.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(6101,'Venomous Vipers','City Tasks','South Qeynos',37,1,'Sages of the Three Towers sent to survey the jungles have found river crossings perilous to their steeds on account of the poisonous eels that lurk within the waters. Aesthetic Winchester of the Concordium has petitioned me to remove this threat by slaying water snakes within the Feerrott.',2310088,'The attacks against horses and pack mules have slowed now that I have slain a number of the eels.','Quests/SouthQeynos/venomous_vipers.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(6102,'Watch One, Do One, Teach One','City Tasks','South Qeynos',37,1,'Students sent by the Three Towers to perfect their skills within the terrifying tangle of the Feerrott have found themselves defenseless against the savagery of kholrat lashers. Aesthetic Winchester of the Concordium has petitioned me to remove this danger by killing the underbrush beasts.',2310088,'The apprentices have been able to continue their studies now that I have killed a number of the kholrat ravagers.','Quests/SouthQeynos/watch_one_do_one_teach_one.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
(6103,'Jungle Prowlers','City Tasks','South Qeynos',38,1,'Merchants attempting to forage for rare herbs and dyes within the Feerrott have suffered ambushes from forest spiders lurking in the trees. Aesthetic Winchester of the Concordium has petitioned me to ensure the supply of goods by destroying forest leapers.',2310088,'Merchants have found safer their travels through the forests now that I have destroyed a number of the giant spiders.','Quests/SouthQeynos/jungle_prowlers.lua',0,1,0,0,0),
